CREATE TABLE [dbo].[tblNomenConfig](
	Tabela [nvarchar](200) NOT NULL,
	Camp [nvarchar](200) NOT NULL,
	TipCamp [int] NULL,
	Vizibil [int] NULL DEFAULT 1,
	SursaCombo [nvarchar](max) NULL,
	IdAutomat [int] NULL DEFAULT 0,
	[USER_NO] [int] NULL,
	[TIME] [date] NULL
 CONSTRAINT [PK_tblNomenConfig] PRIMARY KEY CLUSTERED 
(
	Tabela ASC,
	Camp ASC
)WITH (PAD_INDEX = OFF, STATISTICS_NORECOMPUTE = OFF, IGNORE_DUP_KEY = OFF, ALLOW_ROW_LOCKS = ON, ALLOW_PAGE_LOCKS = ON) ON [PRIMARY]
) ON [PRIMARY]

GO

EXEC sp_addextendedproperty  'MS_Description', '0 - General; 1 - CheckBox; 2 - ComboBox; 3 - Date; 4 - Memo; 5 - ColorPicker', N'Schema', dbo, N'Table',  'tblNomenConfig', N'Column', 'TipCamp';
GO

GO

GO

GO

GO

GO

GO

ALTER TABLE Securitate ALTER COLUMN IdControl nvarchar(150) NOT NULL
GO

ALTER TABLE Securitate ALTER COLUMN IdColoana nvarchar(150) NOT NULL
GO

) ON [PRIMARY]

DELETE FROM relGrupAngajat2 WHERE IdGrup IS NULL OR F10003 IS NULL
GO

delete relGrupAngajat2 from relGrupAngajat2 A
LEFT JOIN (select F10003, IdGrup, MIN(IdAuto) AS IdAuto from relGrupAngajat2 GROUP BY IdGrup, F10003 HAVING COUNT(F10003)>1) B ON A.IdAuto=B.IdAuto
WHERE B.IdAuto IS NULL
GO

ALTER TABLE relGrupAngajat2 DROP CONSTRAINT relGrupAngajat_PK
GO

ALTER TABLE relGrupAngajat2 ALTER COLUMN IdGrup int not null
GO

ALTER TABLE relGrupAngajat2 ALTER COLUMN F10003 int not null
GO

ALTER TABLE relGrupAngajat2 ADD CONSTRAINT relGrupAngajat_PK PRIMARY KEY (IdGrup,F10003)
GO

CREATE TABLE [dbo].[tblZile](
	[Zi] [datetime] NOT NULL,
	[ZiSapt] [int] NULL,
 CONSTRAINT [PK_tblZile] PRIMARY KEY CLUSTERED 
(
	[Zi] ASC
)WITH (PAD_INDEX = OFF, STATISTICS_NORECOMPUTE = OFF, IGNORE_DUP_KEY = OFF, ALLOW_ROW_LOCKS = ON, ALLOW_PAGE_LOCKS = ON) ON [PRIMARY]
) ON [PRIMARY]

GO

DECLARE @zi date

SET @zi = CONVERT(date,'1996/01/01')

WHILE (DATEDIFF(D,@zi,'2030/12/31')>=0)
	BEGIN
	insert into tblZile(zi)
	values(@zi)
	set @zi = DATEADD(D,1,@zi)
	END

GO

update tblZile set ZiSapt=CASE WHEN (datepart(dw,Zi) - 1) =0 THEN 7 ELSE (datepart(dw,Zi) - 1) end
GO

CREATE TABLE [dbo].[Ptj_tblAbsenteConfig](
	[Id] [int] IDENTITY(1,1) NOT NULL,
	[IdAbsenta] [int] NOT NULL,
	[Denumire] [nvarchar](150) NOT NULL,
	[TipCamp] [int] NOT NULL,
	[Obligatoriu] [int] NULL CONSTRAINT [DF_Ptj_tblAbsenteConfig_Obligatoriu]  DEFAULT ((0)),
	[ReadOnly] [int] NULL CONSTRAINT [DF_Ptj_tblAbsenteConfig_ReadOnly]  DEFAULT ((0)),
	[Sursa] [nvarchar](max) NULL,
	[IdCampExtra] [int] NULL,
	[TIME] [datetime] NULL CONSTRAINT [DF_Ptj_tblAbsenteConfig_TIME]  DEFAULT (getdate()),
	[USER_NO] [int] NULL,
 CONSTRAINT [PK_Ptj_tblAbsenteConfig_1] PRIMARY KEY CLUSTERED 
(
	[Id] ASC
)WITH (PAD_INDEX = OFF, STATISTICS_NORECOMPUTE = OFF, IGNORE_DUP_KEY = OFF, ALLOW_ROW_LOCKS = ON, ALLOW_PAGE_LOCKS = ON) ON [PRIMARY]
) ON [PRIMARY] TEXTIMAGE_ON [PRIMARY]

GO

EXEC sys.sp_addextendedproperty @name=N'MS_Description', @value=N'0 - General; 1 - CheckBox; 2 - ComboBox; 3 - Date; 4 - Memo; 5 - ColorPicker' , 

@level0type=N'SCHEMA',@level0name=N'dbo', @level1type=N'TABLE',@level1name=N'Ptj_tblAbsenteConfig', @level2type=N'COLUMN',@level2name=N'TipCamp'
GO

ALTER TABLE "Ptj_tblAbsente" ADD "NrMax" int
GO
ALTER TABLE "Ptj_tblAbsente" ADD "NrMaxAn" int
GO

GO

union
select 1 as Id, ''CheckBox'' as Denumire
union
select 2 as Id, ''ComboBox'' as Denumire
union
select 3 as Id, ''Date'' as Denumire
union
select 4 as Id, ''Memo'' as Denumire
union
select 5 as Id, ''ColorPicker'' as Denumire
union
select 6 as Id, ''Text'' as Denumire
union
select 7 as Id, ''Numeric'' as Denumire' where tabela='tblNomenConfig' and Camp='tipcamp'
GO


CREATE FUNCTION [dbo].[DamiSuperMail]
(
	@IdSuper int, @F10003 int, @IdUSerLogat int
)
RETURNS nvarchar(250)
AS
BEGIN

	DECLARE @rez nvarchar(250);

	SELECT TOP 1 @rez= CASE WHEN A.Mail IS NOT NULL OR A.Mail<>'' THEN A.Mail ELSE B.F100894 END 
	FROM 
	(
		SELECT *, -1 AS Ordine FROM F100Supervizori WHERE IdSuper=@IdSuper AND IdUser=@IdUserLogat AND F10003=@F10003
		UNION
		SELECT *, 0 AS Ordine FROM F100Supervizori where IdSuper=@IdSuper AND F10003=@F10003
	) X 
	LEFT JOIN USERS A ON X.IdUser=A.F70102
	LEFT JOIN F100 B ON A.F10003=B.F10003	
	ORDER BY X.Ordine

	return @rez;

END

GO





CREATE FUNCTION [dbo].[DamiSuperNume]
(
	@IdSuper int, @F10003 int, @IdUSerLogat int
)
RETURNS nvarchar(250)
AS
BEGIN

	DECLARE @rez nvarchar(250);

	SELECT TOP 1 @rez= CASE WHEN B.F10008 IS NOT NULL OR B.F10003<>'' THEN COALESCE(B.F10008,' ') + ' ' + COALESCE(B.F10009,' ') ELSE A.F70104 END 
	FROM 
	(
		SELECT *, -1 AS Ordine FROM F100Supervizori WHERE IdSuper=@IdSuper AND IdUser=@IdUserLogat AND F10003=@F10003
		UNION
		SELECT *, 0 AS Ordine FROM F100Supervizori where IdSuper=@IdSuper AND F10003=@F10003
	) X 
	LEFT JOIN USERS A ON X.IdUser=A.F70102
	LEFT JOIN F100 B ON A.F10003=B.F10003	
	ORDER BY X.Ordine

	return @rez;

END

GO

CREATE SEQUENCE [dbo].[USERS_SEQ] 
 AS [bigint]
 START WITH 1203
 INCREMENT BY 1
 MINVALUE 1
 MAXVALUE 9999999999999
 CACHE 
GO





exec sp_rename 'tblSupervizori', 'tblSupervizori2'
GO

CREATE VIEW tblSupervizori
AS 

SELECT Id, Denumire, Alias, IdUser, ModululCereriAbsente, USER_NO, TIME FROM tblSupervizori2
UNION
SELECT 76, 'Fara rol', 'Fara rol', 1, 1, 1, GetDate()
UNION
SELECT 78, 'Inlocuitor/Delegat', 'Inlocuitor/Delegat', 1, 1, 1, GetDate()

GO

CREATE TABLE [dbo].[tblProiecte](
	[Id] [int] NOT NULL,
	[Denumire] [nvarchar](50) NULL,
	[IdResponsabil] [int] NULL,
	[DataInceput] [datetime] NULL,
	[DataSfarsit] [datetime] NULL,

(
	[Id] ASC
)WITH (PAD_INDEX = OFF, STATISTICS_NORECOMPUTE = OFF, IGNORE_DUP_KEY = OFF, ALLOW_ROW_LOCKS = ON, ALLOW_PAGE_LOCKS = ON) ON [PRIMARY]
) ON [PRIMARY]

ALTER VIEW [dbo].[F100Supervizori]
AS
SELECT        F10003, IdSuper, IdUser, USER_NO, TIME, IdAuto, NumeComplet
FROM            dbo.F100Supervizori2
UNION ALL
SELECT        f100.f10003, 3 AS idsuper, 2 AS iduser, NULL AS user_no, NULL AS time, 1000000 + CONVERT(integer, ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY f100.f10003)) IdAuto, 
f10008 + ' ' + f10009 NumeComplet
FROM            f100
WHERE        F10025 IN (0, 999)
UNION ALL
SELECT A.F10003, 0 AS IdSuper, B.F70102 AS IdUser, NULL AS USER_NO, NULL AS TIME, 10000000 + CONVERT(integer, ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY A.F10003)) IdAuto, A.F10008 + ' ' + A.F10009
FROM F100 A
INNER JOIN USERS B ON A.F10003=B.F10003

GO

CREATE VIEW [dbo].[RapoarteGrupuriUtilizatori]
AS
SELECT DISTINCT A.Id AS IdRaport, C.IdUser, D.ExtensiiPermise
FROM Rap_Rapoarte A
INNER JOIN relGrupRaport AS B ON A.Id=B.IdRaport 
INNER JOIN relGrupUser AS C ON B.IdGrup = C.IdGrup
INNER JOIN tblGrupUsers D ON D.Id=C.IdGrup
UNION
SELECT DISTINCT A.DynReportId AS IdRaport, C.IdUser, D.ExtensiiPermise
FROM DynReports A
INNER JOIN relGrupRaport AS B ON A.DynReportId=B.IdRaport 
INNER JOIN relGrupUser AS C ON B.IdGrup = C.IdGrup
INNER JOIN tblGrupUsers D ON D.Id=C.IdGrup

GO

----------------   2018.10.23


ALTER FUNCTION [dbo].[DamiNorma] (@f10003 int, @dt DATE) 
RETURNs table AS 
return 

                SELECT Norma = COALESCE(
                CASE WHEN @dt >= (SELECT dateadd(d,-1,dateadd(m,1,CONVERT(nvarchar(4),F01011) + '-' + CONVERT(nvarchar(4),F01012) + '-01')) FROM F010 WHERE F01002=A.F10002) THEN                            --in viitor
                (CASE WHEN E.F70407 IS NOT NULL THEN E.F70407 ELSE A.F10043 END)
                ELSE                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       
                (CASE WHEN B.F70407 = -1 THEN C.F91043                                                           
                ELSE                                                                                                                                                                                       
                (CASE WHEN @dt < B.F70406 THEN C.F91043D     
                ELSE C.F91043 END) END)                                                                                                                               
                END,A.F10043)
                FROM F100 A
                LEFT JOIN (SELECT X.F70403, X.F70407, X.F70406, ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY X.F70403 ORDER BY X.F70406 DESC) AS NrCrt FROM F704 X WHERE X.F70404=6 AND  (SELECT dateadd(d,-1,dateadd(m,1,CONVERT(nvarchar(4),F01011) + '-' + CONVERT(nvarchar(4),F01012) + '-01')) FROM F010 WHERE F01002=(SELECT F10002 FROM F100 WHERE F10003=X.F70403)) <= X.F70406 AND X.F70406 <= @dt) E ON A.F10003=E.F70403 AND E.NrCrt=1
                LEFT JOIN (SELECT X.F70403, COALESCE(X.F70407,-1) AS F70407, X.F70406, ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY X.F70403 ORDER BY X.F70406 DESC) AS NrCrt FROM F704 X WHERE X.F70404=6 AND YEAR(X.F70406) = YEAR(@dt) AND MONTH(X.F70406) = MONTH(@dt)) B ON A.F10003=B.F70403 AND B.NrCrt=1
                
    LEFT JOIN (SELECT X.F91003, X.F91043, Y.F91043 AS F91043D FROM F910 X LEFT JOIN F910 Y ON X.F91003 = Y. F91003 WHERE
    X.YEAR=YEAR(@dt) AND X.MONTH=MONTH(@dt) AND
    Y.YEAR=YEAR(dateadd(m,-1,@dt)) AND Y.MONTH=MONTH(dateadd(m,-1,@dt))
    ) C ON A.F10003=C.F91003    
                                
                WHERE A.F10003=@f10003

GO





ALTER FUNCTION [dbo].[DamiDept] (@f10003 int, @dt DATE) 
RETURNs table AS 

RETURN

	SELECT Dept = COALESCE(
	CASE WHEN @dt >= (SELECT dateadd(d,-1,dateadd(m,1,CONVERT(nvarchar(4),F01011) + '-' + CONVERT(nvarchar(4),F01012) + '-01')) FROM F010 WHERE F01002=A.F10002) THEN		--in viitor
	(CASE WHEN E.F70417 IS NOT NULL THEN E.F70417 ELSE A.F10007 END)
	ELSE																	--in trecut
	(CASE WHEN B.F70417 = -1 THEN C.F91007				 --nu exista modificari in luna
	ELSE												 --exista modificari in luna
	(CASE WHEN @dt < B.F70406 THEN D.F91007     -- istoricul din luna precedenta
	ELSE C.F91007 END) END)								 -- istoricul din luna 
	END,A.F10007)
	FROM F100 A
	LEFT JOIN (SELECT X.F70403, X.F70417, X.F70406, ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY X.F70403 ORDER BY X.F70406 DESC) AS NrCrt FROM F704 X WHERE X.F70404=5 AND (SELECT  dateadd(d,-1,dateadd(m,1,CONVERT(nvarchar(4),F01011) + '-' + CONVERT(nvarchar(4),F01012) + '-01')) FROM F010 WHERE F01002=(SELECT F10002 FROM F100 WHERE F10003=X.F70403)) <= X.F70406 AND X.F70406 <= @dt) E ON A.F10003=E.F70403 AND E.NrCrt=1
	LEFT JOIN (SELECT X.F70403, COALESCE(X.F70417,-1) AS F70417, X.F70406, ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY X.F70403 ORDER BY X.F70406 DESC) AS NrCrt FROM F704 X WHERE X.F70404=5 AND YEAR(X.F70406) = YEAR(@dt) AND MONTH(X.F70406) = MONTH(@dt)) B ON A.F10003=B.F70403 AND B.NrCrt=1
	LEFT JOIN F910 C ON A.F10003=C.F91003 AND C.YEAR=YEAR(@dt) AND C.MONTH=MONTH(@dt)
	LEFT JOIN F910 D ON A.F10003=D.F91003 AND D.YEAR=YEAR(dateadd(m,-1,@dt)) AND D.MONTH=MONTH(dateadd(m,-1,@dt))
	WHERE A.F10003=@f10003

GO


ALTER FUNCTION [dbo].[DamiCC] (@f10003 int, @dt DATE) 
RETURNs table AS 
return 

	SELECT CC = COALESCE(
	CASE WHEN @dt >= (SELECT  dateadd(d,-1,dateadd(m,1,CONVERT(nvarchar(4),F01011) + '-' + CONVERT(nvarchar(4),F01012) + '-01')) FROM F010 WHERE F01002=A.F10002) THEN		--in viitor
	(CASE WHEN E.F70407 IS NOT NULL THEN E.F70407 ELSE A.F10053 END)
	ELSE																	--in trecut
	(CASE WHEN B.F70407 = -1 THEN C.F91053				 --nu exista modificari in luna
	ELSE												 --exista modificari in luna
	(CASE WHEN @dt < B.F70406 THEN D.F91053     -- istoricul din luna precedenta
	ELSE C.F91053 END) END)								 -- istoricul din luna 
	END,A.F10053)
	FROM F100 A
	LEFT JOIN (SELECT X.F70403, X.F70407, X.F70406, ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY X.F70403 ORDER BY X.F70406 DESC) AS NrCrt FROM F704 X WHERE X.F70404=14 AND  (SELECT  dateadd(d,-1,dateadd(m,1,CONVERT(nvarchar(4),F01011) + '-' + CONVERT(nvarchar(4),F01012) + '-01')) FROM F010 WHERE F01002=(SELECT F10002 FROM F100 WHERE F10003=X.F70403)) <= X.F70406 AND X.F70406 <= @dt) E ON A.F10003=E.F70403 AND E.NrCrt=1
	LEFT JOIN (SELECT X.F70403, COALESCE(X.F70407,-1) AS F70407, X.F70406, ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY X.F70403 ORDER BY X.F70406 DESC) AS NrCrt FROM F704 X WHERE X.F70404=14 AND YEAR(X.F70406) = YEAR(@dt) AND MONTH(X.F70406) = MONTH(@dt)) B ON A.F10003=B.F70403 AND B.NrCrt=1
	LEFT JOIN F910 C ON A.F10003=C.F91003 AND C.YEAR=YEAR(@dt) AND C.MONTH=MONTH(@dt)
	LEFT JOIN F910 D ON A.F10003=D.F91003 AND D.YEAR=YEAR(dateadd(m,-1,@dt)) AND D.MONTH=MONTH(dateadd(m,-1,@dt))
	WHERE A.F10003=@f10003

GO


ALTER FUNCTION [dbo].[DamiDataPlecare] (@f10003 int, @dt DATE) 
RETURNs table AS 
return 

	SELECT DataPlecare = COALESCE(
	CASE WHEN @dt >= (SELECT dateadd(d,-1,dateadd(m,1,CONVERT(nvarchar(4),F01011) + '-' + CONVERT(nvarchar(4),F01012) + '-01')) FROM F010 WHERE F01002=A.F10002) THEN                            --in viitor
	(CASE WHEN E.F70406 IS NOT NULL THEN dateadd(d,-1,E.F70406) ELSE A.F10023 END)
	ELSE                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       
	(CASE WHEN B.F70407 = -1 THEN C.F91023                                                           
	ELSE                                                                                                                                                                                       
	(CASE WHEN @dt < B.F70406 THEN C.F91023D     
	ELSE C.F91023 END) END)                                                                                                                               
	END,A.F10023)
	FROM F100 A
	LEFT JOIN (SELECT X.F70403, X.F70407, X.F70406, ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY X.F70403 ORDER BY X.F70406 DESC) AS NrCrt FROM F704 X WHERE X.F70404=4 AND  (SELECT dateadd(d,-1,dateadd(m,1,CONVERT(nvarchar(4),F01011) + '-' + CONVERT(nvarchar(4),F01012) + '-01')) FROM F010 WHERE F01002=(SELECT F10002 FROM F100 WHERE F10003=X.F70403)) <= X.F70406 AND X.F70406 <= @dt) E ON A.F10003=E.F70403 AND E.NrCrt=1
	LEFT JOIN (SELECT X.F70403, COALESCE(X.F70407,-1) AS F70407, X.F70406, ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY X.F70403 ORDER BY X.F70406 DESC) AS NrCrt FROM F704 X WHERE X.F70404=4 AND YEAR(X.F70406) = YEAR(@dt) AND MONTH(X.F70406) = MONTH(@dt)) B ON A.F10003=B.F70403 AND B.NrCrt=1
	LEFT JOIN (SELECT X.F91003, X.F91023, Y.F91023 AS F91023D FROM F910 X LEFT JOIN F910 Y ON X.F91003 = Y.F91003 WHERE
	X.YEAR=YEAR(@dt) AND X.MONTH=MONTH(@dt) AND
	Y.YEAR=YEAR(dateadd(m,-1,@dt)) AND Y.MONTH=MONTH(dateadd(m,-1,@dt))
	) C ON A.F10003=C.F91003
	WHERE A.F10003=@f10003
GO

CREATE FUNCTION [dbo].[DamiNorma_Job] (@f10003 int, @dt DATE)
RETURNs table AS

return

	SELECT rez = COALESCE(
	CASE WHEN @dt >= (SELECT dateadd(d,-1,dateadd(m,1,CONVERT(nvarchar(4),F01011) + '-' + CONVERT(nvarchar(4),F01012) + '-01')) FROM F010 WHERE F01002 = A.F10002) THEN                            --in viitor
	(CASE WHEN E.F70407 IS NOT NULL THEN E.F70407 ELSE A.F10043 END)
	ELSE                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       
	(CASE WHEN B.F70407 = -1 THEN C.F91043                                                          
	ELSE                                                                                                                                                                                       
	(CASE WHEN @dt < B.F70406 THEN C.F91043D    
	ELSE C.F91043 END) END)                                                                                                                              
	END,A.F10043)
	FROM F100 A
	LEFT JOIN (SELECT X.F70403, X.F70407, X.F70406, ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY X.F70403 ORDER BY X.F70406 DESC) AS NrCrt FROM F704 X WHERE X.F70404=6 AND  (SELECT dateadd(d,-1,dateadd(m,1,CONVERT(nvarchar(4),F01011) + '-' + CONVERT(nvarchar(4),F01012) + '-01')) FROM F010 WHERE F01002 = X.F70402) <= X.F70406 AND X.F70406 <= @dt) E ON A.F10003=E.F70403 AND E.NrCrt=1
	LEFT JOIN (SELECT X.F70403, COALESCE(X.F70407,-1) AS F70407, X.F70406, ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY X.F70403 ORDER BY X.F70406 DESC) AS NrCrt FROM F704 X WHERE X.F70404=6 AND YEAR(X.F70406) = YEAR(@dt) AND MONTH(X.F70406) = MONTH(@dt)) B ON A.F10003=B.F70403 AND B.NrCrt=1
	LEFT JOIN (SELECT X.F91003, X.F91043, Y.F91043 AS F91043D FROM F910 X LEFT JOIN F910 Y ON X.F91003 = Y. F91003 WHERE
	X.YEAR=YEAR(@dt) AND X.MONTH=MONTH(@dt) AND
	Y.YEAR=YEAR(dateadd(m,-1,@dt)) AND Y.MONTH=MONTH(dateadd(m,-1,@dt))
	) C ON A.F10003=C.F91003   
	WHERE A.F10003=@f10003

GO



CREATE FUNCTION [dbo].[DamiDept_Job] (@f10003 int, @dt DATE)
RETURNs table AS

RETURN

	SELECT rez = COALESCE(
	CASE WHEN @dt >= (SELECT dateadd(d,-1,dateadd(m,1,CONVERT(nvarchar(4),F01011) + '-' + CONVERT(nvarchar(4),F01012) + '-01')) FROM F010 WHERE F01002 = A.F10002) THEN            --in viitor
	(CASE WHEN E.F70417 IS NOT NULL THEN E.F70417 ELSE A.F10007 END)
	ELSE                                                                                                                --in trecut
	(CASE WHEN B.F70417 = -1 THEN C.F91007                        --nu exista modificari in luna
	ELSE                                                                              --exista modificari in luna
	(CASE WHEN @dt < B.F70406 THEN C.F91007D     -- istoricul din luna precedenta
	ELSE C.F91007 END) END)                                                    -- istoricul din luna
	END,A.F10007)
	FROM F100 A
	LEFT JOIN (SELECT X.F70403, X.F70417, X.F70406, ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY X.F70403 ORDER BY X.F70406 DESC) AS NrCrt FROM F704 X WHERE X.F70404=5 AND (SELECT  dateadd(d,-1,dateadd(m,1,CONVERT(nvarchar(4),F01011) + '-' + CONVERT(nvarchar(4),F01012) + '-01')) FROM F010 WHERE F01002 = X.F70402) <= X.F70406 AND X.F70406 <= @dt) E ON A.F10003=E.F70403 AND E.NrCrt=1
	LEFT JOIN (SELECT X.F70403, COALESCE(X.F70417,-1) AS F70417, X.F70406, ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY X.F70403 ORDER BY X.F70406 DESC) AS NrCrt FROM F704 X WHERE X.F70404=5 AND YEAR(X.F70406) = YEAR(@dt) AND MONTH(X.F70406) = MONTH(@dt)) B ON A.F10003=B.F70403 AND B.NrCrt=1
	LEFT JOIN (SELECT X.F91003, X.F91007, Y.F91007 AS F91007D FROM F910 X LEFT JOIN F910 Y ON X.F91003 = Y. F91003 WHERE
	X.YEAR=YEAR(@dt) AND X.MONTH=MONTH(@dt) AND
	Y.YEAR=YEAR(dateadd(m,-1,@dt)) AND Y.MONTH=MONTH(dateadd(m,-1,@dt))
	) C ON A.F10003=C.F91003 
	WHERE A.F10003=@f10003

GO

CREATE FUNCTION [dbo].[DamiCC_Job] (@f10003 int, @dt DATE)
RETURNs table AS

RETURN

	SELECT rez = COALESCE(
	CASE WHEN @dt >= (SELECT  dateadd(d,-1,dateadd(m,1,CONVERT(nvarchar(4),F01011) + '-' + CONVERT(nvarchar(4),F01012) + '-01')) FROM F010) THEN		--in viitor
	(CASE WHEN E.F70407 IS NOT NULL THEN E.F70407 ELSE A.F10053 END)
	ELSE																	--in trecut
	(CASE WHEN B.F70407 = -1 THEN C.F91053				 --nu exista modificari in luna
	ELSE												 --exista modificari in luna
	(CASE WHEN @dt < B.F70406 THEN D.F91053     -- istoricul din luna precedenta
	ELSE C.F91053 END) END)								 -- istoricul din luna 
	END,A.F10053)
	FROM F100 A
	LEFT JOIN (SELECT X.F70403, X.F70407, X.F70406, ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY X.F70403 ORDER BY X.F70406 DESC) AS NrCrt FROM F704 X WHERE X.F70404=14 AND  (SELECT  dateadd(d,-1,dateadd(m,1,CONVERT(nvarchar(4),F01011) + '-' + CONVERT(nvarchar(4),F01012) + '-01')) FROM F010) <= X.F70406 AND X.F70406 <= @dt) E ON A.F10003=E.F70403 AND E.NrCrt=1
	LEFT JOIN (SELECT X.F70403, COALESCE(X.F70407,-1) AS F70407, X.F70406, ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY X.F70403 ORDER BY X.F70406 DESC) AS NrCrt FROM F704 X WHERE X.F70404=14 AND YEAR(X.F70406) = YEAR(@dt) AND MONTH(X.F70406) = MONTH(@dt)) B ON A.F10003=B.F70403 AND B.NrCrt=1
	LEFT JOIN F910 C ON A.F10003=C.F91003 AND C.YEAR=YEAR(@dt) AND C.MONTH=MONTH(@dt)
	LEFT JOIN F910 D ON A.F10003=D.F91003 AND D.YEAR=YEAR(dateadd(m,-1,@dt)) AND D.MONTH=MONTH(dateadd(m,-1,@dt))
	WHERE A.F10003=@f10003

GO

CREATE FUNCTION [dbo].[DamiDataPlecare_Job] (@f10003 int, @dt DATE)
RETURNs table AS

RETURN

	SELECT rez = COALESCE(
	CASE WHEN @dt >= (SELECT dateadd(d,-1,dateadd(m,1,CONVERT(nvarchar(4),F01011) + '-' + CONVERT(nvarchar(4),F01012) + '-01')) FROM F010) THEN                            --in viitor
	(CASE WHEN E.F70406 IS NOT NULL THEN dateadd(d,-1,E.F70406) ELSE A.F10023 END)
	ELSE                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       
	(CASE WHEN B.F70407 = -1 THEN C.F91023                                                           
	ELSE                                                                                                                                                                                       
	(CASE WHEN @dt < B.F70406 THEN C.F91023D     
	ELSE C.F91023 END) END)                                                                                                                               
	END,A.F10023)
	FROM F100 A
	LEFT JOIN (SELECT X.F70403, X.F70407, X.F70406, ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY X.F70403 ORDER BY X.F70406 DESC) AS NrCrt FROM F704 X WHERE X.F70404=4 AND  (SELECT dateadd(d,-1,dateadd(m,1,CONVERT(nvarchar(4),F01011) + '-' + CONVERT(nvarchar(4),F01012) + '-01')) FROM F010) <= X.F70406 AND X.F70406 <= @dt) E ON A.F10003=E.F70403 AND E.NrCrt=1
	LEFT JOIN (SELECT X.F70403, COALESCE(X.F70407,-1) AS F70407, X.F70406, ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY X.F70403 ORDER BY X.F70406 DESC) AS NrCrt FROM F704 X WHERE X.F70404=4 AND YEAR(X.F70406) = YEAR(@dt) AND MONTH(X.F70406) = MONTH(@dt)) B ON A.F10003=B.F70403 AND B.NrCrt=1
	LEFT JOIN (SELECT X.F91003, X.F91023, Y.F91023 AS F91023D FROM F910 X LEFT JOIN F910 Y ON X.F91003 = Y.F91003 WHERE
	X.YEAR=YEAR(@dt) AND X.MONTH=MONTH(@dt) AND
	Y.YEAR=YEAR(dateadd(m,-1,@dt)) AND Y.MONTH=MONTH(dateadd(m,-1,@dt))
	) C ON A.F10003=C.F91003                   
	WHERE A.F10003=@f10003

GO

CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[Create_tabele_Dami] 
AS
BEGIN
	SET NOCOUNT ON;

	delete from DamiNorma_Table where dt>= (select DATEFROMPARTS(f01011, f01012, 1) from f010 where f010.F01002 =DamiNorma_Table.f01002 );

	insert into DamiNorma_Table (f01002,f10003,dt,norma)
	select f010.F01002, f100.f10003,  tblzile."Zi", dn.rez
	from f010 join f100 on f010.f01002 = f100.f10002
	join tblzile on  tblzile.zi between DATEFROMPARTS(f01011, f01012, 1) and dateadd("d",-1,dateadd("m",2, DATEFROMPARTS(f01011, f01012, 1)))
	and tblzile.zi between f100.f10022 and f100.f10023
	OUTER APPLY dbo.DamiNorma_Job(f100.F10003, tblzile."Zi") dn;

	delete from DamiDept_Table where dt>= (select DATEFROMPARTS(f01011, f01012, 1) from f010 where f010.F01002 =DamiDept_Table.f01002 );

	insert into DamiDept_Table (f01002,f10003,dt,dept)
	select f010.F01002, f100.f10003,  tblzile."Zi", dn.rez
	from f010 join f100 on f010.f01002 = f100.f10002
	join tblzile on  tblzile.zi between DATEFROMPARTS(f01011, f01012, 1) and dateadd("d",-1,dateadd("m",2, DATEFROMPARTS(f01011, f01012, 1)))
	and tblzile.zi between f100.f10022 and f100.f10023
	OUTER APPLY dbo.DamiDept_Job(f100.F10003, tblzile."Zi") dn;
	
	delete from DamiCC_Table where dt>= (select DATEFROMPARTS(f01011, f01012, 1) from f010 where f010.F01002 =DamiCC_Table.f01002 );

	insert into DamiCC_Table (f01002,f10003,dt,CC)
	select f010.F01002, f100.f10003,  tblzile."Zi", dn.rez
	from f010 join f100 on f010.f01002 = f100.f10002
	join tblzile on  tblzile.zi between DATEFROMPARTS(f01011, f01012, 1) and dateadd("d",-1,dateadd("m",2, DATEFROMPARTS(f01011, f01012, 1)))
	and tblzile.zi between f100.f10022 and f100.f10023
	OUTER APPLY dbo.DamiCC_Job(f100.F10003, tblzile."Zi") dn;
	
	delete from DamiDataPlecare_Table where dt>= (select DATEFROMPARTS(f01011, f01012, 1) from f010 where f010.F01002 =DamiDataPlecare_Table.f01002 );

	insert into DamiDataPlecare_Table (f01002,f10003,dt,DataPlecare)
	select f010.F01002, f100.f10003,  tblzile."Zi", dn.rez
	from f010 join f100 on f010.f01002 = f100.f10002
	join tblzile on  tblzile.zi between DATEFROMPARTS(f01011, f01012, 1) and dateadd("d",-1,dateadd("m",2, DATEFROMPARTS(f01011, f01012, 1)))
	and tblzile.zi between f100.f10022 and f100.f10023
	OUTER APPLY dbo.DamiDataPlecare_Job(f100.F10003, tblzile."Zi") dn;
END

GO

(
	[Camp] ASC
)WITH (PAD_INDEX = OFF, STATISTICS_NORECOMPUTE = OFF, IGNORE_DUP_KEY = OFF, ALLOW_ROW_LOCKS = ON, ALLOW_PAGE_LOCKS = ON) ON [PRIMARY]
) ON [PRIMARY]

CREATE VIEW [dbo].[Org_NrPosturi]
AS
with cteRecurs(AncestorId,Id,Denumire,IdSuperior)
as
(
    Select Id,Id,Denumire,IdSuperior
      from Org_Posturi
    union all
    Select cteRecurs.AncestorId,Org_Posturi.Id,Org_Posturi.Denumire,Org_Posturi.IdSuperior
      from cteRecurs,
           Org_Posturi
     where Org_Posturi.IdSuperior = cteRecurs.Id
)

select AncestorId AS IdPost,count(*)-1 AS NrTotal From cteRecurs
group by AncestorId
GO

insert into tblParametrii(Nume, Valoare, Explicatie, IdModul)

create VIEW [dbo].[DataBlocareBonusuri]
AS
select 
(SELECT      DATEFROMPARTS (CONVERT(varchar(10), CASE substring(valoare, 1, 1)
								WHEN  'F' THEN F01011 
								WHEN  'C' THEN year(getdate()) 
								WHEN  'D' THEN CASE WHEN month(getdate()) + 1 = 13 THEN  year(getdate())+1 ELSE year(getdate())  END 
								WHEN  'G' THEN CASE WHEN F01012 + 1 = 13 THEN F01011+1 ELSE F01011  END 
								ELSE F01011 END ) ,				
 CONVERT(varchar(10), CASE substring(valoare, 1, 1)
								WHEN  'F' THEN F01012 
								WHEN  'C' THEN month(getdate()) 
								WHEN  'D' THEN CASE WHEN month(getdate()) + 1 = 13 THEN 1 ELSE month(getdate()) + 1 END 
								WHEN  'G' THEN CASE WHEN F01012 + 1 = 13 THEN 1 ELSE F01012 + 1 END 
								ELSE F01012 END ) ,
						  SUBSTRING(dbo.tblParametrii.Valoare, 2, 2) ) as ZiBlocareAvans
FROM            dbo.tblParametrii CROSS JOIN dbo.F010                        
WHERE        (dbo.tblParametrii.Nume = 'ZiBlocareIntroducerePrimaAvans') ) ZiBlocareAvans,
(SELECT      DATEFROMPARTS (CONVERT(varchar(10), CASE substring(valoare, 1, 1)
								WHEN  'F' THEN F01011 
								WHEN  'C' THEN year(getdate()) 
								WHEN  'D' THEN CASE WHEN month(getdate()) + 1 = 13 THEN  year(getdate())+1 ELSE year(getdate())  END 
								WHEN  'G' THEN CASE WHEN F01012 + 1 = 13 THEN F01011+1 ELSE F01011  END 
								ELSE F01011 END ) ,				
 CONVERT(varchar(10), CASE substring(valoare, 1, 1)
								WHEN  'F' THEN F01012 
								WHEN  'C' THEN month(getdate()) 
								WHEN  'D' THEN CASE WHEN month(getdate()) + 1 = 13 THEN 1 ELSE month(getdate()) + 1 END 
								WHEN  'G' THEN CASE WHEN F01012 + 1 = 13 THEN 1 ELSE F01012 + 1 END 
								ELSE F01012 END ) ,
						  SUBSTRING(dbo.tblParametrii.Valoare, 2, 2) ) as ZiBlocareLichidare
FROM            dbo.tblParametrii CROSS JOIN dbo.F010                        
WHERE        (dbo.tblParametrii.Nume = 'ZiBlocareIntroducerePrimaLichidare') ) ZiBlocareLichidare

CREATE TABLE [dbo].[Eval_DrepturiTab](
	[IdQuiz] [int] NOT NULL,
	[Pozitie] [int] NOT NULL,
	[TabIndex] [int] NOT NULL,
	[Blocat] [int] NULL,
	[USER_NO] [int] NULL,
	[TIME] [datetime] NULL,
	[IdAuto] [int] IDENTITY(1,1) NOT NULL,
 CONSTRAINT [PK_Eval_DrepturiTab] PRIMARY KEY CLUSTERED 
(
	[IdQuiz] ASC,
	[Pozitie] ASC,
	[TabIndex] ASC
)WITH (PAD_INDEX = OFF, STATISTICS_NORECOMPUTE = OFF, IGNORE_DUP_KEY = OFF, ALLOW_ROW_LOCKS = ON, ALLOW_PAGE_LOCKS = ON) ON [PRIMARY]
) ON [PRIMARY]
GO

----  2.2.029  ----
CREATE FUNCTION InitialCap(@String VARCHAR(8000))
                  RETURNS VARCHAR(8000)
                 AS
BEGIN 

                   DECLARE @Position INT;

	SELECT @String   = STUFF(LOWER(@String),1,1,UPPER(LEFT(@String,1))) COLLATE Latin1_General_Bin,
                    @Position = PATINDEX('%[^A-Za-z''][a-z]%',@String COLLATE Latin1_General_Bin);

                    WHILE @Position > 0
                    SELECT @String   = STUFF(@String,@Position,2,UPPER(SUBSTRING(@String,@Position,2))) COLLATE Latin1_General_Bin,
                    @Position = PATINDEX('%[^A-Za-z''][a-z]%',@String COLLATE Latin1_General_Bin);

                     RETURN @String;
END ;

ALTER VIEW [dbo].[viewEvaluare360]
AS
select b.IdQuiz, b.F10003,  c.descriere AS Descriere, b.Obiectiv as PuncteForte, b.Activitate as ZoneDeDezvoltare
from Eval_QuizIntrebari a
inner join Eval_QuizIntrebari c on a.parinte = c.Id and c.Descriere = 'Vitality'
inner join Eval_ObiIndividualeTemp b on a.idquiz=b.IdQuiz and a.id=b.IdLinieQuiz
where a.idquiz in (24, 26, 28, 29)
union
select b.IdQuiz, b.F10003,  c.descriere AS Descriere, b.Obiectiv as PuncteForte, b.Activitate as ZoneDeDezvoltare
from Eval_QuizIntrebari a
inner join Eval_QuizIntrebari c on a.parinte = c.Id and c.Descriere = 'Effectiveness'
inner join Eval_ObiIndividualeTemp b on a.idquiz=b.IdQuiz and a.id=b.IdLinieQuiz
where a.idquiz in (24, 26, 28, 29)
union
select b.IdQuiz, b.F10003,  c.descriere AS Descriere, b.Obiectiv as PuncteForte, b.Activitate as ZoneDeDezvoltare
from Eval_QuizIntrebari a
inner join Eval_QuizIntrebari c on a.parinte = c.Id and c.Descriere = 'Creativity'
inner join Eval_ObiIndividualeTemp b on a.idquiz=b.IdQuiz and a.id=b.IdLinieQuiz
where a.idquiz in (24, 26, 28, 29)
union
select b.IdQuiz, b.F10003,  c.descriere AS Descriere, b.Obiectiv as PuncteForte, b.Activitate as ZoneDeDezvoltare
from Eval_QuizIntrebari a
inner join Eval_QuizIntrebari c on a.parinte = c.Id and c.Descriere = 'Common Sense'
inner join Eval_ObiIndividualeTemp b on a.idquiz=b.IdQuiz and a.id=b.IdLinieQuiz
where a.idquiz in (24, 26, 28, 29)
union
select b.IdQuiz, b.F10003,  c.descriere AS Descriere, b.Obiectiv as PuncteForte, b.Activitate as ZoneDeDezvoltare
from Eval_QuizIntrebari a
inner join Eval_QuizIntrebari c on a.parinte = c.Id and c.Descriere = 'Relationships'
inner join Eval_ObiIndividualeTemp b on a.idquiz=b.IdQuiz and a.id=b.IdLinieQuiz
where a.idquiz in (24, 26, 28, 29)
UNION
SELECT IdQuiz, F10003, 'Others' AS Descriere, PuncteForte, '' AS ZoneDeDezvoltare FROM (
SELECT IdQuiz, F10003, ISNULL(Super1,'') AS PuncteForte FROM Eval_RaspunsLinii WHERE Id IN (385,421,459,506,717,874,911,948)
UNION
SELECT IdQuiz, F10003, ISNULL(Super2,'') AS PuncteForte FROM Eval_RaspunsLinii WHERE Id IN (385,421,459,506,717,874,911,948)
UNION
SELECT IdQuiz, F10003, ISNULL(Super3,'') AS PuncteForte FROM Eval_RaspunsLinii WHERE Id IN (385,421,459,506,717,874,911,948)
UNION
SELECT IdQuiz, F10003, ISNULL(Super4,'') AS PuncteForte FROM Eval_RaspunsLinii WHERE Id IN (385,421,459,506,717,874,911,948)
UNION
SELECT IdQuiz, F10003, ISNULL(Super5,'') AS PuncteForte FROM Eval_RaspunsLinii WHERE Id IN (385,421,459,506,717,874,911,948)
UNION
SELECT IdQuiz, F10003, ISNULL(Super6,'') AS PuncteForte FROM Eval_RaspunsLinii WHERE Id IN (385,421,459,506,717,874,911,948)
UNION
SELECT IdQuiz, F10003, ISNULL(Super7,'') AS PuncteForte FROM Eval_RaspunsLinii WHERE Id IN (385,421,459,506,717,874,911,948)
UNION
SELECT IdQuiz, F10003, ISNULL(Super8,'') AS PuncteForte FROM Eval_RaspunsLinii WHERE Id IN (385,421,459,506,717,874,911,948)
UNION
SELECT IdQuiz, F10003, ISNULL(Super9,'') AS PuncteForte FROM Eval_RaspunsLinii WHERE Id IN (385,421,459,506,717,874,911,948)
UNION

UNION
SELECT IdQuiz, F10003, ISNULL(Super20,'') AS PuncteForte FROM Eval_RaspunsLinii WHERE Id IN (385,421,459,506,717,874,911,948)
) X WHERE PuncteForte <> ''

GO

ALTER VIEW [dbo].[viewEvaluare360]
AS
select b.IdQuiz, b.F10003,  c.descriere AS Descriere, b.Obiectiv as PuncteForte, b.Activitate as ZoneDeDezvoltare, D.Anul AS Perioada
from Eval_QuizIntrebari a
inner join Eval_QuizIntrebari c on a.parinte = c.Id and c.Descriere = 'Vitality'
inner join Eval_ObiIndividualeTemp b on a.idquiz=b.IdQuiz and a.id=b.IdLinieQuiz
INNER JOIN Eval_Quiz D ON A.IdQuiz = D.Id
where COALESCE(D.CategorieQuiz,0)=1
union
select b.IdQuiz, b.F10003,  c.descriere AS Descriere, b.Obiectiv as PuncteForte, b.Activitate as ZoneDeDezvoltare, D.Anul AS Perioada
from Eval_QuizIntrebari a
inner join Eval_QuizIntrebari c on a.parinte = c.Id and c.Descriere = 'Effectiveness'
inner join Eval_ObiIndividualeTemp b on a.idquiz=b.IdQuiz and a.id=b.IdLinieQuiz
INNER JOIN Eval_Quiz D ON A.IdQuiz = D.Id
where COALESCE(D.CategorieQuiz,0)=1
union
select b.IdQuiz, b.F10003,  c.descriere AS Descriere, b.Obiectiv as PuncteForte, b.Activitate as ZoneDeDezvoltare, D.Anul AS Perioada
from Eval_QuizIntrebari a
inner join Eval_QuizIntrebari c on a.parinte = c.Id and c.Descriere = 'Creativity'
inner join Eval_ObiIndividualeTemp b on a.idquiz=b.IdQuiz and a.id=b.IdLinieQuiz
INNER JOIN Eval_Quiz D ON A.IdQuiz = D.Id
where COALESCE(D.CategorieQuiz,0)=1
union
select b.IdQuiz, b.F10003,  c.descriere AS Descriere, b.Obiectiv as PuncteForte, b.Activitate as ZoneDeDezvoltare, D.Anul AS Perioada
from Eval_QuizIntrebari a
inner join Eval_QuizIntrebari c on a.parinte = c.Id and c.Descriere = 'Common Sense'
inner join Eval_ObiIndividualeTemp b on a.idquiz=b.IdQuiz and a.id=b.IdLinieQuiz
INNER JOIN Eval_Quiz D ON A.IdQuiz = D.Id
where COALESCE(D.CategorieQuiz,0)=1
union
select b.IdQuiz, b.F10003,  c.descriere AS Descriere, b.Obiectiv as PuncteForte, b.Activitate as ZoneDeDezvoltare, D.Anul AS Perioada
from Eval_QuizIntrebari a
inner join Eval_QuizIntrebari c on a.parinte = c.Id and c.Descriere = 'Relationships'
inner join Eval_ObiIndividualeTemp b on a.idquiz=b.IdQuiz and a.id=b.IdLinieQuiz
INNER JOIN Eval_Quiz D ON A.IdQuiz = D.Id
where COALESCE(D.CategorieQuiz,0)=1
UNION
SELECT IdQuiz, F10003, 'Others' AS Descriere, PuncteForte, '' AS ZoneDeDezvoltare, D.Anul AS Perioada 
FROM (
SELECT IdQuiz, F10003, ISNULL(Super1,'') AS PuncteForte FROM Eval_RaspunsLinii WHERE Id IN (385,421,459,506,717,874,911,948)
UNION
SELECT IdQuiz, F10003, ISNULL(Super2,'') AS PuncteForte FROM Eval_RaspunsLinii WHERE Id IN (385,421,459,506,717,874,911,948)
UNION
SELECT IdQuiz, F10003, ISNULL(Super3,'') AS PuncteForte FROM Eval_RaspunsLinii WHERE Id IN (385,421,459,506,717,874,911,948)
UNION
SELECT IdQuiz, F10003, ISNULL(Super4,'') AS PuncteForte FROM Eval_RaspunsLinii WHERE Id IN (385,421,459,506,717,874,911,948)
UNION
SELECT IdQuiz, F10003, ISNULL(Super5,'') AS PuncteForte FROM Eval_RaspunsLinii WHERE Id IN (385,421,459,506,717,874,911,948)
UNION
SELECT IdQuiz, F10003, ISNULL(Super6,'') AS PuncteForte FROM Eval_RaspunsLinii WHERE Id IN (385,421,459,506,717,874,911,948)
UNION
SELECT IdQuiz, F10003, ISNULL(Super7,'') AS PuncteForte FROM Eval_RaspunsLinii WHERE Id IN (385,421,459,506,717,874,911,948)
UNION
SELECT IdQuiz, F10003, ISNULL(Super8,'') AS PuncteForte FROM Eval_RaspunsLinii WHERE Id IN (385,421,459,506,717,874,911,948)
UNION
SELECT IdQuiz, F10003, ISNULL(Super9,'') AS PuncteForte FROM Eval_RaspunsLinii WHERE Id IN (385,421,459,506,717,874,911,948)
UNION
SELECT IdQuiz, F10003, ISNULL(Super10,'') AS PuncteForte FROM Eval_RaspunsLinii WHERE Id IN (385,421,459,506,717,874,911,948)
UNION
SELECT IdQuiz, F10003, ISNULL(Super11,'') AS PuncteForte FROM Eval_RaspunsLinii WHERE Id IN (385,421,459,506,717,874,911,948)
UNION
SELECT IdQuiz, F10003, ISNULL(Super12,'') AS PuncteForte FROM Eval_RaspunsLinii WHERE Id IN (385,421,459,506,717,874,911,948)
UNION
SELECT IdQuiz, F10003, ISNULL(Super13,'') AS PuncteForte FROM Eval_RaspunsLinii WHERE Id IN (385,421,459,506,717,874,911,948)
UNION
SELECT IdQuiz, F10003, ISNULL(Super14,'') AS PuncteForte FROM Eval_RaspunsLinii WHERE Id IN (385,421,459,506,717,874,911,948)
UNION
SELECT IdQuiz, F10003, ISNULL(Super15,'') AS PuncteForte FROM Eval_RaspunsLinii WHERE Id IN (385,421,459,506,717,874,911,948)
UNION
SELECT IdQuiz, F10003, ISNULL(Super16,'') AS PuncteForte FROM Eval_RaspunsLinii WHERE Id IN (385,421,459,506,717,874,911,948)
UNION
SELECT IdQuiz, F10003, ISNULL(Super17,'') AS PuncteForte FROM Eval_RaspunsLinii WHERE Id IN (385,421,459,506,717,874,911,948)
UNION
SELECT IdQuiz, F10003, ISNULL(Super18,'') AS PuncteForte FROM Eval_RaspunsLinii WHERE Id IN (385,421,459,506,717,874,911,948)
UNION
SELECT IdQuiz, F10003, ISNULL(Super19,'') AS PuncteForte FROM Eval_RaspunsLinii WHERE Id IN (385,421,459,506,717,874,911,948)
UNION
SELECT IdQuiz, F10003, ISNULL(Super20,'') AS PuncteForte FROM Eval_RaspunsLinii WHERE Id IN (385,421,459,506,717,874,911,948)
) X 
INNER JOIN Eval_Quiz D ON X.IdQuiz = D.Id
WHERE PuncteForte <> ''

GO

alter table tblGrupUsers add MeniuRestrans smallint
GO

alter VIEW [dbo].[RapoarteGrupuriUtilizatori]
AS
SELECT DISTINCT r.DynReportId AS IdRaport, gu.IdUser, gs.ExtensiiPermise, gs.MeniuRestrans
FROM DynReports AS r
INNER JOIN relGrupRaport AS gr ON r.DynReportId = gr.IdRaport 
INNER JOIN relGrupUser AS gu ON gr.IdGrup = gu.IdGrup
INNER JOIN tblGrupUsers AS gs ON gu.IdGrup = gs.Id
GO

CREATE TABLE [dbo].[DynReports](
	[DynReportId] [int] IDENTITY(1,1) NOT NULL,
	[Name] [nvarchar](50) NOT NULL,
	[Description] [nvarchar](250) NULL,
	[DynReportTypeId] [smallint] NOT NULL,
	[LayoutData] [varbinary](max) NULL,
	[RegUserId] [nvarchar](128) NULL,
	[UpdUserId] [nvarchar](128) NULL,
	[RegDate] [datetime] NOT NULL,
	[UpdDate] [datetime] NULL,
 CONSTRAINT [PK_DynReports] PRIMARY KEY CLUSTERED 
(
	[DynReportId] ASC
)WITH (PAD_INDEX = OFF, STATISTICS_NORECOMPUTE = OFF, IGNORE_DUP_KEY = OFF, ALLOW_ROW_LOCKS = ON, ALLOW_PAGE_LOCKS = ON) ON [PRIMARY]
) ON [PRIMARY] TEXTIMAGE_ON [PRIMARY]
GO

ALTER TABLE [dbo].[DynReports] ADD  CONSTRAINT [DF_DynReports_RegDate]  DEFAULT (getdate()) FOR [RegDate]
GO

ALTER TABLE [dbo].[DynReports]  WITH CHECK ADD  CONSTRAINT [FK_DynReports_DynReportTypes] FOREIGN KEY([DynReportTypeId])
REFERENCES [dbo].[DynReportTypes] ([DynReportTypeId])
GO

ALTER TABLE [dbo].[DynReports] CHECK CONSTRAINT [FK_DynReports_DynReportTypes]
GO



CREATE TABLE [dbo].[DynReportsUsers](
	[DynReportUserId] [int] IDENTITY(1,1) NOT NULL,
	[DynReportId] [int] NOT NULL,
	[Name] [nvarchar](50) NOT NULL,
	[Description] [nvarchar](250) NULL,
	[LayoutData] [varbinary](max) NULL,
	[RegUserId] [nvarchar](128) NULL,
	[UpdUserId] [nvarchar](128) NULL,
	[RegDate] [datetime] NOT NULL,
	[UpdDate] [datetime] NULL,
 CONSTRAINT [PK_DynReportsUsers] PRIMARY KEY CLUSTERED 
(
	[DynReportUserId] ASC
)WITH (PAD_INDEX = OFF, STATISTICS_NORECOMPUTE = OFF, IGNORE_DUP_KEY = OFF, ALLOW_ROW_LOCKS = ON, ALLOW_PAGE_LOCKS = ON) ON [PRIMARY]
) ON [PRIMARY] TEXTIMAGE_ON [PRIMARY]
GO

ALTER TABLE [dbo].[DynReportsUsers] ADD  CONSTRAINT [DF_DynReportsUsers_RegDate]  DEFAULT (getdate()) FOR [RegDate]
GO

ALTER TABLE [dbo].[DynReportsUsers]  WITH CHECK ADD  CONSTRAINT [FK_DynReportsUsers_DynReports] FOREIGN KEY([DynReportId])
REFERENCES [dbo].[DynReports] ([DynReportId])
ON DELETE CASCADE
GO

ALTER TABLE [dbo].[DynReportsUsers] CHECK CONSTRAINT [FK_DynReportsUsers_DynReports]
GO

DECLARE @SQL NVARCHAR(MAX) = N'';
SELECT @SQL += N'
ALTER TABLE ' + OBJECT_NAME(PARENT_OBJECT_ID) + ' DROP CONSTRAINT ' + OBJECT_NAME(OBJECT_ID) + ';' 
FROM SYS.OBJECTS
WHERE TYPE_DESC LIKE '%CONSTRAINT' AND OBJECT_NAME(PARENT_OBJECT_ID) = 'F100Supervizori2' and OBJECT_NAME(OBJECT_ID) like '%F100Super__Data%';
--PRINT @SQL
EXECUTE(@SQL)

IF COL_LENGTH('F003', 'F00310') IS NULL
BEGIN
    ALTER TABLE F003  ADD F00310 DATETIME NULL DEFAULT GETDATE();
	DECLARE @sql NVARCHAR(2048) = 'UPDATE F003 SET F00310 = ''1900-01-01''WHERE F00310 IS NULL;' ;
	EXEC sys.sp_executesql @query = @sql;
END;
GO

CREATE TABLE [dbo].[tblTichete_WebService](
	[IdAuto] [int] NOT NULL,
	[Companie] [nvarchar](250) NOT NULL,
	[Tichete] [nvarchar](250) NOT NULL,
	[NumeTichet] [nvarchar](250) NOT NULL,
	[Adresa] [int] NULL,
 CONSTRAINT [PK_tblTichete_WebService] PRIMARY KEY CLUSTERED 
(
	[IdAuto] ASC
)WITH (PAD_INDEX = OFF, STATISTICS_NORECOMPUTE = OFF, IGNORE_DUP_KEY = OFF, ALLOW_ROW_LOCKS = ON, ALLOW_PAGE_LOCKS = ON) ON [PRIMARY]
) ON [PRIMARY]

GO

CREATE TABLE [dbo].[tblTipAdresa_WebService](
	[TipAdresa] [int] NOT NULL,
	[IdAdresaWiz] [int] NOT NULL,
	[IdAdresaSodexo] [int] NULL,
	[Tichete] [nvarchar](150) NULL,
	[PersContact] [int] NULL,
	[USER_NO] [int] NULL,
	[TIME] [datetime] NULL,
 CONSTRAINT [PK_tblTipAdresa_WebService] PRIMARY KEY CLUSTERED 
(
	[TipAdresa] ASC,
	[IdAdresaWiz] ASC
)WITH (PAD_INDEX = OFF, STATISTICS_NORECOMPUTE = OFF, IGNORE_DUP_KEY = OFF, ALLOW_ROW_LOCKS = ON, ALLOW_PAGE_LOCKS = ON) ON [PRIMARY]
) ON [PRIMARY]

GO

CREATE TABLE [dbo].[Ptj_ProgrameOreNoapte](
	[IdProgram] [int] NOT NULL,
	[Rotunjire] [int] NULL,
	[OraInceput] [datetime] NULL,
	[OraSfarsit] [datetime] NULL,
	[ValMin] [datetime] NULL,
	[ValMax] [datetime] NULL,
	[ValFixa] [datetime] NULL,
	[Multiplicator] [numeric](22, 2) NULL,
	[Camp] [nvarchar](150) NULL,
	[IdAuto] [int] IDENTITY(1,1) NOT NULL,
	[USER_NO] [int] NULL,
	[TIME] [datetime] NULL,
 CONSTRAINT [Ptj_ProgrameOreNoapte_PK] PRIMARY KEY CLUSTERED 
(
	[IdAuto] ASC
)WITH (PAD_INDEX = OFF, STATISTICS_NORECOMPUTE = OFF, IGNORE_DUP_KEY = OFF, ALLOW_ROW_LOCKS = ON, ALLOW_PAGE_LOCKS = ON) ON [PRIMARY]
) ON [PRIMARY]
GO

ALTER TABLE [dbo].[Ptj_ProgrameOreNoapte] ADD  CONSTRAINT [DF_Ptj_ProgrameOreNoapte_TIME]  DEFAULT (getdate()) FOR [TIME]
GO

	[USER_NO] [int] NULL,
	[TIME] [datetime] NULL CONSTRAINT [DF__Admin_Evaluare_Time]  DEFAULT (getdate()),
	[IdAuto] [int] IDENTITY(1,1) NOT NULL,

(
	[IdAuto] ASC
)WITH (PAD_INDEX = OFF, STATISTICS_NORECOMPUTE = OFF, IGNORE_DUP_KEY = OFF, ALLOW_ROW_LOCKS = ON, ALLOW_PAGE_LOCKS = ON) ON [PRIMARY]
) ON [PRIMARY]

CREATE VIEW Cursuri_VIEW AS
select Marca,NumeComplet,IdTipCurs,IdDescriereCurs,NumeFurnizor,TemaCurs,Info,NrOre,DataCurs,Buget,PerioadaAmortizare,AutorizareExpirare,USER_NO,[TIME],IdAuto
from
Admin_Cursuri
WHERE 1<1

GO

CREATE VIEW Admin_Cursuri_VIEW as
select Marca,NumeComplet,IdTipCurs,IdDescriereCurs,NumeFurnizor,TemaCurs,Info,NrOre,DataCurs,Buget,PerioadaAmortizare,AutorizareExpirare,USER_NO,[TIME],IdAuto
from
Admin_Cursuri
UNION ALL
SELECT Marca,NumeComplet,IdTipCurs,IdDescriereCurs,NumeFurnizor,TemaCurs,Info,NrOre,DataCurs,Buget,PerioadaAmortizare,AutorizareExpirare,USER_NO,[TIME],IdAuto
from
Cursuri_VIEW

GO


INSERT INTO [Admin_TipCurs] (TipCurs) Select 'Intern' where not exists ( select 2 from [Admin_TipCurs]  where TipCurs='Intern')

INSERT INTO [Admin_TipCurs] (TipCurs) Select 'Extern' where not exists ( select 2 from [Admin_TipCurs]  where TipCurs='Extern')

INSERT INTO [Admin_TipCurs] (TipCurs) Select 'Online' where not exists ( select 2 from [Admin_TipCurs]  where TipCurs='Online')


INSERT INTO [Admin_DescrCurs] ([DescriereCurs]) Select 'Soft skills' where not exists ( select 2 from [Admin_DescrCurs]  where [DescriereCurs]='Soft skills')

INSERT INTO [Admin_DescrCurs] ([DescriereCurs]) Select 'Tehnic' where not exists ( select 2 from [Admin_DescrCurs]  where [DescriereCurs]='Tehnic')

GO

INSERT INTO MP_tblTaburi(Denumire,Pagina,ORDINE,"TIME")
SELECT 'Cursuri','Cursuri',(SELECT MAX(ORDINE)+1 FROM MP_tblTaburi),GETDATE() 

INSERT INTO MP_tblTaburi(Denumire,Pagina,ORDINE,"TIME")
SELECT 'Evaluare','Evaluare',(SELECT MAX(ORDINE)+1 FROM MP_tblTaburi),GETDATE() 

INSERT INTO MP_tblTaburi(Denumire,Pagina,ORDINE,"TIME")
SELECT 'Atestate','Atestate',(SELECT MAX(ORDINE)+1 FROM MP_tblTaburi),GETDATE() 

GO

BEGIN

DECLARE @AC_ID INT,@AC_NXT_ID INT,@AO_ID INT ,  @EXISTA_AO INT
DECLARE @DENUMIRE VARCHAR(500)
DECLARE @TAB TABLE ( DENUMIRE VARCHAR(500) )

INSERT INTO @TAB ( DENUMIRE ) VALUES ('Avertisment verbal') 
INSERT INTO @TAB ( DENUMIRE ) VALUES ('Avertisment scris') 
INSERT INTO @TAB ( DENUMIRE ) VALUES ('Reducerea salariului cu 5% - 1 luna') 
INSERT INTO @TAB ( DENUMIRE ) VALUES ('Reducerea salariului cu 5% - 2 luni') 
INSERT INTO @TAB ( DENUMIRE ) VALUES ('Reducerea salariului cu 5% - 3 luni') 
INSERT INTO @TAB ( DENUMIRE ) VALUES ('Reducerea salariului cu 10% - 3 luni') 
INSERT INTO @TAB ( DENUMIRE ) VALUES ('Reducerea salariului cu 10% - 3 luni') 
INSERT INTO @TAB ( DENUMIRE ) VALUES ('Reducerea salariului cu 10% - 3 luni') 
INSERT INTO @TAB ( DENUMIRE ) VALUES ('Desfacerea CIM') 

DECLARE X CURSOR FOR 
SELECT DENUMIRE FROM @TAB


SELECT @AC_NXT_ID = ( MAX(ID) + 1 ) FROM Admin_Categorii

SELECT @AC_ID = ISNULL((SELECT ID FROM Admin_Categorii WHERE Denumire = 'Cercetare disciplinara'),0)

IF @AC_ID = 0 
BEGIN
	INSERT INTO Admin_Categorii (IdArie,Denumire,Id,OrdineInPosturi)
	VALUES(7,'Cercetare disciplinara',@AC_NXT_ID,4)
END


OPEN X
FETCH NEXT FROM X INTO @DENUMIRE 
WHILE @@FETCH_STATUS = 0 
BEGIN

SELECT @EXISTA_AO = ISNULL((SELECT  1 FROM Admin_Obiecte WHERE IdCategorie = @AC_ID AND DENUMIRE = @DENUMIRE),0)

IF @EXISTA_AO = 0 
BEGIN

SELECT @AO_ID = MAX(ID) + 1  FROM Admin_Obiecte

INSERT INTO Admin_Obiecte (Id,IdCategorie,Denumire,ValoareEstimata)
VALUES (@AO_ID,@AC_ID,@DENUMIRE,NULL)  

END

FETCH NEXT FROM X INTO @DENUMIRE 
END

CLOSE X
DEALLOCATE X 

END

GO

DECLARE @SQL NVARCHAR(MAX) = N'';
SELECT @SQL += N'
ALTER TABLE ' + OBJECT_NAME(PARENT_OBJECT_ID) + ' DROP CONSTRAINT ' + OBJECT_NAME(OBJECT_ID) + ';' 
FROM SYS.OBJECTS
WHERE (TYPE_DESC LIKE '%CONSTRAINT' AND OBJECT_NAME(PARENT_OBJECT_ID) = 'F003' and OBJECT_NAME(OBJECT_ID) like '%F003__F003%')
OR (TYPE_DESC LIKE '%CONSTRAINT' AND OBJECT_NAME(PARENT_OBJECT_ID) = 'F004' and OBJECT_NAME(OBJECT_ID) like '%F004__F004%')
OR (TYPE_DESC LIKE '%CONSTRAINT' AND OBJECT_NAME(PARENT_OBJECT_ID) = 'F005' and OBJECT_NAME(OBJECT_ID) like '%F005__F005%')
OR (TYPE_DESC LIKE '%CONSTRAINT' AND OBJECT_NAME(PARENT_OBJECT_ID) = 'F006' and OBJECT_NAME(OBJECT_ID) like '%F006__F006%')
OR (TYPE_DESC LIKE '%CONSTRAINT' AND OBJECT_NAME(PARENT_OBJECT_ID) = 'F007' and OBJECT_NAME(OBJECT_ID) like '%F007__F007%')
OR (TYPE_DESC LIKE '%CONSTRAINT' AND OBJECT_NAME(PARENT_OBJECT_ID) = 'F008' and OBJECT_NAME(OBJECT_ID) like '%F008__F008%')
OR (TYPE_DESC LIKE '%CONSTRAINT' AND OBJECT_NAME(PARENT_OBJECT_ID) = 'F011' and OBJECT_NAME(OBJECT_ID) like '%F011__F011%')
OR (TYPE_DESC LIKE '%CONSTRAINT' AND OBJECT_NAME(PARENT_OBJECT_ID) = 'F013' and OBJECT_NAME(OBJECT_ID) like '%F013__F013%')
OR (TYPE_DESC LIKE '%CONSTRAINT' AND OBJECT_NAME(PARENT_OBJECT_ID) = 'F021' and OBJECT_NAME(OBJECT_ID) like '%F021__F021%')
OR (TYPE_DESC LIKE '%CONSTRAINT' AND OBJECT_NAME(PARENT_OBJECT_ID) = 'F025' and OBJECT_NAME(OBJECT_ID) like '%F025__F025%')
OR (TYPE_DESC LIKE '%CONSTRAINT' AND OBJECT_NAME(PARENT_OBJECT_ID) = 'F062' and OBJECT_NAME(OBJECT_ID) like '%F062__F062%')
OR (TYPE_DESC LIKE '%CONSTRAINT' AND OBJECT_NAME(PARENT_OBJECT_ID) = 'F080' and OBJECT_NAME(OBJECT_ID) like '%F080__F080%');
EXECUTE(@SQL)

CREATE VIEW viewCategoriePontaj
AS 
SELECT F10003, F72404 AS Denumire FROM (
SELECT F10003, F10061 AS Id FROM F100
UNION
SELECT F10003, F10062 AS Id FROM F100
) X 
INNER JOIN F724 B ON B.F72402=X.Id
GROUP BY X.F10003, B.F72404
GO

ALTER VIEW [dbo].[viewCategoriePontaj]
AS 
SELECT F10003, F72404 AS Denumire FROM (
SELECT F10003, F10061 AS Id FROM F100
) X 
INNER JOIN F724 B ON B.F72402=X.Id
GROUP BY X.F10003, B.F72404

GO


ALTER FUNCTION [dbo].[DamiNorma] (@f10003 int, @dt DATE) 
RETURNs table AS 
return 

	SELECT top 1 Norma =   Norma, DATA_Norma = DATA_Norma, Tip_Norma = Tip_Norma, Durata_timp = Durata_timp, Repartizare = Repartizare, Interval = Interval  from 
(
SELECT top 1 1 as rank, F70403 marca,  F70407 Norma, F70406 Data_norma, F70424 Tip_Norma, F70425 Durata_timp, F70426  Repartizare, F70427 Interval,  F70406 Data from f704   WHERE F70404=6 AND F70406 <= @dt and F70403 = @f10003 ORDER BY F70406 DESC
union 
select 2 as rank, f100.f10003 marca, f10043 Norma, case when coalesce(year(F100955),2100) in (1900,2100) then F10022 else f100955 end Data_norma, F100926 Tip_Norma, F100927 Durata_timp, F100928  Repartizare, F100939 Interval, case when coalesce(100*year(F100955)+month(F100955), 100*2100+1) = 100 * f01011 + f01012 then F100955 else  DATEFROMPARTS(f01011, f01012, 1) end data from f100 join f1001 on f100.f10003 = f1001.f10003 join f010 on 1=1 where f100.f10003 =@f10003 and case when coalesce(100*year(F100955)+month(F100955), 100*2100+1) = 100 * f01011 + f01012 then F100955 else  DATEFROMPARTS(f01011, f01012, 1) end<=@dt
union
select top 1 3 as rank, f910.f91003 marca, F91043 Norma, case when coalesce(year(F910955),2100) in (1900,2100) then F91022 else f910955 end Data_norma, F910926 Tip_Norma, F910927 Durata_timp, F910928  Repartizare, F910939 Interval, case when coalesce(100*year(F910955)+month(F910955), 100*2100+1) = 100 * f910.YEAR + f910.month then F910955 else  DATEFROMPARTS(f910.year, f910.MONTH, 1) end data from f910 join f9101 on f910.f91003 = f9101.f91003 and f910.year = f9101.year and f910.month=f9101.month where case when coalesce(100*year(F910955)+month(F910955), 100*2100+1) = 100 * f910.YEAR + f910.month then F910955 else  DATEFROMPARTS(f910.year, f910.MONTH, 1) end <= @dt and f910.f91003 = @f10003 order by f910.year desc, f910.month desc
union
select 4 as rank, f100.f10003 marca, F10043 Norma, case when coalesce(year(F100955),2100) in (1900,2100) then F10022 else f100955 end Data_norma, F100926 Tip_Norma, F100927 Durata_timp, F100928  Repartizare, F100939 Interval, DATEFROMPARTS(1900,1,1) data from f100 join f1001 on f100.f10003 = f1001.f10003  where f100.f10003 =@f10003
) x
order by data desc, rank
GO

ALTER FUNCTION [dbo].[DamiDept] (@f10003 int, @dt DATE) 
RETURNs table AS 
return 

	SELECT top 1 Dept =   Dept, Data_dept = data_dept  from 
(
SELECT top 1 1 as rank, F70403 marca,  F70417 dept,  f70406 data_dept,  F70406 Data from f704   WHERE F70404=5 AND F70406 <= @dt and F70403 = @f10003 ORDER BY F70406 DESC
union 
select 2 as rank, f100.f10003 marca, f10007 dept, case when coalesce(year(F100910),2100) in (1900,2100) then F10022 else f100910 end data_dept, case when coalesce(100*year(F100910)+month(F100910), 100*2100+1) = 100 * f01011 + f01012 then F100910 else  DATEFROMPARTS(f01011, f01012, 1) end data from f100 join f010 on 1=1 where f100.f10003 =@f10003 and case when coalesce(100*year(F100910)+month(F100910), 100*2100+1) = 100 * f01011 + f01012 then F100910 else  DATEFROMPARTS(f01011, f01012, 1) end<=@dt
union
select top 1 3 as rank, f910.f91003 marca, F91007 dept, case when coalesce(year(F910910),2100) in (1900,2100) then F91022 else f910910 end data_dept, case when coalesce(100*year(F910910)+month(F910910), 100*2100+1) = 100 * f910.YEAR + f910.month then F910910 else  DATEFROMPARTS(f910.year, f910.MONTH, 1) end data from f910  where case when coalesce(100*year(F910910)+month(F910910), 100*2100+1) = 100 * f910.YEAR + f910.month then F910910 else  DATEFROMPARTS(f910.year, f910.MONTH, 1) end <= @dt and f910.f91003 = @f10003 order by f910.year desc, f910.month desc
union
select 4 as rank, f10003 marca, F10007 dept, case when coalesce(year(F100910),2100) in (1900,2100) then F10022 else f100910 end data_dept, DATEFROMPARTS(1900,1,1) data from f100 where f10003 =@f10003
) x
order by data desc, rank
GO


ALTER FUNCTION [dbo].[DamiCC] (@f10003 int, @dt DATE) 
RETURNs table AS 
return 

	SELECT top 1 CC =   cc, data_cc = data_cc from 
(
SELECT top 1 1 as rank, F70403 marca, F70407 cc,  F70406 data_cc, F70406 data from f704   WHERE F70404=14 AND F70406 <= @dt and F70403 = @f10003 ORDER BY F70406 DESC
union 
select 2 as rank, f10003 marca, f10053 cc, F10022 data_cc, DATEFROMPARTS(f01011, f01012, 1) data from f100 join f010 on 1=1 where f10003 =@f10003 and DATEFROMPARTS(f01011, f01012, 1)<=@dt
union
select top 1 3 as rank, f91003 marca, f91053 cc, F91022 data_cc, DATEFROMPARTS(year, MONTH, 1) data from f910 where DATEFROMPARTS(year, MONTH, 1)<= @dt and f91003 = @f10003 order by year desc, month desc
union
select 4 as rank, f10003 marca, f10053 cc, f10022 data_cc, DATEFROMPARTS(1900,1,1) data from f100 where f10003 =@f10003
) x
order by data desc, rank
GO


ALTER FUNCTION [dbo].[DamiDataPlecare] (@f10003 int, @dt DATE) 
RETURNs table AS 
return 

	SELECT top 1 DataPlecare =   DataPlecare from 
(
SELECT top 1 1 as rank, F70403 marca,  F70406 - 1 dataplecare,  F70406 Data from f704   WHERE F70404=4 AND F70406 <= @dt and F70403 = @f10003 ORDER BY F70406 DESC
union 
select 2 as rank, f10003 marca, f10023 Dataplecare,   DATEFROMPARTS(f01011, f01012, 1) data from f100 join f010 on 1=1 where f10003 =@f10003 and DATEFROMPARTS(f01011, f01012, 1)<=@dt
union
select top 1 3 as rank, f91003 marca, f91023 dataplecare,  DATEFROMPARTS(year, MONTH, 1) data from f910 where DATEFROMPARTS(year, MONTH, 1)<= @dt and f91003 = @f10003 order by year desc, month desc
union
select 4 as rank, f10003 marca, F10023 dataplecare, DATEFROMPARTS(1900,1,1) data from f100 where f10003 =@f10003
) x
order by data desc, rank
GO




create FUNCTION [dbo].[DamiSalariu] (@f10003 int, @dt DATE) 
RETURNs table AS 
return 

	SELECT top 1 Salariu =   Salariu, DATA_Salariu = DATA_Salariu from 
(
SELECT top 1 1 as rank, F70403 marca,  F70407 Salariu, f70406 Data_salariu, F70406 Data from f704   WHERE F70404=1 AND F70406 <= @dt and F70403 = @f10003 ORDER BY F70406 DESC
union 
select 2 as rank, f100.f10003 marca, f100699 Salariu, case when coalesce(year(F100991),2100) in (1900,2100) then F10022 else f100991 end Data_salariu,  case when coalesce(100*year(F100991)+month(F100991), 100*2100+1) = 100 * f01011 + f01012 then F100991 else  DATEFROMPARTS(f01011, f01012, 1) end data from f100 join f010 on 1=1 where f100.f10003 =@f10003 and case when coalesce(100*year(F100991)+month(F100991), 100*2100+1) = 100 * f01011 + f01012 then F100991 else  DATEFROMPARTS(f01011, f01012, 1) end<=@dt
union
select top 1 3 as rank, f910.f91003 marca, F910699 Salariu, case when coalesce(year(F910991),2100) in (1900,2100) then F91022 else f910991 end Data_salariu, case when coalesce(100*year(F910991)+month(F910991), 100*2100+1) = 100 * f910.YEAR + f910.month then F910991 else  DATEFROMPARTS(f910.year, f910.MONTH, 1) end data from f910  where case when coalesce(100*year(F910991)+month(F910991), 100*2100+1) = 100 * f910.YEAR + f910.month then F910991 else  DATEFROMPARTS(f910.year, f910.MONTH, 1) end <= @dt and f910.f91003 = @f10003 order by f910.year desc, f910.month desc
union
select 4 as rank, f10003 marca, F100699 Salariu, case when coalesce(year(F100991),2100) in (1900,2100) then F10022 else f100991 end Data_salariu, DATEFROMPARTS(1900,1,1) data from f100 where f10003 =@f10003
) x
order by data desc, rank
GO


create FUNCTION [dbo].[DamiFunctie] (@f10003 int, @dt DATE) 
RETURNs table AS 
return 

	SELECT top 1 Functie =   Functie, DATA_Functie = DATA_Functie from 
(
SELECT top 1 1 as rank, F70403 marca,  F70407 Functie, f70406 DATA_Functie, F70406 Data from f704   WHERE F70404=2 AND F70406 <= @dt and F70403 = @f10003 ORDER BY F70406 DESC
union 
select 2 as rank, f100.f10003 marca, f10071 Functie, case when coalesce(year(F100992),2100) in (1900,2100) then F10022 else f100992 end DATA_Functie,  case when coalesce(100*year(F100992)+month(F100992), 100*2100+1) = 100 * f01011 + f01012 then F100992 else  DATEFROMPARTS(f01011, f01012, 1) end data from f100 join f010 on 1=1 where f100.f10003 =@f10003 and case when coalesce(100*year(F100992)+month(F100992), 100*2100+1) = 100 * f01011 + f01012 then F100992 else  DATEFROMPARTS(f01011, f01012, 1) end<=@dt
union
select top 1 3 as rank, f910.f91003 marca, F91071 Functie, case when coalesce(year(F910992),2100) in (1900,2100) then F91022 else f910992 end DATA_Functie, case when coalesce(100*year(F910992)+month(F910992), 100*2100+1) = 100 * f910.YEAR + f910.month then F910992 else  DATEFROMPARTS(f910.year, f910.MONTH, 1) end data from f910  where case when coalesce(100*year(F910992)+month(F910992), 100*2100+1) = 100 * f910.YEAR + f910.month then F910992 else  DATEFROMPARTS(f910.year, f910.MONTH, 1) end <= @dt and f910.f91003 = @f10003 order by f910.year desc, f910.month desc
union
select 4 as rank, f10003 marca, F10071 Functie, case when coalesce(year(F100992),2100) in (1900,2100) then F10022 else f100992 end DATA_Functie, DATEFROMPARTS(1900,1,1) data from f100 where f10003 =@f10003
) x
order by data desc, rank
GO


CREATE FUNCTION [dbo].[DamiCodCOR] (@f10003 int, @dt DATE) 
RETURNs table AS 
return 

	SELECT top 1 CodCOR =   CodCOR, DATA_CodCOR = DATA_CodCOR from 
(
SELECT top 1 1 as rank, F70403 marca,  F70407 CodCOR, F70406 DATA_CodCOR, F70406 Data from f704   WHERE F70404=3 AND F70406 <= @dt and F70403 = @f10003 ORDER BY F70406 DESC
union 
select 2 as rank, f100.f10003 marca, f10098 CodCOR, case when coalesce(year(F100956),2100) in (1900,2100) then F10022 else f100956 end DATA_CodCOR,  case when coalesce(100*year(F100956)+month(F100956), 100*2100+1) = 100 * f01011 + f01012 then F100956 else  DATEFROMPARTS(f01011, f01012, 1) end data from f100 join f1001 on f100.f10003 = f1001.f10003 join f010 on 1=1 where f100.f10003 =@f10003 and case when coalesce(100*year(F100956)+month(F100956), 100*2100+1) = 100 * f01011 + f01012 then F100956 else  DATEFROMPARTS(f01011, f01012, 1) end<=@dt
union
select top 1 3 as rank, f910.f91003 marca, F91098 CodCOR, case when coalesce(year(F910956),2100) in (1900,2100) then F91022 else f910956 end DATA_CodCOR, case when coalesce(100*year(F910956)+month(F910956), 100*2100+1) = 100 * f910.YEAR + f910.month then F910956 else  DATEFROMPARTS(f910.year, f910.MONTH, 1) end data from f910 join f9101 on f910.f91003 = f9101.f91003 and f910.year = f9101.year and f910.month=f9101.month where case when coalesce(100*year(F910956)+month(F910956), 100*2100+1) = 100 * f910.YEAR + f910.month then F910956 else  DATEFROMPARTS(f910.year, f910.MONTH, 1) end <= @dt and f910.f91003 = @f10003 order by f910.year desc, f910.month desc
union
select 4 as rank, f100.f10003 marca, F10098 CodCOR, case when coalesce(year(F100956),2100) in (1900,2100) then F10022 else f100956 end DATA_CodCOR,  DATEFROMPARTS(1900,1,1) data from f100 join f1001 on f100.f10003 = f1001.f10003  where f100.f10003 =@f10003
) x
order by data desc, rank
GO

CREATE VIEW viewAdresaDetaliata as
select F10003, case when TipNivel1 = 40 and UPPER(NumeNivel1) not like '%BUCURESTI%' then NumeNivel1 else '' end as Judet,  
case when TipNivel1 = 40 and UPPER(NumeNivel1) like '%BUCURESTI%' then NumeNivel1 else '' end as MunicipiuRangJudet, 
case when TipNivel2 = 1 or TipNivel2 = 4  then NumeNivel2 else '' end as Municipiu,
case when TipNivel2 = 2  then NumeNivel2 else '' end as Oras,
case when TipNivel2 = 3  then NumeNivel2 else '' end as Comuna, 
case when TipNivel3 = 9 or TipNivel3 = 10 or TipNivel3 = 17 or TipNivel3 = 18 then NumeNivel3 else '' end as Localitate,
case when TipNivel3 = 11 or TipNivel3 = 19 or TipNivel3 = 22 or TipNivel3 = 23 then NumeNivel3 else '' end as Sat,
case when TipNivel3 = 6  then NumeNivel3 else '' end as Sector,
(case when Strada is not null and LEN(Strada) > 0 then 'Str. ' + Strada + ',' else '' end) + (case when Numar is not null and LEN(Numar) > 0 then ' nr. ' + Numar + ',' else '' end) +
(case when Bloc is not null and LEN(Bloc) > 0 then ' bl. ' + Bloc + ',' else '' end) + (case when Scara is not null and LEN(Scara) > 0 then ' sc. ' + Scara + ',' else '' end) +
(case when Etaj is not null and LEN(Etaj) > 0 then ' et. ' + Etaj + ',' else '' end) + (case when Apartament is not null and LEN(Apartament) > 0 then ' ap. ' + Apartament + ',' else '' end) +
(case when TipNivel3 = 6 then (case when UPPER(NumeNivel3) not like '%SECTOR%' then ' sector ' + NumeNivel3 + ',' else ' ' + NumeNivel3 + ',' end) 
                  when TipNivel3 = 11 or TipNivel3 = 19 or TipNivel3 = 22 or TipNivel3 = 23 then (case when UPPER(NumeNivel3) not like 'SAT %' then ' sat ' + NumeNivel3 + ',' else ' ' + NumeNivel3 + ',' end) 
                  when TipNivel3 = 9 or TipNivel3 = 10 or TipNivel3 = 17 or TipNivel3 = 18 then ' ' + NumeNivel3 + ',' else '' end) +
(case when TipNivel2 = 1 or TipNivel2 = 4 then (case when UPPER(NumeNivel2) not like 'MUNICIPIU%' then ' municipiul ' + NumeNivel2 + ',' else ' ' + NumeNivel2 + ',' end)
                when  TipNivel2 = 2 then (case when UPPER(NumeNivel2) not like 'ORAS%' then ' orasul ' + NumeNivel2 + ',' else ' ' + NumeNivel2 + ',' end)
                when  TipNivel2 = 3 then (case when UPPER(NumeNivel2) not like 'COMUNA%' then ' comuna ' + NumeNivel2 + ',' else ' ' + NumeNivel2 + ',' end) else '' end) +
(case when TipNivel1 = 40 and UPPER(NumeNivel1) not like '%BUCURESTI%' then (case when UPPER(NumeNivel1) not like 'JUDET%' then ' judetul ' + NumeNivel1 else ' ' + NumeNivel1 end)
                when TipNivel1 = 40 and UPPER(NumeNivel1) like '%BUCURESTI%' then (case when UPPER(NumeNivel1) not like 'MUNICIPIU%' then ' municipiul ' + NumeNivel1 else ' ' + NumeNivel1 end) else '' end)
as Adresa  from F100Adrese
GO

CREATE FUNCTION [dbo].[DamiTipContract] (@f10003 int, @dt DATE) RETURNs table AS return 

select TipContract, DataInceputCIM, DataSfarsitCIM ,Numar_prelungiri, Data_ultimei_prelungiri, case when Urmeaza_TipContract = 1 and tipcontract = 1 then null else Urmeaza_TipContract end Urmeaza_TipContract, case when Urmeaza_TipContract = 1 and tipcontract = 1 then null when Urmeaza_TipContract = 1 and tipcontract = 2 then DataSfarsitCIM + 1 else Urmeaza_TipContract_LaData end Urmeaza_TipContract_LaData  from (SELECT top 1  TipContract, DataInceputCIM, DataSfarsitCIM from (select f10003 marca, f1009741 tipcontract, f100933 DataInceputCIM, f100934 DataSfarsitCIM from f100 where f10003=@f10003 union select distinct f91003 marca, f9109741 tipcontract, f910933 DataInceputCIM, f910934 DataSfarsitCIM from f910 where f91003=@f10003) a where DataSfarsitCIM >= @dt order by DataInceputCIM , DataSfarsitCIM )x join (select count(*) as Numar_prelungiri, max(DataSfarsitCIM) + 1 as Data_ultimei_prelungiri from (select  marca, tipcontract, datainceputCIM, max(DataSfarsitCIM)  DataSfarsitCIM from (select f10003 marca, f1009741 tipcontract, f100933 DataInceputCIM, f100934 DataSfarsitCIM from f100 where f10003=@f10003 union select distinct f91003 marca, f9109741 tipcontract, f910933 DataInceputCIM, f910934 DataSfarsitCIM from f910 where f91003=@f10003) a group by marca, tipcontract, datainceputCIM having max(DataSfarsitCIM) < @dt )b)y on 1=1 join (SELECT top 1  tipcontract as Urmeaza_TipContract, DataInceputCIM as Urmeaza_TipContract_LaData from (select f10003 marca, f1009741 tipcontract, f100933 DataInceputCIM, f100934 DataSfarsitCIM from f100 where f10003=@f10003 union select distinct f91003 marca, f9109741 tipcontract, f910933 DataInceputCIM, f910934 DataSfarsitCIM from f910 where f91003=@f10003) a where DataInceputCIM > @dt order by DataInceputCIM , DataSfarsitCIM desc ) z on 1=1


INSERT INTO tblParametrii(Nume, Valoare, Explicatie, IdModul, Criptat) VALUES('PontajCCVerificareDepasireNorma','1','Daca valoarea parametrului este 1 se face verificare ca totalul pe centri de cost sa nu depaseasca norma',2, 0)
GO

UPDATE 
     F1001
SET 
     F1001131 = a.F100902,
	 F1001132 = a.F100903,
	 F1001133 = a.F100904
FROM 
     F1001 b
     INNER JOIN F100 a
     ON a.F10003 = b.F10003;

CREATE TABLE [dbo].[tmpIdPrint](
	[IdSesiune] [int] NOT NULL,
	[Id] [int] NOT NULL,
	[TIME] [date] NULL,
 CONSTRAINT [PK_tmpIdPrint] PRIMARY KEY CLUSTERED 
(
	[IdSesiune] ASC,
	[Id] ASC
)WITH (PAD_INDEX = OFF, STATISTICS_NORECOMPUTE = OFF, IGNORE_DUP_KEY = OFF, ALLOW_ROW_LOCKS = ON, ALLOW_PAGE_LOCKS = ON) ON [PRIMARY]
) ON [PRIMARY]
GO

ALTER TABLE [dbo].[tmpIdPrint] ADD  CONSTRAINT [DF_tmpIdPrint_TIME]  DEFAULT (getdate()) FOR [TIME]
GO

CREATE SEQUENCE [dbo].[tmpIdPrint_Id_SEQ] 
 AS [bigint]
 START WITH 1
 INCREMENT BY 1
 MINVALUE 1
 MAXVALUE 9999999999999
 CACHE 
GO

ALTER VIEW "RapoarteGrupuriUtilizatori" ("IdRaport", "IdUser", "ExtensiiPermise", "MeniuRestrans") AS 
SELECT DISTINCT r."DynReportId" AS "IdRaport", gu."IdUser", gs."ExtensiiPermise", gs."MeniuRestrans"
FROM "DynReports" r
INNER JOIN "relGrupRaport"  gr ON r."DynReportId" = gr."IdRaport"
INNER JOIN "relGrupUser"  gu ON gr."IdGrup" = gu."IdGrup"
INNER JOIN "tblGrupUsers"  gs ON gu."IdGrup" = gs."Id"
UNION ALL
SELECT "DynReportId" AS "IdRaport", "IdUser" AS "IdUser", NULL AS "ExtensiiPermise", NULL AS "MeniuRestrans"
FROM "relGrupUser", "DynReports"
WHERE "IdGrup" = 0 AND "DynReportId" NOT IN (SELECT "IdRaport" FROM "relGrupRaport" WHERE "IdGrup" = 0)
UNION ALL
SELECT B."IdRaport", A.F70102 AS "IdUser", NULL AS "ExtensiiPermise", NULL AS "MeniuRestrans"
FROM USERS A
INNER JOIN "relGrupRaport" B ON B."IdGrup"=-1

alter view viewAdresaDetaliata as
 select F10003, a.Denumire as TipAdresa, 
 case when TipNivel1 = 40 and UPPER(NumeNivel1) not like '%BUCURESTI%' then NumeNivel1 else '' end as Judet,  
case when TipNivel1 = 40 and UPPER(NumeNivel1) like '%BUCURESTI%' then NumeNivel1 else '' end as MunicipiuRangJudet, 
case when TipNivel2 = 1 or TipNivel2 = 4  then NumeNivel2 else '' end as Municipiu,
case when TipNivel2 = 2  then NumeNivel2 else '' end as Oras,
case when TipNivel2 = 3  then NumeNivel2 else '' end as Comuna, 
case when TipNivel3 = 9 or TipNivel3 = 10 or TipNivel3 = 17 or TipNivel3 = 18 then NumeNivel3 else '' end as Localitate,
case when TipNivel3 = 11 or TipNivel3 = 19 or TipNivel3 = 22 or TipNivel3 = 23 then NumeNivel3 else '' end as Sat,
case when TipNivel3 = 6  then NumeNivel3 else '' end as Sector,
b.Denumire as TipArtera,
(case when Strada is not null and LEN(Strada) > 0 then Strada + ',' else '' end) + (case when Numar is not null and LEN(Numar) > 0 then ' nr. ' + Numar + ',' else '' end) +
(case when Bloc is not null and LEN(Bloc) > 0 then ' bl. ' + Bloc + ',' else '' end) + (case when Scara is not null and LEN(Scara) > 0 then ' sc. ' + Scara + ',' else '' end) +
(case when Etaj is not null and LEN(Etaj) > 0 then ' et. ' + Etaj + ',' else '' end) + (case when Apartament is not null and LEN(Apartament) > 0 then ' ap. ' + Apartament + ',' else '' end) +
(case when TipNivel3 = 6 then (case when UPPER(NumeNivel3) not like '%SECTOR%' then ' sector ' + NumeNivel3 + ',' else ' ' + NumeNivel3 + ',' end) 
	  when TipNivel3 = 11 or TipNivel3 = 19 or TipNivel3 = 22 or TipNivel3 = 23 then (case when UPPER(NumeNivel3) not like 'SAT %' then ' sat ' + NumeNivel3 + ',' else ' ' + NumeNivel3 + ',' end) 
	  when TipNivel3 = 9 or TipNivel3 = 10 or TipNivel3 = 17 or TipNivel3 = 18 then ' ' + NumeNivel3 + ',' else '' end) +
(case when TipNivel2 = 1 or TipNivel2 = 4 then (case when UPPER(NumeNivel2) not like 'MUNICIPIU%' then ' municipiul ' + NumeNivel2 + ',' else ' ' + NumeNivel2 + ',' end)
	 when  TipNivel2 = 2 then (case when UPPER(NumeNivel2) not like 'ORAS%' then ' orasul ' + NumeNivel2 + ',' else ' ' + NumeNivel2 + ',' end)
	 when  TipNivel2 = 3 then (case when UPPER(NumeNivel2) not like 'COMUNA%' then ' comuna ' + NumeNivel2 + ',' else ' ' + NumeNivel2 + ',' end) else '' end) +
(case when TipNivel1 = 40 and UPPER(NumeNivel1) not like '%BUCURESTI%' then (case when UPPER(NumeNivel1) not like 'JUDET%' then ' judetul ' + NumeNivel1 else ' ' + NumeNivel1 end)
	when TipNivel1 = 40 and UPPER(NumeNivel1) like '%BUCURESTI%' then (case when UPPER(NumeNivel1) not like 'MUNICIPIU%' then ' municipiul ' + NumeNivel1 else ' ' + NumeNivel1 end) else '' end)
as Adresa  from F100Adrese
left join tblTipAdresa a on a.Id = IdTipAdresa
left join tblTipstrada b on b.Id = IdTipStrada





CREATE TABLE [dbo].[relRapGrupModul](
	[IdModul] [int] NOT NULL,
	[IdRaport] [int] NOT NULL,
	[IdGrup] [int] NOT NULL,

	[TIME] [datetime] NULL DEFAULT getdate()
 CONSTRAINT [relRapGrupModul_PK] PRIMARY KEY CLUSTERED 
(
	[IdModul], [IdRaport], [IdGrup] ASC
)WITH (PAD_INDEX = OFF, STATISTICS_NORECOMPUTE = OFF, IGNORE_DUP_KEY = OFF, ALLOW_ROW_LOCKS = ON, ALLOW_PAGE_LOCKS = ON) ON [PRIMARY]
) ON [PRIMARY]

GO

DECLARE @table NVARCHAR(512), @sql NVARCHAR(MAX);
SELECT @table = N'dbo.Ptj_CC';
SELECT @sql = 'ALTER TABLE ' + @table 
    + ' DROP CONSTRAINT ' + name + ';'
    FROM sys.key_constraints
    WHERE [type] = 'PK'
    AND [parent_object_id] = OBJECT_ID(@table);
EXEC sp_executeSQL @sql;
GO

ALTER VIEW [dbo].[Cursuri_VIEW] AS
select Marca,NumeComplet,IdTipCurs,IdDescriereCurs,NumeFurnizor,TemaCurs,Info,NrOre,DataCurs,Buget,PerioadaAmortizare,AutorizareExpirare,USER_NO,[TIME],IdAuto,DataInceput, DataSfarsit, NrZile
from
Admin_Cursuri
WHERE 1<1
GO

ALTER VIEW [dbo].[Admin_Cursuri_VIEW] as
select Marca,NumeComplet,IdTipCurs,IdDescriereCurs,NumeFurnizor,TemaCurs,Info,NrOre,DataCurs,Buget,PerioadaAmortizare,AutorizareExpirare,USER_NO,[TIME],IdAuto,DataInceput, DataSfarsit, NrZile
from
Admin_Cursuri
UNION ALL
SELECT Marca,NumeComplet,IdTipCurs,IdDescriereCurs,NumeFurnizor,TemaCurs,Info,NrOre,DataCurs,Buget,PerioadaAmortizare,AutorizareExpirare,USER_NO,[TIME],IdAuto,DataInceput, DataSfarsit, NrZile
from
Cursuri_VIEW
GO

ALTER VIEW [dbo].[viewEvaluare360]
AS
select  b.IdQuiz, b.F10003,  c.descriere AS Descriere, a.Descriere as Intrebare, b.Obiectiv as PuncteForte, b.Activitate as ZoneDeDezvoltare, D.Anul AS Perioada
from Eval_QuizIntrebari a
inner join Eval_QuizIntrebari c on a.parinte = c.Id and c.Descriere = 'Vitality'
inner join Eval_ObiIndividualeTemp b on a.idquiz=b.IdQuiz and a.id=b.IdLinieQuiz
INNER JOIN Eval_Quiz D ON A.IdQuiz = D.Id
where COALESCE(D.CategorieQuiz,0)=1
union
select b.IdQuiz, b.F10003,  c.descriere AS Descriere, a.Descriere as Intrebare, b.Obiectiv as PuncteForte, b.Activitate as ZoneDeDezvoltare, D.Anul AS Perioada
from Eval_QuizIntrebari a
inner join Eval_QuizIntrebari c on a.parinte = c.Id and c.Descriere = 'Effectiveness'
inner join Eval_ObiIndividualeTemp b on a.idquiz=b.IdQuiz and a.id=b.IdLinieQuiz
INNER JOIN Eval_Quiz D ON A.IdQuiz = D.Id
where COALESCE(D.CategorieQuiz,0)=1
union
select b.IdQuiz, b.F10003,  c.descriere AS Descriere, a.Descriere as Intrebare, b.Obiectiv as PuncteForte, b.Activitate as ZoneDeDezvoltare, D.Anul AS Perioada
from Eval_QuizIntrebari a
inner join Eval_QuizIntrebari c on a.parinte = c.Id and c.Descriere = 'Creativity'
inner join Eval_ObiIndividualeTemp b on a.idquiz=b.IdQuiz and a.id=b.IdLinieQuiz
INNER JOIN Eval_Quiz D ON A.IdQuiz = D.Id
where COALESCE(D.CategorieQuiz,0)=1
union
select b.IdQuiz, b.F10003,  c.descriere AS Descriere, a.Descriere as Intrebare, b.Obiectiv as PuncteForte, b.Activitate as ZoneDeDezvoltare, D.Anul AS Perioada
from Eval_QuizIntrebari a
inner join Eval_QuizIntrebari c on a.parinte = c.Id and c.Descriere = 'Common Sense'
inner join Eval_ObiIndividualeTemp b on a.idquiz=b.IdQuiz and a.id=b.IdLinieQuiz
INNER JOIN Eval_Quiz D ON A.IdQuiz = D.Id
where COALESCE(D.CategorieQuiz,0)=1
union
select b.IdQuiz, b.F10003,  c.descriere AS Descriere, a.Descriere as Intrebare, b.Obiectiv as PuncteForte, b.Activitate as ZoneDeDezvoltare, D.Anul AS Perioada
from Eval_QuizIntrebari a
inner join Eval_QuizIntrebari c on a.parinte = c.Id and c.Descriere = 'Relationships'
inner join Eval_ObiIndividualeTemp b on a.idquiz=b.IdQuiz and a.id=b.IdLinieQuiz
INNER JOIN Eval_Quiz D ON A.IdQuiz = D.Id
where COALESCE(D.CategorieQuiz,0)=1
UNION
SELECT IdQuiz, F10003, 'Others' AS Descriere, '' as Intrebare, PuncteForte, '' AS ZoneDeDezvoltare, D.Anul AS Perioada 
FROM (
SELECT IdQuiz, F10003, ISNULL(Super1,'') AS PuncteForte FROM Eval_RaspunsLinii WHERE Id IN (385,421,459,506,717,874,911,948)
UNION
SELECT IdQuiz, F10003, ISNULL(Super2,'') AS PuncteForte FROM Eval_RaspunsLinii WHERE Id IN (385,421,459,506,717,874,911,948)
UNION
SELECT IdQuiz, F10003, ISNULL(Super3,'') AS PuncteForte FROM Eval_RaspunsLinii WHERE Id IN (385,421,459,506,717,874,911,948)
UNION
SELECT IdQuiz, F10003, ISNULL(Super4,'') AS PuncteForte FROM Eval_RaspunsLinii WHERE Id IN (385,421,459,506,717,874,911,948)
UNION
SELECT IdQuiz, F10003, ISNULL(Super5,'') AS PuncteForte FROM Eval_RaspunsLinii WHERE Id IN (385,421,459,506,717,874,911,948)
UNION
SELECT IdQuiz, F10003, ISNULL(Super6,'') AS PuncteForte FROM Eval_RaspunsLinii WHERE Id IN (385,421,459,506,717,874,911,948)
UNION
SELECT IdQuiz, F10003, ISNULL(Super7,'') AS PuncteForte FROM Eval_RaspunsLinii WHERE Id IN (385,421,459,506,717,874,911,948)
UNION
SELECT IdQuiz, F10003, ISNULL(Super8,'') AS PuncteForte FROM Eval_RaspunsLinii WHERE Id IN (385,421,459,506,717,874,911,948)
UNION
SELECT IdQuiz, F10003, ISNULL(Super9,'') AS PuncteForte FROM Eval_RaspunsLinii WHERE Id IN (385,421,459,506,717,874,911,948)
UNION
SELECT IdQuiz, F10003, ISNULL(Super10,'') AS PuncteForte FROM Eval_RaspunsLinii WHERE Id IN (385,421,459,506,717,874,911,948)
UNION
SELECT IdQuiz, F10003, ISNULL(Super11,'') AS PuncteForte FROM Eval_RaspunsLinii WHERE Id IN (385,421,459,506,717,874,911,948)
UNION
SELECT IdQuiz, F10003, ISNULL(Super12,'') AS PuncteForte FROM Eval_RaspunsLinii WHERE Id IN (385,421,459,506,717,874,911,948)
UNION
SELECT IdQuiz, F10003, ISNULL(Super13,'') AS PuncteForte FROM Eval_RaspunsLinii WHERE Id IN (385,421,459,506,717,874,911,948)
UNION
SELECT IdQuiz, F10003, ISNULL(Super14,'') AS PuncteForte FROM Eval_RaspunsLinii WHERE Id IN (385,421,459,506,717,874,911,948)
UNION
SELECT IdQuiz, F10003, ISNULL(Super15,'') AS PuncteForte FROM Eval_RaspunsLinii WHERE Id IN (385,421,459,506,717,874,911,948)
UNION
SELECT IdQuiz, F10003, ISNULL(Super16,'') AS PuncteForte FROM Eval_RaspunsLinii WHERE Id IN (385,421,459,506,717,874,911,948)
UNION
SELECT IdQuiz, F10003, ISNULL(Super17,'') AS PuncteForte FROM Eval_RaspunsLinii WHERE Id IN (385,421,459,506,717,874,911,948)
UNION
SELECT IdQuiz, F10003, ISNULL(Super18,'') AS PuncteForte FROM Eval_RaspunsLinii WHERE Id IN (385,421,459,506,717,874,911,948)
UNION
SELECT IdQuiz, F10003, ISNULL(Super19,'') AS PuncteForte FROM Eval_RaspunsLinii WHERE Id IN (385,421,459,506,717,874,911,948)
UNION
SELECT IdQuiz, F10003, ISNULL(Super20,'') AS PuncteForte FROM Eval_RaspunsLinii WHERE Id IN (385,421,459,506,717,874,911,948)
) X 
INNER JOIN Eval_Quiz D ON X.IdQuiz = D.Id
WHERE PuncteForte <> ''


GO

ALTER VIEW [dbo].[viewEvaluareProiect]
AS
select b.IdQuiz, b.F10003,  c.descriere AS Descriere, a.Descriere as Intrebare, b.Obiectiv as PuncteForte, b.Activitate as ZoneDeDezvoltare, D.Anul AS Perioada
from Eval_QuizIntrebari a
inner join Eval_QuizIntrebari c on a.parinte = c.Id and c.Descriere = 'Vitality'
inner join Eval_ObiIndividualeTemp b on a.idquiz=b.IdQuiz and a.id=b.IdLinieQuiz
INNER JOIN Eval_Quiz D ON A.IdQuiz = D.Id
where COALESCE(D.CategorieQuiz,0)=2
union
select b.IdQuiz, b.F10003,  c.descriere AS Descriere, a.Descriere as Intrebare, b.Obiectiv as PuncteForte, b.Activitate as ZoneDeDezvoltare, D.Anul AS Perioada
from Eval_QuizIntrebari a
inner join Eval_QuizIntrebari c on a.parinte = c.Id and c.Descriere = 'Effectiveness'
inner join Eval_ObiIndividualeTemp b on a.idquiz=b.IdQuiz and a.id=b.IdLinieQuiz
INNER JOIN Eval_Quiz D ON A.IdQuiz = D.Id
where COALESCE(D.CategorieQuiz,0)=2
union 
select b.IdQuiz, b.F10003,  c.descriere AS Descriere, a.Descriere as Intrebare, b.Obiectiv as PuncteForte, b.Activitate as ZoneDeDezvoltare, D.Anul AS Perioada
from Eval_QuizIntrebari a
inner join Eval_QuizIntrebari c on a.parinte = c.Id and c.Descriere = 'Creativity'
inner join Eval_ObiIndividualeTemp b on a.idquiz=b.IdQuiz and a.id=b.IdLinieQuiz
INNER JOIN Eval_Quiz D ON A.IdQuiz = D.Id
where COALESCE(D.CategorieQuiz,0)=2
union 
select b.IdQuiz, b.F10003,  c.descriere AS Descriere, a.Descriere as Intrebare, b.Obiectiv as PuncteForte, b.Activitate as ZoneDeDezvoltare, D.Anul AS Perioada
from Eval_QuizIntrebari a
inner join Eval_QuizIntrebari c on a.parinte = c.Id and c.Descriere = 'Common Sense'
inner join Eval_ObiIndividualeTemp b on a.idquiz=b.IdQuiz and a.id=b.IdLinieQuiz
INNER JOIN Eval_Quiz D ON A.IdQuiz = D.Id
where COALESCE(D.CategorieQuiz,0)=2
union 
select b.IdQuiz, b.F10003,  c.descriere AS Descriere, a.Descriere as Intrebare, b.Obiectiv as PuncteForte, b.Activitate as ZoneDeDezvoltare, D.Anul AS Perioada
from Eval_QuizIntrebari a
inner join Eval_QuizIntrebari c on a.parinte = c.Id and c.Descriere = 'Relationships'
inner join Eval_ObiIndividualeTemp b on a.idquiz=b.IdQuiz and a.id=b.IdLinieQuiz
INNER JOIN Eval_Quiz D ON A.IdQuiz = D.Id
where COALESCE(D.CategorieQuiz,0)=2

GO

CREATE TABLE [dbo].[ALIASCMP](
	[IDCMP] [int] NOT NULL,
	[TABELA] [nvarchar](50) NULL,
	[CAMP] [nvarchar](50) NULL,
	[DESCRIERE] [nvarchar](250) NULL,
 CONSTRAINT [PK_ALIASCMP] PRIMARY KEY CLUSTERED 
(
	[IDCMP] ASC
)WITH (PAD_INDEX = OFF, STATISTICS_NORECOMPUTE = OFF, IGNORE_DUP_KEY = OFF, ALLOW_ROW_LOCKS = ON, ALLOW_PAGE_LOCKS = ON) ON [PRIMARY]
) ON [PRIMARY]

GO

	[DESCRIERE] [nvarchar](250) NULL,

(
	[IDTAB] ASC
)WITH (PAD_INDEX = OFF, STATISTICS_NORECOMPUTE = OFF, IGNORE_DUP_KEY = OFF, ALLOW_ROW_LOCKS = ON, ALLOW_PAGE_LOCKS = ON) ON [PRIMARY]
) ON [PRIMARY]

GO

	[Id] [int] NOT NULL,
	[Denumire] [nvarchar](4000) NULL,
	[DenumireScurta] [nvarchar](150) NULL,
	[Activ] [int] NULL,
	[USER_NO] [int] NULL,
	[TIME] [datetime] NULL,

(
	[Id] ASC
)WITH (PAD_INDEX = OFF, STATISTICS_NORECOMPUTE = OFF, IGNORE_DUP_KEY = OFF, ALLOW_ROW_LOCKS = ON, ALLOW_PAGE_LOCKS = ON) ON [PRIMARY]
) ON [PRIMARY]
GO

IF COL_LENGTH('DynReports', 'HasPassword') IS NOT NULL
	ALTER TABLE [dbo].[DynReports] DROP COLUMN [HasPassword];
GO
UPDATE DynReports SET DynReportTypeId = 1 WHERE DynReportTypeId = 5;
DELETE FROM [dbo].[DynReportTypes] WHERE [DynReportTypeId] = 5;
UPDATE [dbo].[tblMeniuri] SET [Pagina] = 'Generatoare\Reports\Pages\Manage' WHERE [Id] = 24
--ALTER TABLE [dbo].[tblGrupUsers] ADD [MeniuRestrans] smallint NULL;

IF OBJECT_ID(N'relGrupRaport2', N'U') IS NULL
BEGIN
    EXEC sp_rename 'relGrupRaport', 'relGrupRaport2';
	EXEC('CREATE VIEW [relGrupRaport] AS SELECT * FROM [relGrupRaport2];');	
END

IF COL_LENGTH('relGrupRaport2', 'AreParola') IS NULL
	ALTER TABLE [dbo].[relGrupRaport2] ADD [AreParola] bit NOT NULL DEFAULT (0);
GO

ALTER VIEW [dbo].[RapoarteGrupuriUtilizatori] ("IdRaport", "IdUser", "ExtensiiPermise", "MeniuRestrans", "AreParola")
AS 
SELECT DISTINCT r."DynReportId" AS "IdRaport", gu."IdUser", gs."ExtensiiPermise", gs."MeniuRestrans", gr."AreParola"
FROM "DynReports" r
INNER JOIN "relGrupRaport2" gr ON r."DynReportId" = gr."IdRaport"
INNER JOIN "relGrupUser" gu ON gr."IdGrup" = gu."IdGrup"
INNER JOIN "tblGrupUsers" gs ON gu."IdGrup" = gs."Id"
UNION ALL
SELECT "DynReportId" AS "IdRaport", "IdUser" AS "IdUser", NULL AS "ExtensiiPermise", NULL AS "MeniuRestrans", ISNULL(CAST(0 AS BIT), 0) AS "AreParola"
FROM "relGrupUser", "DynReports"
WHERE "IdGrup" = 0 AND "DynReportId" NOT IN (SELECT "IdRaport" FROM "relGrupRaport" WHERE "IdGrup" = 0)
UNION ALL
SELECT B."IdRaport", A.F70102 AS "IdUser", NULL AS "ExtensiiPermise", NULL AS "MeniuRestrans", B."AreParola"
FROM USERS A
INNER JOIN "relGrupRaport2" B ON B."IdGrup"=-1
GO

GO

DELETE FROM "tblParametrii" WHERE "Nume" = 'RecalculCuloare'
GO

UPDATE Ntf_Setari SET ContinutMail=REPLACE(ContinutMail,'#$Link Aproba$#','#$Link1 Aproba$#') WHERE ContinutMail LIKE '%#$Link Aproba$#%'
UPDATE Ntf_Setari SET ContinutMail=REPLACE(ContinutMail,'#$Link Respinge$#','#$Link2 Respinge$#') WHERE ContinutMail LIKE '%#$Link Respinge$#%'
GO

EXEC sp_rename 'tblZile', 'tblZile2'
GO

CREATE VIEW tblZile
AS 
SELECT A.Zi, A.ZiSapt, CASE WHEN B.DAY IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS ZiLiberaLegala FROM tblZile2 A
LEFT JOIN HOLIDAYS B ON A.Zi=B.DAY
GO

CREATE TABLE ImportDateSablon(
	NumeTabela [nvarchar](200),
	ColoanaFisier [nvarchar](200),
	ColoanaBD [nvarchar](200) ,
	IdAuto [int] NOT NULL
 CONSTRAINT [PK_ImportDateSablon] PRIMARY KEY CLUSTERED 
(
	NumeTabela ASC,		
	IdAuto ASC
)WITH (PAD_INDEX = OFF, STATISTICS_NORECOMPUTE = OFF, IGNORE_DUP_KEY = OFF, ALLOW_ROW_LOCKS = ON, ALLOW_PAGE_LOCKS = ON) ON [PRIMARY]
) ON [PRIMARY]
GO

	NumeTabela [nvarchar](200),
	NumeColoana [nvarchar](200),
	Obligatoriu [int] NULL DEFAULT 0,
	ValoareImplicita [nvarchar](max) NULL DEFAULT '',
	IdAuto [int]  NOT NULL
 CONSTRAINT [PK_ImportDateNomen] PRIMARY KEY CLUSTERED 
(	
	IdAuto ASC
)WITH (PAD_INDEX = OFF, STATISTICS_NORECOMPUTE = OFF, IGNORE_DUP_KEY = OFF, ALLOW_ROW_LOCKS = ON, ALLOW_PAGE_LOCKS = ON) ON [PRIMARY]
) ON [PRIMARY]
GO

UPDATE tblMeniuri SET Pagina='Contracte\Lista' WHERE Pagina = 'ContracteLucru\Contract'
