INSERT INTO "Ptj_ContracteSchimburi"("IdContract", "TipSchimb", "Denumire", "IdProgram", "OraInceput", "OraInceputDeLa", "OraInceputLa", "OraSfarsit", "OraSfarsitDeLa", "OraSfarsitLa", "ModVerificare")
SELECT "ContractId", "ZiSapt", "ProgramDen", "ProgramId", "OraInceput", "OraInceputDeLa", "OraInceputLa", "OraSfarsit", "OraSfarsitDeLa", "OraSfarsitLa", "ModVerificare"
FROM (
SELECT DISTINCT A."Id" AS "ContractId", A."Denumire" AS "ContractDen", 1 AS "ZiSapt", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb1", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN COALESCE(A."Program1", A."Program0") ELSE COALESCE(B."IdProgram", D."IdProgram") END AS "ProgramId",
C."Denumire" AS "ProgramDen", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb7", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN C."OraIntrare" ELSE COALESCE(B."OraInceput", D."OraInceput") END AS "OraInceput", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb7", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."OraInceputDeLa", D."OraInceputDeLa") END AS "OraInceputDeLa", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb7", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."OraInceputLa", D."OraInceputLa") END AS "OraInceputLa", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb7", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN C."OraIesire" ELSE COALESCE(B."OraSfarsit", D."OraSfarsit") END AS "OraSfarsit", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb7", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."OraSfarsitDeLa", D."OraSfarsitDeLa") END AS "OraSfarsitDeLa", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb7", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."OraSfarsitLa", D."OraSfarsitLa") END AS "OraSfarsitLa", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb7", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."ModVerificare", D."ModVerificare") END AS "ModVerificare"
FROM "Ptj_Contracte" A
LEFT JOIN "Ptj_ContracteSchimburi" B ON A."Id"=B."IdContract" AND B."TipSchimb"=1 
LEFT JOIN "Ptj_ContracteSchimburi" D ON A."Id"=D."IdContract" AND D."TipSchimb"=0 
LEFT JOIN "Ptj_Programe" C ON C."Id" = (CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb1", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN COALESCE(A."Program1", A."Program0") ELSE COALESCE(B."IdProgram", D."IdProgram") END)
UNION
SELECT DISTINCT A."Id" AS "ContractId", A."Denumire" AS "ContractDen", 2 AS "ZiSapt", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb2", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN COALESCE(A."Program2", A."Program0") ELSE COALESCE(B."IdProgram", D."IdProgram") END AS "ProgramId",
C."Denumire" AS "ProgramDen", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb7", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN C."OraIntrare" ELSE COALESCE(B."OraInceput", D."OraInceput") END AS "OraInceput", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb7", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."OraInceputDeLa", D."OraInceputDeLa") END AS "OraInceputDeLa", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb7", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."OraInceputLa", D."OraInceputLa") END AS "OraInceputLa", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb7", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN C."OraIesire" ELSE COALESCE(B."OraSfarsit", D."OraSfarsit") END AS "OraSfarsit", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb7", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."OraSfarsitDeLa", D."OraSfarsitDeLa") END AS "OraSfarsitDeLa", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb7", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."OraSfarsitLa", D."OraSfarsitLa") END AS "OraSfarsitLa", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb7", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."ModVerificare", D."ModVerificare") END AS "ModVerificare"
FROM "Ptj_Contracte" A
LEFT JOIN "Ptj_ContracteSchimburi" B ON A."Id"=B."IdContract" AND B."TipSchimb"=2
LEFT JOIN "Ptj_ContracteSchimburi" D ON A."Id"=D."IdContract" AND D."TipSchimb"=0 
LEFT JOIN "Ptj_Programe" C ON C."Id" = (CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb2", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN COALESCE(A."Program2", A."Program0") ELSE COALESCE(B."IdProgram", D."IdProgram") END)
UNION
SELECT DISTINCT A."Id" AS "ContractId", A."Denumire" AS "ContractDen", 3 AS "ZiSapt", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb3", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN COALESCE(A."Program3", A."Program0") ELSE COALESCE(B."IdProgram", D."IdProgram") END AS "ProgramId",
C."Denumire" AS "ProgramDen", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb7", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN C."OraIntrare" ELSE COALESCE(B."OraInceput", D."OraInceput") END AS "OraInceput", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb7", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."OraInceputDeLa", D."OraInceputDeLa") END AS "OraInceputDeLa", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb7", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."OraInceputLa", D."OraInceputLa") END AS "OraInceputLa", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb7", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN C."OraIesire" ELSE COALESCE(B."OraSfarsit", D."OraSfarsit") END AS "OraSfarsit", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb7", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."OraSfarsitDeLa", D."OraSfarsitDeLa") END AS "OraSfarsitDeLa", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb7", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."OraSfarsitLa", D."OraSfarsitLa") END AS "OraSfarsitLa", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb7", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."ModVerificare", D."ModVerificare") END AS "ModVerificare"
FROM "Ptj_Contracte" A
LEFT JOIN "Ptj_ContracteSchimburi" B ON A."Id"=B."IdContract" AND B."TipSchimb"=3
LEFT JOIN "Ptj_ContracteSchimburi" D ON A."Id"=D."IdContract" AND D."TipSchimb"=0 
LEFT JOIN "Ptj_Programe" C ON C."Id" = (CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb3", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN COALESCE(A."Program3", A."Program0") ELSE COALESCE(B."IdProgram", D."IdProgram") END)
UNION
SELECT DISTINCT A."Id" AS "ContractId", A."Denumire" AS "ContractDen", 4 AS "ZiSapt", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb4", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN COALESCE(A."Program4", A."Program0") ELSE COALESCE(B."IdProgram", D."IdProgram") END AS "ProgramId",
C."Denumire" AS "ProgramDen", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb7", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN C."OraIntrare" ELSE COALESCE(B."OraInceput", D."OraInceput") END AS "OraInceput", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb7", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."OraInceputDeLa", D."OraInceputDeLa") END AS "OraInceputDeLa", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb7", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."OraInceputLa", D."OraInceputLa") END AS "OraInceputLa", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb7", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN C."OraIesire" ELSE COALESCE(B."OraSfarsit", D."OraSfarsit") END AS "OraSfarsit", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb7", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."OraSfarsitDeLa", D."OraSfarsitDeLa") END AS "OraSfarsitDeLa", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb7", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."OraSfarsitLa", D."OraSfarsitLa") END AS "OraSfarsitLa", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb7", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."ModVerificare", D."ModVerificare") END AS "ModVerificare"
FROM "Ptj_Contracte" A
LEFT JOIN "Ptj_ContracteSchimburi" B ON A."Id"=B."IdContract" AND B."TipSchimb"=4
LEFT JOIN "Ptj_ContracteSchimburi" D ON A."Id"=D."IdContract" AND D."TipSchimb"=0 
LEFT JOIN "Ptj_Programe" C ON C."Id" = (CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb4", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN COALESCE(A."Program4", A."Program0") ELSE COALESCE(B."IdProgram", D."IdProgram") END)
UNION
SELECT DISTINCT A."Id" AS "ContractId", A."Denumire" AS "ContractDen", 5 AS "ZiSapt", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb5", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN COALESCE(A."Program5", A."Program0") ELSE COALESCE(B."IdProgram", D."IdProgram") END AS "ProgramId",
C."Denumire" AS "ProgramDen", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb7", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN C."OraIntrare" ELSE COALESCE(B."OraInceput", D."OraInceput") END AS "OraInceput", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb7", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."OraInceputDeLa", D."OraInceputDeLa") END AS "OraInceputDeLa", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb7", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."OraInceputLa", D."OraInceputLa") END AS "OraInceputLa", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb7", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN C."OraIesire" ELSE COALESCE(B."OraSfarsit", D."OraSfarsit") END AS "OraSfarsit", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb7", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."OraSfarsitDeLa", D."OraSfarsitDeLa") END AS "OraSfarsitDeLa", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb7", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."OraSfarsitLa", D."OraSfarsitLa") END AS "OraSfarsitLa", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb7", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."ModVerificare", D."ModVerificare") END AS "ModVerificare"
FROM "Ptj_Contracte" A
LEFT JOIN "Ptj_ContracteSchimburi" B ON A."Id"=B."IdContract" AND B."TipSchimb"=5
LEFT JOIN "Ptj_ContracteSchimburi" D ON A."Id"=D."IdContract" AND D."TipSchimb"=0 
LEFT JOIN "Ptj_Programe" C ON C."Id" = (CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb5", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN COALESCE(A."Program5", A."Program0") ELSE COALESCE(B."IdProgram", D."IdProgram") END)
UNION
SELECT DISTINCT A."Id" AS "ContractId", A."Denumire" AS "ContractDen", 6 AS "ZiSapt", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb6", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN COALESCE(A."Program6", A."Program0") ELSE COALESCE(B."IdProgram", D."IdProgram") END AS "ProgramId",
C."Denumire" AS "ProgramDen", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb7", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN C."OraIntrare" ELSE COALESCE(B."OraInceput", D."OraInceput") END AS "OraInceput", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb7", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."OraInceputDeLa", D."OraInceputDeLa") END AS "OraInceputDeLa", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb7", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."OraInceputLa", D."OraInceputLa") END AS "OraInceputLa", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb7", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN C."OraIesire" ELSE COALESCE(B."OraSfarsit", D."OraSfarsit") END AS "OraSfarsit", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb7", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."OraSfarsitDeLa", D."OraSfarsitDeLa") END AS "OraSfarsitDeLa", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb7", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."OraSfarsitLa", D."OraSfarsitLa") END AS "OraSfarsitLa", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb7", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."ModVerificare", D."ModVerificare") END AS "ModVerificare"
FROM "Ptj_Contracte" A
LEFT JOIN "Ptj_ContracteSchimburi" B ON A."Id"=B."IdContract" AND B."TipSchimb"=6
LEFT JOIN "Ptj_ContracteSchimburi" D ON A."Id"=D."IdContract" AND D."TipSchimb"=0 
LEFT JOIN "Ptj_Programe" C ON C."Id" = (CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb6", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN COALESCE(A."Program6", A."Program0") ELSE COALESCE(B."IdProgram", D."IdProgram") END)
UNION
SELECT DISTINCT A."Id" AS "ContractId", A."Denumire" AS "ContractDen", 7 AS "ZiSapt", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb7", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN COALESCE(A."Program7", A."Program0") ELSE COALESCE(B."IdProgram", D."IdProgram") END AS "ProgramId",
C."Denumire" AS "ProgramDen", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb7", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN C."OraIntrare" ELSE COALESCE(B."OraInceput", D."OraInceput") END AS "OraInceput", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb7", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."OraInceputDeLa", D."OraInceputDeLa") END AS "OraInceputDeLa", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb7", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."OraInceputLa", D."OraInceputLa") END AS "OraInceputLa", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb7", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN C."OraIesire" ELSE COALESCE(B."OraSfarsit", D."OraSfarsit") END AS "OraSfarsit", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb7", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."OraSfarsitDeLa", D."OraSfarsitDeLa") END AS "OraSfarsitDeLa", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb7", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."OraSfarsitLa", D."OraSfarsitLa") END AS "OraSfarsitLa", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb7", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."ModVerificare", D."ModVerificare") END AS "ModVerificare"
FROM "Ptj_Contracte" A
LEFT JOIN "Ptj_ContracteSchimburi" B ON A."Id"=B."IdContract" AND B."TipSchimb"=7
LEFT JOIN "Ptj_ContracteSchimburi" D ON A."Id"=D."IdContract" AND D."TipSchimb"=0 
LEFT JOIN "Ptj_Programe" C ON C."Id" = (CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb7", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN COALESCE(A."Program7", A."Program0") ELSE COALESCE(B."IdProgram", D."IdProgram") END)
UNION
SELECT DISTINCT A."Id" AS "ContractId", A."Denumire" AS "ContractDen", 8 AS "ZiSapt", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb8", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN COALESCE(A."Program8", A."Program0") ELSE COALESCE(B."IdProgram", D."IdProgram") END AS "ProgramId",
C."Denumire" AS "ProgramDen", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb7", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN C."OraIntrare" ELSE COALESCE(B."OraInceput", D."OraInceput") END AS "OraInceput", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb7", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."OraInceputDeLa", D."OraInceputDeLa") END AS "OraInceputDeLa", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb7", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."OraInceputLa", D."OraInceputLa") END AS "OraInceputLa", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb7", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN C."OraIesire" ELSE COALESCE(B."OraSfarsit", D."OraSfarsit") END AS "OraSfarsit", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb7", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."OraSfarsitDeLa", D."OraSfarsitDeLa") END AS "OraSfarsitDeLa", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb7", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."OraSfarsitLa", D."OraSfarsitLa") END AS "OraSfarsitLa", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb7", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."ModVerificare", D."ModVerificare") END AS "ModVerificare"
FROM "Ptj_Contracte" A
LEFT JOIN "Ptj_ContracteSchimburi" B ON A."Id"=B."IdContract" AND B."TipSchimb"=8
LEFT JOIN "Ptj_ContracteSchimburi" D ON A."Id"=D."IdContract" AND D."TipSchimb"=0 
LEFT JOIN "Ptj_Programe" C ON C."Id" = (CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb8", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN COALESCE(A."Program8", A."Program0") ELSE COALESCE(B."IdProgram", D."IdProgram") END)
) X
WHERE X."ProgramId" IS NOT NULL
AND ("ContractId" * 1000000 + "ProgramId" * 10 + "ZiSapt") NOT IN 
(SELECT "IdContract" * 1000000 + "IdProgram" * 10 + "TipSchimb" FROM "Ptj_ContracteSchimburi") 
GO

CREATE TABLE Template(
	Id [int] NOT NULL,
	NumeSablon [nvarchar](200),
	NumeTabela [nvarchar](200)
 CONSTRAINT [PK_Template] PRIMARY KEY CLUSTERED 
(	
	Id ASC
)WITH (PAD_INDEX = OFF, STATISTICS_NORECOMPUTE = OFF, IGNORE_DUP_KEY = OFF, ALLOW_ROW_LOCKS = ON, ALLOW_PAGE_LOCKS = ON) ON [PRIMARY]
) ON [PRIMARY]
GO

CREATE TABLE TemplateCampuri(
	Id [int] NOT NULL,
	ColoanaBD [nvarchar](200),
	ColoanaFisier [nvarchar](200),
	Obligatoriu [int] NULL DEFAULT 0,
	ValoareImplicita [nvarchar](max) NULL DEFAULT '',
	IdAuto [int]  NOT NULL
 CONSTRAINT [PK_TemplateCampuri] PRIMARY KEY CLUSTERED 
(	
	Id ASC,
	IdAuto ASC
)WITH (PAD_INDEX = OFF, STATISTICS_NORECOMPUTE = OFF, IGNORE_DUP_KEY = OFF, ALLOW_ROW_LOCKS = ON, ALLOW_PAGE_LOCKS = ON) ON [PRIMARY]
) ON [PRIMARY]
GO

insert into template
select  CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1))) , 'Sablon ' + convert(nvarchar, CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))), numetabela from ImportDateSablon
group by NumeTabela
GO

insert into TemplateCampuri
select a.id, b.coloanaBD, b.ColoanaFisier, c.Obligatoriu, c.ValoareImplicita , CONVERT(int,ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY (SELECT 1)))
from template a
left join ImportDateSablon b on a.NumeTabela = b.NumeTabela
left join ImportDateNomen c on b.ColoanaBD = c.NumeColoana and a.NumeTabela = c.NumeTabela
GO

DROP table ImportDateSablon
GO
DROP TABLE ImportDateNomen
GO

                   WHERE F80603 = 1)
   BEGIN
       INSERT INTO f806 (F80601, F80602, F80603, F80604)
       VALUES (806, 1, 1, 'Invatamant primar')
   END
END
GO

   IF NOT EXISTS (SELECT * FROM f806 
                   WHERE F80603 = 2)
   BEGIN
       INSERT INTO f806 (F80601, F80602, F80603, F80604)
       VALUES (806, 1, 2, 'Invatamant gimnazial')
   END
END

CREATE TABLE tblTipInvatamant(
	Id [int] NOT NULL,
	Denumire [nvarchar](250),
	[USER_NO] [int] NULL,
	[TIME] [datetime] NULL,
 CONSTRAINT [PK_tblTipInvatamant] PRIMARY KEY CLUSTERED 
(	
	Id ASC
)WITH (PAD_INDEX = OFF, STATISTICS_NORECOMPUTE = OFF, IGNORE_DUP_KEY = OFF, ALLOW_ROW_LOCKS = ON, ALLOW_PAGE_LOCKS = ON) ON [PRIMARY]
) ON [PRIMARY]
GO

	Id [int] NOT NULL,
	Denumire [nvarchar](250),
	[USER_NO] [int] NULL,
	[TIME] [datetime] NULL,
 CONSTRAINT [PK_tblTipInstitutie] PRIMARY KEY CLUSTERED 
(	
	Id ASC
)WITH (PAD_INDEX = OFF, STATISTICS_NORECOMPUTE = OFF, IGNORE_DUP_KEY = OFF, ALLOW_ROW_LOCKS = ON, ALLOW_PAGE_LOCKS = ON) ON [PRIMARY]
) ON [PRIMARY]
GO

CREATE TABLE F100Studii(
	F10003 [int] ,
	IdTipInvatamant [int],
	IdNivel [int],
	NivelISCED [int],
	IdTipInstitutie [int], 
	NumeInstitutie varchar(250),
	NrClase int,
	SirutaLocalitate int,
	DeLaData datetime,
	LaData datetime,
	Specializare varchar(250),
	IdProfil int,
	IdDomeniu int,
	Calificare varchar(250),	
	IdAuto [int] NOT NULL IDENTITY,
	[USER_NO] [int] NULL,
	[TIME] [datetime] NULL,
 CONSTRAINT [PK_F100Studii] PRIMARY KEY CLUSTERED 
(	
	IdAuto ASC
)WITH (PAD_INDEX = OFF, STATISTICS_NORECOMPUTE = OFF, IGNORE_DUP_KEY = OFF, ALLOW_ROW_LOCKS = ON, ALLOW_PAGE_LOCKS = ON) ON [PRIMARY]
) ON [PRIMARY]
GO

-- #391 - Completare date in template evaluare
-- https://github.com/wizromRD/WizOne/issues/391

--  Competente

DECLARE @i INT
SET @i = 1
WHILE (@i <= 300)
BEGIN
    IF ((SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Eval_ConfigCompTemplate WHERE TemplateId=@i)=0)
	INSERT INTO Eval_ConfigCompTemplate(TemplateId, TemplateName) VALUES(@i, 'Template ' + CONVERT(nvarchar(10),@i));
    SET @i = @i + 1
END
GO

DECLARE @i INT
SET @i = 1
WHILE (@i <= 300)
BEGIN
    IF ((SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Eval_ConfigCompTemplateDetail WHERE TemplateId=@i AND ColumnName='Competenta')=0)
	INSERT INTO Eval_ConfigCompTemplateDetail(Id, TemplateId, ColumnName, Width, Obligatoriu, Citire, Editare, Vizibil, IdNomenclator) VALUES(1, @i, 'Competenta', 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, -99);
	IF ((SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Eval_ConfigCompTemplateDetail WHERE TemplateId=@i AND ColumnName='Pondere')=0)
	INSERT INTO Eval_ConfigCompTemplateDetail(Id, TemplateId, ColumnName, Width, Obligatoriu, Citire, Editare, Vizibil, IdNomenclator) VALUES(2, @i, 'Pondere', 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, -99);
	IF ((SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Eval_ConfigCompTemplateDetail WHERE TemplateId=@i AND ColumnName='Calificativ')=0)
	INSERT INTO Eval_ConfigCompTemplateDetail(Id, TemplateId, ColumnName, Width, Obligatoriu, Citire, Editare, Vizibil, IdNomenclator) VALUES(3, @i, 'Calificativ', 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, -99);
	IF ((SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Eval_ConfigCompTemplateDetail WHERE TemplateId=@i AND ColumnName='Explicatii')=0)
	INSERT INTO Eval_ConfigCompTemplateDetail(Id, TemplateId, ColumnName, Width, Obligatoriu, Citire, Editare, Vizibil, IdNomenclator) VALUES(4, @i, 'Explicatii', 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, -99);
	IF ((SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Eval_ConfigCompTemplateDetail WHERE TemplateId=@i AND ColumnName='ExplicatiiCalificativ')=0)
	INSERT INTO Eval_ConfigCompTemplateDetail(Id, TemplateId, ColumnName, Width, Obligatoriu, Citire, Editare, Vizibil, IdNomenclator) VALUES(5, @i, 'ExplicatiiCalificativ', 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, -99);

    SET @i = @i + 1
END
GO

--  Obiective

DECLARE @i INT
SET @i = 1
WHILE (@i <= 300)
BEGIN
    IF ((SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Eval_ConfigObTemplate WHERE TemplateId=@i)=0)
	INSERT INTO Eval_ConfigObTemplate(TemplateId, TemplateName, NrMinObiective, NrMaxObiective, PoateAdauga, PoateSterge, PoateModifica) VALUES(@i, 'Template ' + CONVERT(nvarchar(10),@i), 0, 900, 0, 0, 0);
    SET @i = @i + 1
END
GO

DECLARE @i INT
SET @i = 1
WHILE (@i <= 300)
BEGIN
    IF ((SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Eval_ConfigObTemplateDetail WHERE TemplateId=@i AND ColumnName='Obiectiv')=0)
	INSERT INTO Eval_ConfigObTemplateDetail(Id, TemplateId, ColumnName, Width, Obligatoriu, Citire, Editare, Vizibil, TipValoare, IdNomenclator) VALUES(1, @i, 'Obiectiv', 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, -99, -99);
	IF ((SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Eval_ConfigObTemplateDetail WHERE TemplateId=@i AND ColumnName='Activitate')=0)
	INSERT INTO Eval_ConfigObTemplateDetail(Id, TemplateId, ColumnName, Width, Obligatoriu, Citire, Editare, Vizibil, TipValoare, IdNomenclator) VALUES(2, @i, 'Activitate', 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, -99, -99);
	IF ((SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Eval_ConfigObTemplateDetail WHERE TemplateId=@i AND ColumnName='Pondere')=0)
	INSERT INTO Eval_ConfigObTemplateDetail(Id, TemplateId, ColumnName, Width, Obligatoriu, Citire, Editare, Vizibil, TipValoare, IdNomenclator) VALUES(3, @i, 'Pondere', 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, -99, -99);

	INSERT INTO Eval_ConfigObTemplateDetail(Id, TemplateId, ColumnName, Width, Obligatoriu, Citire, Editare, Vizibil, TipValoare, IdNomenclator) VALUES(4, @i, 'Descriere', 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, -99, -99);

	INSERT INTO Eval_ConfigObTemplateDetail(Id, TemplateId, ColumnName, Width, Obligatoriu, Citire, Editare, Vizibil, TipValoare, IdNomenclator) VALUES(5, @i, 'Target', 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, -99, -99);
	IF ((SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Eval_ConfigObTemplateDetail WHERE TemplateId=@i AND ColumnName='Termen')=0)
	INSERT INTO Eval_ConfigObTemplateDetail(Id, TemplateId, ColumnName, Width, Obligatoriu, Citire, Editare, Vizibil, TipValoare, IdNomenclator) VALUES(6, @i, 'Termen', 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, -99, -99);
	IF ((SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Eval_ConfigObTemplateDetail WHERE TemplateId=@i AND ColumnName='Realizat')=0)
	INSERT INTO Eval_ConfigObTemplateDetail(Id, TemplateId, ColumnName, Width, Obligatoriu, Citire, Editare, Vizibil, TipValoare, IdNomenclator) VALUES(7, @i, 'Realizat', 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, -99, -99);
	IF ((SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Eval_ConfigObTemplateDetail WHERE TemplateId=@i AND ColumnName='Calificativ')=0)
	INSERT INTO Eval_ConfigObTemplateDetail(Id, TemplateId, ColumnName, Width, Obligatoriu, Citire, Editare, Vizibil, TipValoare, IdNomenclator) VALUES(8, @i, 'Calificativ', 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, -99, -99);
	IF ((SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Eval_ConfigObTemplateDetail WHERE TemplateId=@i AND ColumnName='ExplicatiiCalificativ')=0)
	INSERT INTO Eval_ConfigObTemplateDetail(Id, TemplateId, ColumnName, Width, Obligatoriu, Citire, Editare, Vizibil, TipValoare, IdNomenclator) VALUES(9, @i, 'ExplicatiiCalificativ', 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, -99, -99);
	IF ((SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Eval_ConfigObTemplateDetail WHERE TemplateId=@i AND ColumnName='ColoanaSuplimentara1')=0)
	INSERT INTO Eval_ConfigObTemplateDetail(Id, TemplateId, ColumnName, Width, Obligatoriu, Citire, Editare, Vizibil, TipValoare, IdNomenclator) VALUES(10, @i, 'ColoanaSuplimentara1', 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, -99, -99);
	IF ((SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Eval_ConfigObTemplateDetail WHERE TemplateId=@i AND ColumnName='ColoanaSuplimentara2')=0)
	INSERT INTO Eval_ConfigObTemplateDetail(Id, TemplateId, ColumnName, Width, Obligatoriu, Citire, Editare, Vizibil, TipValoare, IdNomenclator) VALUES(11, @i, 'ColoanaSuplimentara2', 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, -99, -99);
	IF ((SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Eval_ConfigObTemplateDetail WHERE TemplateId=@i AND ColumnName='ColoanaSuplimentara3')=0)
	INSERT INTO Eval_ConfigObTemplateDetail(Id, TemplateId, ColumnName, Width, Obligatoriu, Citire, Editare, Vizibil, TipValoare, IdNomenclator) VALUES(12, @i, 'ColoanaSuplimentara3', 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, -99, -99);
	IF ((SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Eval_ConfigObTemplateDetail WHERE TemplateId=@i AND ColumnName='ColoanaSuplimentara4')=0)
	INSERT INTO Eval_ConfigObTemplateDetail(Id, TemplateId, ColumnName, Width, Obligatoriu, Citire, Editare, Vizibil, TipValoare, IdNomenclator) VALUES(13, @i, 'ColoanaSuplimentara4', 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, -99, -99);

    SET @i = @i + 1
END

--https://github.com/wizromRD/WizOne/issues/461
--Scriptul care insereaza in Ptj_ContracteSchimburi insereaza linii in plus pentru zilele in care exista un singur schimb #461

INSERT INTO "Ptj_ContracteSchimburi"("IdContract", "TipSchimb", "Denumire", "IdProgram", "OraInceput", "OraInceputDeLa", "OraInceputLa", "OraSfarsit", "OraSfarsitDeLa", "OraSfarsitLa", "ModVerificare")
SELECT "ContractId", "ZiSapt", "ProgramDen", "ProgramId", "OraInceput", "OraInceputDeLa", "OraInceputLa", "OraSfarsit", "OraSfarsitDeLa", "OraSfarsitLa", "ModVerificare"
FROM (
SELECT DISTINCT A."Id" AS "ContractId", A."Denumire" AS "ContractDen", 1 AS "ZiSapt", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb1", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN COALESCE(A."Program1", A."Program0") ELSE COALESCE(B."IdProgram", D."IdProgram") END AS "ProgramId",
C."Denumire" AS "ProgramDen", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb1", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN C."OraIntrare" ELSE COALESCE(B."OraInceput", D."OraInceput") END AS "OraInceput", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb1", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."OraInceputDeLa", D."OraInceputDeLa") END AS "OraInceputDeLa", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb1", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."OraInceputLa", D."OraInceputLa") END AS "OraInceputLa", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb1", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN C."OraIesire" ELSE COALESCE(B."OraSfarsit", D."OraSfarsit") END AS "OraSfarsit", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb1", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."OraSfarsitDeLa", D."OraSfarsitDeLa") END AS "OraSfarsitDeLa", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb1", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."OraSfarsitLa", D."OraSfarsitLa") END AS "OraSfarsitLa", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb1", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."ModVerificare", D."ModVerificare") END AS "ModVerificare"
FROM "Ptj_Contracte" A
LEFT JOIN "Ptj_ContracteSchimburi" B ON A."Id"=B."IdContract" AND B."TipSchimb"=1 
LEFT JOIN "Ptj_ContracteSchimburi" D ON A."Id"=D."IdContract" AND D."TipSchimb"=0 
LEFT JOIN "Ptj_Programe" C ON C."Id" = (CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb1", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN COALESCE(A."Program1", A."Program0") ELSE COALESCE(B."IdProgram", D."IdProgram") END)
UNION
SELECT DISTINCT A."Id" AS "ContractId", A."Denumire" AS "ContractDen", 2 AS "ZiSapt", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb2", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN COALESCE(A."Program2", A."Program0") ELSE COALESCE(B."IdProgram", D."IdProgram") END AS "ProgramId",
C."Denumire" AS "ProgramDen", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb2", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN C."OraIntrare" ELSE COALESCE(B."OraInceput", D."OraInceput") END AS "OraInceput", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb2", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."OraInceputDeLa", D."OraInceputDeLa") END AS "OraInceputDeLa", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb2", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."OraInceputLa", D."OraInceputLa") END AS "OraInceputLa", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb2", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN C."OraIesire" ELSE COALESCE(B."OraSfarsit", D."OraSfarsit") END AS "OraSfarsit", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb2", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."OraSfarsitDeLa", D."OraSfarsitDeLa") END AS "OraSfarsitDeLa", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb2", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."OraSfarsitLa", D."OraSfarsitLa") END AS "OraSfarsitLa", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb2", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."ModVerificare", D."ModVerificare") END AS "ModVerificare"
FROM "Ptj_Contracte" A
LEFT JOIN "Ptj_ContracteSchimburi" B ON A."Id"=B."IdContract" AND B."TipSchimb"=2
LEFT JOIN "Ptj_ContracteSchimburi" D ON A."Id"=D."IdContract" AND D."TipSchimb"=0 
LEFT JOIN "Ptj_Programe" C ON C."Id" = (CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb2", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN COALESCE(A."Program2", A."Program0") ELSE COALESCE(B."IdProgram", D."IdProgram") END)
UNION
SELECT DISTINCT A."Id" AS "ContractId", A."Denumire" AS "ContractDen", 3 AS "ZiSapt", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb3", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN COALESCE(A."Program3", A."Program0") ELSE COALESCE(B."IdProgram", D."IdProgram") END AS "ProgramId",
C."Denumire" AS "ProgramDen", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb3", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN C."OraIntrare" ELSE COALESCE(B."OraInceput", D."OraInceput") END AS "OraInceput", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb3", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."OraInceputDeLa", D."OraInceputDeLa") END AS "OraInceputDeLa", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb3", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."OraInceputLa", D."OraInceputLa") END AS "OraInceputLa", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb3", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN C."OraIesire" ELSE COALESCE(B."OraSfarsit", D."OraSfarsit") END AS "OraSfarsit", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb3", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."OraSfarsitDeLa", D."OraSfarsitDeLa") END AS "OraSfarsitDeLa", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb3", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."OraSfarsitLa", D."OraSfarsitLa") END AS "OraSfarsitLa", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb3", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."ModVerificare", D."ModVerificare") END AS "ModVerificare"
FROM "Ptj_Contracte" A
LEFT JOIN "Ptj_ContracteSchimburi" B ON A."Id"=B."IdContract" AND B."TipSchimb"=3
LEFT JOIN "Ptj_ContracteSchimburi" D ON A."Id"=D."IdContract" AND D."TipSchimb"=0 
LEFT JOIN "Ptj_Programe" C ON C."Id" = (CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb3", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN COALESCE(A."Program3", A."Program0") ELSE COALESCE(B."IdProgram", D."IdProgram") END)
UNION
SELECT DISTINCT A."Id" AS "ContractId", A."Denumire" AS "ContractDen", 4 AS "ZiSapt", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb4", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN COALESCE(A."Program4", A."Program0") ELSE COALESCE(B."IdProgram", D."IdProgram") END AS "ProgramId",
C."Denumire" AS "ProgramDen", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb4", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN C."OraIntrare" ELSE COALESCE(B."OraInceput", D."OraInceput") END AS "OraInceput", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb4", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."OraInceputDeLa", D."OraInceputDeLa") END AS "OraInceputDeLa", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb4", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."OraInceputLa", D."OraInceputLa") END AS "OraInceputLa", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb4", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN C."OraIesire" ELSE COALESCE(B."OraSfarsit", D."OraSfarsit") END AS "OraSfarsit", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb4", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."OraSfarsitDeLa", D."OraSfarsitDeLa") END AS "OraSfarsitDeLa", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb4", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."OraSfarsitLa", D."OraSfarsitLa") END AS "OraSfarsitLa", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb4", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."ModVerificare", D."ModVerificare") END AS "ModVerificare"
FROM "Ptj_Contracte" A
LEFT JOIN "Ptj_ContracteSchimburi" B ON A."Id"=B."IdContract" AND B."TipSchimb"=4
LEFT JOIN "Ptj_ContracteSchimburi" D ON A."Id"=D."IdContract" AND D."TipSchimb"=0 
LEFT JOIN "Ptj_Programe" C ON C."Id" = (CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb4", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN COALESCE(A."Program4", A."Program0") ELSE COALESCE(B."IdProgram", D."IdProgram") END)
UNION
SELECT DISTINCT A."Id" AS "ContractId", A."Denumire" AS "ContractDen", 5 AS "ZiSapt", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb5", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN COALESCE(A."Program5", A."Program0") ELSE COALESCE(B."IdProgram", D."IdProgram") END AS "ProgramId",
C."Denumire" AS "ProgramDen", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb5", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN C."OraIntrare" ELSE COALESCE(B."OraInceput", D."OraInceput") END AS "OraInceput", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb5", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."OraInceputDeLa", D."OraInceputDeLa") END AS "OraInceputDeLa", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb5", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."OraInceputLa", D."OraInceputLa") END AS "OraInceputLa", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb5", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN C."OraIesire" ELSE COALESCE(B."OraSfarsit", D."OraSfarsit") END AS "OraSfarsit", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb5", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."OraSfarsitDeLa", D."OraSfarsitDeLa") END AS "OraSfarsitDeLa", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb5", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."OraSfarsitLa", D."OraSfarsitLa") END AS "OraSfarsitLa", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb5", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."ModVerificare", D."ModVerificare") END AS "ModVerificare"
FROM "Ptj_Contracte" A
LEFT JOIN "Ptj_ContracteSchimburi" B ON A."Id"=B."IdContract" AND B."TipSchimb"=5
LEFT JOIN "Ptj_ContracteSchimburi" D ON A."Id"=D."IdContract" AND D."TipSchimb"=0 
LEFT JOIN "Ptj_Programe" C ON C."Id" = (CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb5", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN COALESCE(A."Program5", A."Program0") ELSE COALESCE(B."IdProgram", D."IdProgram") END)
UNION
SELECT DISTINCT A."Id" AS "ContractId", A."Denumire" AS "ContractDen", 6 AS "ZiSapt", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb6", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN COALESCE(A."Program6", A."Program0") ELSE COALESCE(B."IdProgram", D."IdProgram") END AS "ProgramId",
C."Denumire" AS "ProgramDen", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb6", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN C."OraIntrare" ELSE COALESCE(B."OraInceput", D."OraInceput") END AS "OraInceput", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb6", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."OraInceputDeLa", D."OraInceputDeLa") END AS "OraInceputDeLa", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb6", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."OraInceputLa", D."OraInceputLa") END AS "OraInceputLa", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb6", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN C."OraIesire" ELSE COALESCE(B."OraSfarsit", D."OraSfarsit") END AS "OraSfarsit", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb6", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."OraSfarsitDeLa", D."OraSfarsitDeLa") END AS "OraSfarsitDeLa", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb6", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."OraSfarsitLa", D."OraSfarsitLa") END AS "OraSfarsitLa", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb6", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."ModVerificare", D."ModVerificare") END AS "ModVerificare"
FROM "Ptj_Contracte" A
LEFT JOIN "Ptj_ContracteSchimburi" B ON A."Id"=B."IdContract" AND B."TipSchimb"=6
LEFT JOIN "Ptj_ContracteSchimburi" D ON A."Id"=D."IdContract" AND D."TipSchimb"=0 
LEFT JOIN "Ptj_Programe" C ON C."Id" = (CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb6", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN COALESCE(A."Program6", A."Program0") ELSE COALESCE(B."IdProgram", D."IdProgram") END)
UNION
SELECT DISTINCT A."Id" AS "ContractId", A."Denumire" AS "ContractDen", 7 AS "ZiSapt", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb7", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN COALESCE(A."Program7", A."Program0") ELSE COALESCE(B."IdProgram", D."IdProgram") END AS "ProgramId",
C."Denumire" AS "ProgramDen", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb7", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN C."OraIntrare" ELSE COALESCE(B."OraInceput", D."OraInceput") END AS "OraInceput", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb7", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."OraInceputDeLa", D."OraInceputDeLa") END AS "OraInceputDeLa", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb7", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."OraInceputLa", D."OraInceputLa") END AS "OraInceputLa", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb7", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN C."OraIesire" ELSE COALESCE(B."OraSfarsit", D."OraSfarsit") END AS "OraSfarsit", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb7", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."OraSfarsitDeLa", D."OraSfarsitDeLa") END AS "OraSfarsitDeLa", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb7", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."OraSfarsitLa", D."OraSfarsitLa") END AS "OraSfarsitLa", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb7", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."ModVerificare", D."ModVerificare") END AS "ModVerificare"
FROM "Ptj_Contracte" A
LEFT JOIN "Ptj_ContracteSchimburi" B ON A."Id"=B."IdContract" AND B."TipSchimb"=7
LEFT JOIN "Ptj_ContracteSchimburi" D ON A."Id"=D."IdContract" AND D."TipSchimb"=0 
LEFT JOIN "Ptj_Programe" C ON C."Id" = (CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb7", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN COALESCE(A."Program7", A."Program0") ELSE COALESCE(B."IdProgram", D."IdProgram") END)
UNION
SELECT DISTINCT A."Id" AS "ContractId", A."Denumire" AS "ContractDen", 8 AS "ZiSapt", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb8", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN COALESCE(A."Program8", A."Program0") ELSE COALESCE(B."IdProgram", D."IdProgram") END AS "ProgramId",
C."Denumire" AS "ProgramDen", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb8", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN C."OraIntrare" ELSE COALESCE(B."OraInceput", D."OraInceput") END AS "OraInceput", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb8", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."OraInceputDeLa", D."OraInceputDeLa") END AS "OraInceputDeLa", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb8", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."OraInceputLa", D."OraInceputLa") END AS "OraInceputLa", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb8", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN C."OraIesire" ELSE COALESCE(B."OraSfarsit", D."OraSfarsit") END AS "OraSfarsit", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb8", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."OraSfarsitDeLa", D."OraSfarsitDeLa") END AS "OraSfarsitDeLa", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb8", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."OraSfarsitLa", D."OraSfarsitLa") END AS "OraSfarsitLa", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb8", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."ModVerificare", D."ModVerificare") END AS "ModVerificare"
FROM "Ptj_Contracte" A
LEFT JOIN "Ptj_ContracteSchimburi" B ON A."Id"=B."IdContract" AND B."TipSchimb"=8
LEFT JOIN "Ptj_ContracteSchimburi" D ON A."Id"=D."IdContract" AND D."TipSchimb"=0 
LEFT JOIN "Ptj_Programe" C ON C."Id" = (CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb8", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN COALESCE(A."Program8", A."Program0") ELSE COALESCE(B."IdProgram", D."IdProgram") END)
) X
WHERE X."ProgramId" IS NOT NULL
AND ("ContractId" * 1000000 + "ProgramId" * 10 + "ZiSapt") NOT IN 
(SELECT "IdContract" * 1000000 + "IdProgram" * 10 + "TipSchimb" FROM "Ptj_ContracteSchimburi") 
GO

CREATE FUNCTION [dbo].[CalculCO] (
         @f10003 INT,
    @zi datetime,
    @mod int,
    @grila int
)
    RETURNS @CalculCO TABLE (
        ZileCuveniteAn int,
        ZileCuvenite int,
        ZileCuveniteZi int,
        ZileAnPrecedent int
    )
 AS

 BEGIN

 declare @ZileCuveniteAn int, @ZileCuvenite int, @ZileCuveniteZi int, @ZileAnPrecedent int, @ZileAngajare int, @ZileAngajareZi int, @ZileSuspendare int, @ZileSuspendareZi int,
 @PrimaZiAn date, @UltimaZiAn date, @TipCalcul int, @ZileSuplimentare int, @LuniVechime int, @CalculCOProp18Ani int, @CalculCOPropHand int, @ZileAn int,
 @SuspendariExcluse nvarchar(100), @f10023 datetime


-- @TipCalcul
--  1 -- se calculeaza vechimea in munca in ultima zi din an
-- 2. se calculeaza vechimea in munca in prima zi din an
--  3 se calculeaza vechimea in munca la data angajarii
--   11 -- se calculeaza vechimea in companie in ultima zi din an
-- 12 se calculeaza vechimea in companie in prima zi din an
--  13 se calculeaza vechimea in companie la data angajarii
--   21 -- se calculeaza vechimea de la data angajarii in ultima zi din an
-- 22 se calculeaza vechimea de la data angajarii in prima zi din an
--  23 se calculeaza vechimea de la data angajarii la data angajarii

-- 99 - particular

select @ZileAn = 365
if  year(@zi) % 4 = 0
    select @ZileAn = 366;

if isnull(@grila,0)= 0
    select @grila = f10072 from f100 where f10003 = @f10003;


select @f10023 = DataPlecare from DamiDataPlecare(@f10003, @zi);

 Select @ZileSuplimentare = Convert(int,isnull((select "Valoare" from "tblParametrii" where "Nume"='NrZilePersoanaDizabilitatiSauMaiMica18Ani'),3));
 Select @TipCalcul = Convert(int,isnull((select "Valoare" from "tblParametrii" where "Nume"='ModCalculZileCOCuvenite'),1));
 Select @CalculCOProp18Ani = Convert(int,isnull((select "Valoare" from "tblParametrii" where "Nume"='ModCalculZileCO_Proportional_18Ani'),0));
 Select @CalculCOPropHand = Convert(int,isnull((select "Valoare" from "tblParametrii" where "Nume"='ModCalculZileCO_Proportional_Handicap'),0));
 Select @SuspendariExcluse = Convert(nvarchar(100),isnull((select "Valoare" from "tblParametrii" where "Nume"='ModCalculZileCO_SuspendariExcluse'),' '));




Select @PrimaZiAn = CASE WHEN cast(F10022 as date) < convert(varchar, year(@zi))  +  '-01-01'  THEN convert(varchar, year(@zi))  +  '-01-01'  ELSE cast(F10022 as date) END,
 @UltimaZiAn = CASE WHEN cast(@f10023 as date) < convert(varchar, year(@zi))  +  '-12-31'  THEN cast(@f10023 as date) ELSE convert(varchar, year(@zi))  +  '-12-31'  END
 from (select * from F100 where f10003 = @F10003) a ;

Select @ZileAngajare = datediff(day, @PrimaZiAn, @UltimaZiAn)+1 ,
 @ZileAngajareZi = datediff(day, @PrimaZiAn,  (CASE WHEN cast(@f10023 as date) < @zi THEN cast(@f10023 as date) ELSE @zi END))+1
 from (select * from F100 where f10003 = @F10003) a  ;

If @TipCalcul = 1
     Select @LuniVechime = ISNULL(convert(int,substring(F100644,1,2)),0) * 12 + ISNULL(convert(int,substring(F100644,3,2)),0) + DATEDIFF (MONTH,   (select convert(nvarchar(4),F01011) + '-' +
            convert(nvarchar(4),F01012) + '-01' from F010),convert(varchar, year(@zi))  +  '-12-31') from f100 where f10003 = @f10003
Else if @TipCalcul = 2
     Select @LuniVechime = ISNULL(convert(int,substring(F100644,1,2)),0) * 12 + ISNULL(convert(int,substring(F100644,3,2)),0) + DATEDIFF (MONTH,   (select convert(nvarchar(4),F01011) + '-' +
            convert(nvarchar(4),F01012) + '-01' from F010),convert(varchar, year(@zi))  +  '-01-01') from f100 where f10003 = @f10003
Else if @TipCalcul = 3
     Select @LuniVechime = ISNULL(convert(int,substring(F100644,1,2)),0) * 12 + ISNULL(convert(int,substring(F100644,3,2)),0) + DATEDIFF (MONTH,   (select convert(nvarchar(4),F01011) + '-' +
            convert(nvarchar(4),F01012) + '-01' from F010), @zi ) from f100 where f10003 = @f10003
Else If @TipCalcul = 11
     Select @LuniVechime = ISNULL(convert(int,substring(F100643,1,2)),0) * 12 + ISNULL(convert(int,substring(F100643,3,2)),0) + DATEDIFF (MONTH,   (select convert(nvarchar(4),F01011) + '-' +
            convert(nvarchar(4),F01012) + '-01' from F010),convert(varchar, year(@zi))  +  '-12-31') from f100 where f10003 = @f10003
Else if @TipCalcul = 12
     Select @LuniVechime = ISNULL(convert(int,substring(F100643,1,2)),0) * 12 + ISNULL(convert(int,substring(F100643,3,2)),0) + DATEDIFF (MONTH,   (select convert(nvarchar(4),F01011) + '-' +
            convert(nvarchar(4),F01012) + '-01' from F010),convert(varchar, year(@zi))  +  '-01-01') from f100 where f10003 = @f10003
Else if @TipCalcul = 13
     Select @LuniVechime = ISNULL(convert(int,substring(F100643,1,2)),0) * 12 + ISNULL(convert(int,substring(F100643,3,2)),0) + DATEDIFF (MONTH,   (select convert(nvarchar(4),F01011) + '-' +
            convert(nvarchar(4),F01012) + '-01' from F010), @zi ) from f100 where f10003 = @f10003
Else If @TipCalcul = 21
     Select @LuniVechime =  DATEDIFF (MONTH, F10022,convert(varchar, year(@zi))  +  '-12-31')
     - case when day(f10022) > day(convert(varchar, year(@zi))  +  '-12-31') then 1 else 0 end from f100 where f10003 = @f10003
Else if @TipCalcul = 22
     Select @LuniVechime =  DATEDIFF (MONTH, F10022,convert(varchar, year(@zi))  +  '-01-01')
     - case when day(f10022) > day(convert(varchar, year(@zi))  +  '-01-01') then 1 else 0 end from f100 where f10003 = @f10003
Else if @TipCalcul = 23
    Select @LuniVechime = DATEDIFF (MONTH, F10022, @zi )
     - case when day(f10022) > day(@zi)  then 1 else 0 end from f100 where f10003 = @f10003
Else if @TipCalcul = 99
     select @LuniVechime =  DATEDIFF (MONTH,  case when f10022 <= '2018-02-14' then '2018-02-14' else f10022 end , @zi )
     - case when ( case when f10022 <= '2018-02-14' then 14 else day(f10022) end) > day(@zi)  then 1 else 0 end
    from f100 where f10003 = @f10003;

if isnull(@LuniVechime,0) < =0 
	 select @LuniVechime = 0;


If @mod <> 1
     select @ZileCuveniteAn = CuveniteAn from ptj_tblzileco where an=year(@zi) and f10003 = @f10003
 else
    select @ZileCuveniteAn =     c.F02615
    + CASE WHEN ISNULL(a.F10027,0)>=2 THEN
     convert(int, round( case when @CalculCOPropHand = 0 or f100271 = '2100-01-01' or f100271 = '1900-01-01' then 1 else
     (datediff(day, @PrimaZiAn, (case when  f100271 <= @UltimaZiAn  then f100271 else @UltimaZiAn end) )+1 ) / convert(float, @ZileAn)
    end * @ZileSuplimentare,0)) ELSE 0 END
    +  case when dateadd(year,18,f10021) >= @PrimaZiAn  then
    convert(int, round( case when @CalculCOProp18Ani = 0 then 1 else
     (datediff(day, @PrimaZiAn, (case when  dateadd(year, 18, f10021) <= @UltimaZiAn  then dateadd(year, 18, f10021)  else @UltimaZiAn end) )+1 ) / convert(float, @ZileAn)
    end * @ZileSuplimentare,0))  else 0 end
        from (select * from F100 where f10003 = @F10003) a    left join F026 c on convert(int,@grila) = c.F02604 and
        (convert(int,c.F02610/100) * 12) <= @LuniVechime and @LuniVechime < (convert(int,c.F02611/100) * 12)  where (year(@zi)  between year(F10022) and year(F10023) ) and a.F10003= @f10003 ;



    with xx as  ( select f111.f11103 Marca, f111.f11105 de_la_data, case when f111.f11107='2100-01-01' then f111.f11106 else dateadd(d,-1,f111.f11107) end la_data from f111
	 inner join
  (select a.f11103, a.f11105, case when a.f11107='2100-01-01' then a.f11106 else dateadd(d,-1,a.f11107) end f11107, a.time, max(b.time) timp from F111 a inner join f111 b  on
  a.F11103 = b.F11103 and  (a.f11105 <= case when b.f11107='2100-01-01' then b.f11106 else dateadd(d,-1,b.f11107) end   and b.f11105 <= case when a.f11107='2100-01-01'
  then a.f11106 else dateadd(d,-1,a.f11107) end)  group by a.f11103, a.f11105, case when a.f11107='2100-01-01' then a.f11106 else dateadd(d,-1,a.f11107) end, a.time) t  on f111.f11103 = t.f11103 and
  f111.f11105 = t.f11105 and   case when f111.f11107='2100-01-01' then f111.f11106 else dateadd(d,-1,f111.f11107) end = t.f11107 and f111.time = t.timp 
  where CHARINDEX(concat(',',ltrim(rtrim(convert(nvarchar(100),f111.f11104))),','), concat(',',ltrim(rtrim(@SuspendariExcluse)),','))  = 0 
   union all
  select f10003 Marca, datainceput de_la_data, datasfarsit la_data  from ptj_cereri inner join Ptj_tblAbsente on Ptj_Cereri.IdAbsenta = Ptj_tblAbsente.id  where
  ptj_cereri.IdStare=3 and isnull(Ptj_tblAbsente.AbsenteCFPInCalculCO,0) = 1  ),
   yy as  (select distinct a.marca, min(b.de_la_data) de_la_data, max(b.la_data) la_data from xx a  inner join xx b on a.marca = b.marca and
   (a.de_la_data <= b.la_data and b.de_la_data <= a.la_data)  group by a.marca, a.de_la_data, a.la_data),
   f111_2 as   (select distinct a.marca f11103, min(b.de_la_data) f11105, max(b.la_data)  f11107 from yy a  inner join yy b on a.marca = b.marca and (a.de_la_data <=
    b.la_data and b.de_la_data <= a.la_data)  group by a.marca, a.de_la_data, a.la_data)

  select  @ZileSuspendare= (select COALESCE(SUM(datediff(d,CASE WHEN F11105 <  CONVERT(date,convert(varchar, year(@zi))  +  '-01-01') THEN CONVERT(date,convert(varchar, year(@zi))  +  '-01-01') else F11105 END,CASE WHEN F11107 > CONVERT(date,convert(varchar, year(@zi))  +  '-12-31') THEN CONVERT(date,convert(varchar, year(@zi))  +  '-12-31') else F11107 END) + 1) ,0)
  from (select * from F100 where f10003 = @F10003) a  join f111_2 Z on a.f10003 = z.f11103
   and F11105 <= F11107 AND F11107 >= CONVERT(date,convert(varchar, year(@zi))  +  '-01-01') AND F11105 <= CONVERT(date,convert(varchar, year(@zi))  +  '-12-31')) ,
  @ZileSuspendareZi = (select COALESCE(SUM(datediff(d,CASE WHEN F11105 <
   CONVERT(date,convert(varchar, year(@zi))  +  '-01-01') THEN CONVERT(date,convert(varchar, year(@zi))  +  '-01-01') else F11105 END,CASE WHEN F11107 > CONVERT(date,@zi) THEN CONVERT(date,@zi) else F11107 END)+1) ,0)
   from (select * from F100 where f10003 = @F10003) a  join f111_2 Z on a.f10003 = z.f11103
   and F11105 <= F11107 AND F11107 >= CONVERT(date,convert(varchar, year(@zi))  +  '-01-01') AND F11105 <= CONVERT(date,@zi)) ;

   select @ZileCuvenite = case when @mod= 1 then round(convert(float,@ZileCuveniteAn * (@ZileAngajare - isnull(@ZileSuspendare,0))) /CONVERT(float,@ZileAn),0)
             else (select Cuvenite from Ptj_tblZileCO where f10003 = @f10003 and an = year(@zi)) end;

   select @ZileCuveniteZi =  round(convert(float, @ZileCuveniteAn * (@ZileAngajareZi - isnull(@ZileSuspendareZi,0))) /CONVERT(float,@ZileAn),0);



 INSERT INTO @CalculCO
  SELECT @ZileCuveniteAn, isnull(@ZileCuvenite,0), @ZileCuveniteZi, isnull((select SoldAnterior from Ptj_tblZileCO where f10003 = @f10003 and an=year(@zi)),0);

   RETURN;
  END

  GO



  CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[CalculCOProc]
     @f10003 INT,
	@zi datetime,
	@mod int = 1,
	@grila int = 0
AS

BEGIN

DECLARE @ZileCuveniteAn INT;
DECLARE @ZileCuvenite INT;
DECLARE @ZileCuveniteZi INT;
DECLARE @ZileAnPrecedent INT;
DECLARE @cnt INT;

SELECT @ZileCuveniteAn=ZileCuveniteAn, @ZileCuvenite=ZileCuvenite,@ZileCuveniteZi=ZileCuveniteZi,@ZileAnPrecedent=ZileAnPrecedent  FROM CalculCO(@f10003, @zi, @mod, @grila)

SELECT @cnt = COUNT(*) FROM Ptj_tblZileCO WHERE F10003 = @f10003 and An = year(@zi)

    if (year(@zi) = (SELECT F01011 FROM F010))
	UPDATE F100 set F100642 =  @ZileCuveniteAn, F100995 =  @ZileCuvenite, F100996 = @ZileAnPrecedent WHERE
	F10003 = @f10003;

  if (year(@zi) >= (SELECT F01011 FROM F010))
   if(@cnt > 0)
		UPDATE Ptj_tblZileCO set CuveniteAn = @ZileCuveniteAn, Cuvenite = @ZileCuvenite WHERE
		F10003 = @f10003 and An = year(@zi);
	else
		INSERT INTO Ptj_tblZileCO (F10003, An, Cuvenite, SoldAnterior, Efectuate, CuveniteAn)
		VALUES (@f10003, year(@zi), @ZileCuvenite, 0, 0, @ZileCuveniteAn)
END

GO


Declare @Querydef1 nvarchar(max)
 
SELECT @Querydef1 = REPLACE (REPLACE (sm.definition, 'CREATE VIEW', 'ALTER VIEW'), ', B.Efectuate', ', B.Efectuate, B.Anulate')
FROM sys.sql_modules sm JOIN sys.objects o
ON sm.object_id = o.object_id
WHERE
o.name = 'SituatieZileAbsente' AND o.type = 'V'
 
exec sp_executeSql @querydef1
GO
  Declare @Querydef2 nvarchar(max)
 
SELECT @Querydef2 = REPLACE (REPLACE (sm.definition, 'CREATE VIEW', 'ALTER VIEW'), ',B.Efectuate', ',B.Efectuate, B.Anulate')
FROM sys.sql_modules sm JOIN sys.objects o
ON sm.object_id = o.object_id
WHERE
o.name = 'SituatieZileAbsente' AND o.type = 'V'
 
exec sp_executeSql @querydef2
 
GO
 
Declare @Querydef3 nvarchar(max)
 
SELECT @Querydef3 = REPLACE (REPLACE (sm.definition, 'CREATE VIEW', 'ALTER VIEW'), 'ISNULL(B.Efectuate, 0)', 'ISNULL(B.Efectuate, 0) + ISNULL(B.Anulate,0)')
FROM sys.sql_modules sm JOIN sys.objects o
ON sm.object_id = o.object_id
WHERE
o.name = 'SituatieZileAbsente' AND o.type = 'V'
 
exec sp_executeSql @querydef3
 
GO
Declare @Querydef4 nvarchar(max)
 
SELECT @Querydef4 = REPLACE (REPLACE (sm.definition, 'CREATE VIEW', 'ALTER VIEW'), 'ISNULL(B.Efectuate,0)', 'ISNULL(B.Efectuate,0) + ISNULL(B.Anulate,0)')
FROM sys.sql_modules sm JOIN sys.objects o
ON sm.object_id = o.object_id
WHERE
o.name = 'SituatieZileAbsente' AND o.type = 'V'
 
exec sp_executeSql @querydef4
GO
 
Declare @Querydef5 nvarchar(max)
 
SELECT @Querydef5 = REPLACE (REPLACE (sm.definition, 'CREATE VIEW', 'ALTER VIEW'), 'COALESCE(B.Efectuate, 0)', 'COALESCE(B.Efectuate, 0) + COALESCE(B.Anulate,0)')
FROM sys.sql_modules sm JOIN sys.objects o
ON sm.object_id = o.object_id
WHERE
o.name = 'SituatieZileAbsente' AND o.type = 'V'
 
exec sp_executeSql @querydef5
GO
Declare @Querydef6 nvarchar(max)
 
SELECT @Querydef6 = REPLACE (REPLACE (sm.definition, 'CREATE VIEW', 'ALTER VIEW'), 'COALESCE(B.Efectuate,0)', 'COALESCE(B.Efectuate,0) + COALESCE(B.Anulate,0)')
FROM sys.sql_modules sm JOIN sys.objects o
ON sm.object_id = o.object_id
WHERE
o.name = 'SituatieZileAbsente' AND o.type = 'V'
 
exec sp_executeSql @querydef6
GO

CREATE FUNCTION [dbo].[DamiSubdept] (@f10003 int, @dt DATE) 
RETURNs table AS 
return 

SELECT top 1 Subdept =   Subdept, Data_Subdept = data_Subdept  from 
(
SELECT top 1 1 as rank, F70403 marca,  F70418 Subdept,  f70406 data_Subdept,  F70406 Data from f704   WHERE F70404=5 AND F70406 <= @dt and F70403 = @f10003 ORDER BY F70406 DESC
union 
select 2 as rank, f100.f10003 marca, F100958 Subdept, case when coalesce(year(F100910),2100) in (1900,2100) then F10022 else f100910 end data_Subdept, 
case when coalesce(100*year(F100910)+month(F100910), 100*2100+1) = 100 * f01011 + f01012 then F100910 else  DATEFROMPARTS(f01011, f01012, 1) end data 
from f100 
inner join f1001 on f100.F10003=f1001.F10003
join f010 on 1=1 where f100.f10003 =@f10003 and case when coalesce(100*year(F100910)+month(F100910), 100*2100+1) = 100 * f01011 + f01012 then F100910 else  
DATEFROMPARTS(f01011, f01012, 1) end<=@dt
union
select top 1 3 as rank, f910.f91003 marca, F910958 subdept, case when coalesce(year(F910910),2100) in (1900,2100) then F91022 else f910910 end data_subdept, 
case when coalesce(100*year(F910910)+month(F910910), 100*2100+1) = 100 * f910.YEAR + f910.month then F910910 else  DATEFROMPARTS(f910.year, f910.MONTH, 1) end data 
from f910, F9101
where f910.F91003=f9101.F91003 and case when coalesce(100*year(F910910)+month(F910910), 100*2100+1) = 100 * f910.YEAR + f910.month then F910910 else  DATEFROMPARTS(f910.year, f910.MONTH, 1) end <= @dt 
and f910.f91003 = @f10003 order by f910.year desc, f910.month desc
union
select 4 as rank, f100.f10003 marca, F100958 Subdept, case when coalesce(year(F100910),2100) in (1900,2100) then F10022 else f100910 end data_Subdept, DATEFROMPARTS(1900,1,1) data from f100
join f1001 on f100.F10003=f1001.F10003
where f100.f10003 =@f10003
) x
order by data desc, rank
GO



CREATE FUNCTION [dbo].[DamiBirou] (@f10003 int, @dt DATE) 
RETURNs table AS 
return 

SELECT top 1 Birou =   Birou, Data_Birou = data_Birou  from 
(
SELECT top 1 1 as rank, F70403 marca,  F704180 Birou,  f70406 data_Birou,  F70406 Data from f704   WHERE F70404=5 AND F70406 <= @dt and F70403 = @f10003 ORDER BY F70406 DESC
union 
select 2 as rank, f100.f10003 marca, F100959 Birou, case when coalesce(year(F100910),2100) in (1900,2100) then F10022 else f100910 end data_Birou, 
case when coalesce(100*year(F100910)+month(F100910), 100*2100+1) = 100 * f01011 + f01012 then F100910 else  DATEFROMPARTS(f01011, f01012, 1) end data 
from f100 
inner join f1001 on f100.F10003=f1001.F10003
join f010 on 1=1 where f100.f10003 =@f10003 and case when coalesce(100*year(F100910)+month(F100910), 100*2100+1) = 100 * f01011 + f01012 then F100910 else  
DATEFROMPARTS(f01011, f01012, 1) end<=@dt
union
select top 1 3 as rank, f910.f91003 marca, F910959 Birou, case when coalesce(year(F910910),2100) in (1900,2100) then F91022 else f910910 end data_birou, 
case when coalesce(100*year(F910910)+month(F910910), 100*2100+1) = 100 * f910.YEAR + f910.month then F910910 else  DATEFROMPARTS(f910.year, f910.MONTH, 1) end data 
from f910, F9101
where f910.F91003=f9101.F91003 and case when coalesce(100*year(F910910)+month(F910910), 100*2100+1) = 100 * f910.YEAR + f910.month then F910910 else  DATEFROMPARTS(f910.year, f910.MONTH, 1) end <= @dt 
and f910.f91003 = @f10003 order by f910.year desc, f910.month desc
union
select 4 as rank, f100.f10003 marca, F100959 Birou, case when coalesce(year(F100910),2100) in (1900,2100) then F10022 else f100910 end data_Birou, DATEFROMPARTS(1900,1,1) data from f100
join f1001 on f100.F10003=f1001.F10003
where f100.f10003 =@f10003
) x
order by data desc, rank
GO

ALTER FUNCTION [dbo].[CalculCO] (
        @f10003 INT,
   @zi datetime,
   @mod int,
   @grila int
)
   RETURNS @CalculCO TABLE (
       ZileCuveniteAn int,
       ZileCuvenite int,
       ZileCuveniteZi int,
       ZileAnPrecedent int
   )
AS

BEGIN

declare @ZileCuveniteAn int,  @ZileCuveniteAnSuplim18Ani int, @ZileCuveniteAnSuplimHand int, @ZileCuvenite int, @ZileCuveniteZi int, @ZileAnPrecedent int, @ZileAngajare int, @ZileAngajareZi int,@ZileSuspendare int, @ZileSuspendareZi int, @ZileSuspendare18Ani int, @ZileSuspendare18AniZi int, @ZileSuspendareHand int, @ZileSuspendareHandZi int, @PrimaZiAn date, @UltimaZiAn date, @UltimaZi18Ani date, @UltimaZiHand date, @UltimaZi18aniZi date, @UltimaZiHandZi date, @TipCalcul int, @ZileSuplimentare int, @LuniVechime int, @DataPrimeiAngajari date, @CalculCOProp18Ani int, @CalculCOPropHand int, @ZileAn int, @SuspendariExcluse nvarchar(100), @f10023 datetime


-- @TipCalcul
--  1 -- se calculeaza vechimea in munca in ultima zi din an
-- 2. se calculeaza vechimea in munca in prima zi din an
--  3 se calculeaza vechimea in munca la data angajarii
--   11 -- se calculeaza vechimea in companie in ultima zi din an
-- 12 se calculeaza vechimea in companie in prima zi din an
--  13 se calculeaza vechimea in companie la data angajarii
--   21 -- se calculeaza vechimea de la data angajarii in ultima zi din an
-- 22 se calculeaza vechimea de la data angajarii in prima zi din an
--  23 se calculeaza vechimea de la data angajarii la data angajarii
--   31 -- se calculeaza vechimea de la data primei angajarii in ultima zi din an
-- 32 - se calculeaza vechimea de la data primei angajarii in prima zi din an
--  33  -se calculeaza vechimea de la data primei angajarii la data angajarii 

-- 99 - particular

select @ZileAn = 365
if  year(@zi) % 4 = 0
   select @ZileAn = 366;

if isnull(@grila,0)= 0
   select @grila = f10072 from f100 where f10003 = @f10003;


select @f10023 = DataPlecare from DamiDataPlecare(@f10003, @zi);

Select @ZileSuplimentare = Convert(int,isnull((select "Valoare" from "tblParametrii" where "Nume"='NrZilePersoanaDizabilitatiSauMaiMica18Ani'),3));
Select @TipCalcul = Convert(int,isnull((select "Valoare" from "tblParametrii" where "Nume"='ModCalculZileCOCuvenite'),1));
Select @CalculCOProp18Ani = Convert(int,isnull((select "Valoare" from "tblParametrii" where "Nume"='ModCalculZileCO_Proportional_18Ani'),0));
Select @CalculCOPropHand = Convert(int,isnull((select "Valoare" from "tblParametrii" where "Nume"='ModCalculZileCO_Proportional_Handicap'),0));
Select @SuspendariExcluse = Convert(nvarchar(100),isnull((select "Valoare" from "tblParametrii" where "Nume"='ModCalculZileCO_SuspendariExcluse'),' '));


Select @PrimaZiAn = CASE WHEN cast(F10022 as date) < convert(varchar, year(@zi))  +  '-01-01'  THEN convert(varchar, year(@zi))  + '-01-01'  ELSE cast(F10022 as date) END, @UltimaZiAn = CASE WHEN cast(@f10023 as date) < convert(varchar, year(@zi))  +  '-12-31'  THEN cast(@f10023 as date) ELSE convert(varchar, year(@zi))  +  '-12-31'  END from (select * from F100 where f10003 = @F10003) a ;

Select @ZileAngajare = datediff(day, @PrimaZiAn, @UltimaZiAn)+1 , @ZileAngajareZi = datediff(day, @PrimaZiAn,  (CASE WHEN cast(@f10023 as date) < @zi THEN cast(@f10023 as date) ELSE @zi END))+1 from (select * from F100 where f10003 = @F10003) a  ;

Select @DataPrimeiAngajari = case when year(isnull(F1001049,'2100-01-01')) not in (1900,2100) then F1001049 else F10022 end  from (select f100.f10003, f100.f10022, f1001.F1001049 from F100 join f1001 on f100.f10003 = f1001.f10003 where f100.f10003 = @F10003) a  ;


If @TipCalcul = 1
    Select @LuniVechime = ISNULL(convert(int,substring(F100644,1,2)),0) * 12 + ISNULL(convert(int,substring(F100644,3,2)),0) + DATEDIFF (MONTH,   (select convert(nvarchar(4),F01011) + '-' +
           convert(nvarchar(4),F01012) + '-01' from F010),convert(varchar, year(@zi))  +  '-12-31') from f100 where f10003 = @f10003 Else if @TipCalcul = 2
    Select @LuniVechime = ISNULL(convert(int,substring(F100644,1,2)),0) * 12 + ISNULL(convert(int,substring(F100644,3,2)),0) + DATEDIFF (MONTH,   (select convert(nvarchar(4),F01011) + '-' +
           convert(nvarchar(4),F01012) + '-01' from F010),convert(varchar, year(@zi))  +  '-01-01') from f100 where f10003 = @f10003 Else if @TipCalcul = 3
    Select @LuniVechime = ISNULL(convert(int,substring(F100644,1,2)),0) * 12 + ISNULL(convert(int,substring(F100644,3,2)),0) + DATEDIFF (MONTH,   (select convert(nvarchar(4),F01011) + '-' +
           convert(nvarchar(4),F01012) + '-01' from F010), @zi ) from f100 where f10003 = @f10003 Else If @TipCalcul = 11
    Select @LuniVechime = ISNULL(convert(int,substring(F100643,1,2)),0) * 12 + ISNULL(convert(int,substring(F100643,3,2)),0) + DATEDIFF (MONTH,   (select convert(nvarchar(4),F01011) + '-' +
           convert(nvarchar(4),F01012) + '-01' from F010),convert(varchar, year(@zi))  +  '-12-31') from f100 where f10003 = @f10003 Else if @TipCalcul = 12
    Select @LuniVechime = ISNULL(convert(int,substring(F100643,1,2)),0) * 12 + ISNULL(convert(int,substring(F100643,3,2)),0) + DATEDIFF (MONTH,   (select convert(nvarchar(4),F01011) + '-' +
           convert(nvarchar(4),F01012) + '-01' from F010),convert(varchar, year(@zi))  +  '-01-01') from f100 where f10003 = @f10003 Else if @TipCalcul = 13
    Select @LuniVechime = ISNULL(convert(int,substring(F100643,1,2)),0) * 12 + ISNULL(convert(int,substring(F100643,3,2)),0) + DATEDIFF (MONTH,   (select convert(nvarchar(4),F01011) + '-' +
           convert(nvarchar(4),F01012) + '-01' from F010), @zi ) from f100 where f10003 = @f10003 Else If @TipCalcul = 21
    Select @LuniVechime =  DATEDIFF (MONTH, F10022,convert(varchar, year(@zi))  +  '-12-31')
    - case when day(f10022) > day(convert(varchar, year(@zi))  +  '-12-31') then 1 else 0 end from f100 where f10003 = @f10003 Else if @TipCalcul = 22
    Select @LuniVechime =  DATEDIFF (MONTH, F10022,convert(varchar, year(@zi))  +  '-01-01')
    - case when day(f10022) > day(convert(varchar, year(@zi))  +  '-01-01') then 1 else 0 end from f100 where f10003 = @f10003 Else if @TipCalcul = 23
   Select @LuniVechime = DATEDIFF (MONTH, F10022, @zi )
    - case when day(f10022) > day(@zi)  then 1 else 0 end from f100 where f10003 = @f10003 Else If @TipCalcul = 31 
	Select @LuniVechime =  DATEDIFF (MONTH, @DataPrimeiAngajari,convert(varchar, year(@zi))  +  '-12-31')
	- case when day(@DataPrimeiAngajari) > day(convert(varchar, year(@zi))  +  '-12-31') then 1 else 0 end from f100 where f10003 = @f10003 Else if @TipCalcul = 32
	Select @LuniVechime =  DATEDIFF (MONTH, @DataPrimeiAngajari,convert(varchar, year(@zi))  +  '-01-01') 
	- case when day(@DataPrimeiAngajari) > day(convert(varchar, year(@zi))  +  '-01-01') then 1 else 0 end from f100 where f10003 = @f10003 Else if @TipCalcul = 33 
	Select @LuniVechime = DATEDIFF (MONTH, @DataPrimeiAngajari, @zi )  
	- case when day(@DataPrimeiAngajari) > day(@zi)  then 1 else 0 end from f100 where f10003 = @f10003 Else if @TipCalcul = 99
    select @LuniVechime =  DATEDIFF (MONTH,  case when f10022 <= '2018-02-14' then '2018-02-14' else f10022 end , @zi )
    - case when ( case when f10022 <= '2018-02-14' then 14 else day(f10022) end) > day(@zi)  then 1 else 0 end
   from f100 where f10003 = @f10003;

if isnull(@LuniVechime,0) < =0 
	 select @LuniVechime = 0;

select @ZileCuveniteAnSuplimHand  = CASE WHEN ISNULL(a.F10027,0)>=2 and (f100271 = '2100-01-01' or f100271 = '1900-01-01' or @PrimaZiAn <= f100271) THEN convert(int, @ZileSuplimentare) else 0 end,
@ZileCuveniteAnSuplim18Ani =   case when dateadd(year,18,f10021) >= @PrimaZiAn  then convert(int, @ZileSuplimentare,0)  else 0 end
  from (select * from F100 where f10003 = @F10003) a ;  

If @mod <> 1
    select @ZileCuveniteAn = CuveniteAn from ptj_tblzileco where an=year(@zi) and f10003 = @f10003 else
   select @ZileCuveniteAn =     c.F02615 + @ZileCuveniteAnSuplim18Ani + @ZileCuveniteAnSuplimHand
       from (select * from F100 where f10003 = @F10003) a    left join F026 c on convert(int,@grila) = c.F02604 and
       (convert(int,c.F02610/100) * 12) <= @LuniVechime and @LuniVechime < (convert(int,c.F02611/100) * 12)  where (year(@zi)  between year(F10022) and year(F10023) ) and a.F10003= @f10003 ;

 
  select @UltimaZi18Ani = case when  dateadd(year, 18, f10021) <= @UltimaZiAn  then dateadd(year, 18, f10021)  else @UltimaZiAn end,
  @UltimaZiHand = case when f100271 = '2100-01-01' or f100271 = '1900-01-01' or f100271 > @UltimaZiAn then @UltimaZiAn else f100271 end
  from (select * from F100 where f10003 = @F10003) a;

  select @UltimaZi18AniZi = case when @UltimaZi18Ani <= CONVERT(date,@zi) then @UltimaZi18Ani else CONVERT(date,@zi) end,
   @UltimaZiHandZi = case when @UltimaZiHand <= CONVERT(date,@zi) then @UltimaZiHand else CONVERT(date,@zi) end;

   with xx as  ( select f111.f11103 Marca, f111.f11105 de_la_data, case when f111.f11107='2100-01-01' then f111.f11106 else dateadd(d,-1,f111.f11107) end la_data from f111
	 inner join
 (select a.f11103, a.f11105, case when a.f11107='2100-01-01' then a.f11106 else dateadd(d,-1,a.f11107) end f11107, a.time, max(b.time) timp from F111 a inner join f111 b  on
 a.F11103 = b.F11103 and  (a.f11105 <= case when b.f11107='2100-01-01' then b.f11106 else dateadd(d,-1,b.f11107) end   and b.f11105 <= case when a.f11107='2100-01-01'
 then a.f11106 else dateadd(d,-1,a.f11107) end)  group by a.f11103, a.f11105, case when a.f11107='2100-01-01' then a.f11106 else dateadd(d,-1,a.f11107) end, a.time) t  on f111.f11103 = t.f11103 and
 f111.f11105 = t.f11105 and   case when f111.f11107='2100-01-01' then f111.f11106 else dateadd(d,-1,f111.f11107) end = t.f11107 and f111.time = t.timp 
 where CHARINDEX(concat(',',ltrim(rtrim(convert(nvarchar(100),f111.f11104))),','), concat(',',ltrim(rtrim(@SuspendariExcluse)),','))  = 0
  union all
 select f10003 Marca, datainceput de_la_data, datasfarsit la_data  from ptj_cereri inner join Ptj_tblAbsente on Ptj_Cereri.IdAbsenta = Ptj_tblAbsente.id  where
 ptj_cereri.IdStare=3 and isnull(Ptj_tblAbsente.AbsenteCFPInCalculCO,0) = 1  ),
  yy as  (select distinct a.marca, min(b.de_la_data) de_la_data, max(b.la_data) la_data from xx a  inner join xx b on a.marca = b.marca and
  (a.de_la_data <= b.la_data and b.de_la_data <= a.la_data)  group by a.marca, a.de_la_data, a.la_data),
  f111_2 as   (select distinct a.marca f11103, min(b.de_la_data) f11105, max(b.la_data)  f11107 from yy a  inner join yy b on a.marca = b.marca and (a.de_la_data <=
   b.la_data and b.de_la_data <= a.la_data)  group by a.marca, a.de_la_data, a.la_data)

  select  @ZileSuspendare= (select COALESCE(SUM(datediff(d,CASE WHEN F11105 <  @PrimaZiAn THEN @PrimaZiAn else F11105 END,CASE WHEN F11107 > @UltimaZiAn THEN @UltimaZiAn else F11107 END) + 1) ,0)  from (select * from F100 where f10003 = @F10003) a  join f111_2 Z on a.f10003 = z.f11103
  and F11105 <= F11107 AND F11107 >= @PrimaZiAn AND F11105 <= @UltimaZiAn) ,  @ZileSuspendareZi = (select COALESCE(SUM(datediff(d,CASE WHEN F11105 < @PrimaZiAn THEN @PrimaZiAn else F11105 END,CASE WHEN F11107 > CONVERT(date,@zi) THEN CONVERT(date,@zi) else F11107 END)+1) ,0)
  from (select * from F100 where f10003 = @F10003) a  join f111_2 Z on a.f10003 = z.f11103
  and F11105 <= F11107 AND F11107 >= @PrimaZiAn AND F11105 <= CONVERT(date,@zi)),
  @ZileSuspendare18Ani= (select COALESCE(SUM(datediff(d,CASE WHEN F11105 <  @PrimaZiAn THEN @PrimaZiAn else F11105 END,CASE WHEN F11107 > @UltimaZi18Ani THEN @UltimaZi18Ani else F11107 END) + 1) ,0)  from (select * from F100 where f10003 = @F10003) a  join f111_2 Z on a.f10003 = z.f11103
  and F11105 <= F11107 AND F11107 >= @PrimaZiAn AND F11105 <= @UltimaZi18Ani) ,  @ZileSuspendare18AniZi = (select COALESCE(SUM(datediff(d,CASE WHEN F11105 < @PrimaZiAn THEN @PrimaZiAn else F11105 END,CASE WHEN F11107 > @UltimaZi18AniZi THEN @UltimaZi18AniZi else F11107 END)+1) ,0)
  from (select * from F100 where f10003 = @F10003) a  join f111_2 Z on a.f10003 = z.f11103
  and F11105 <= F11107 AND F11107 >= @PrimaZiAn AND F11105 <= @UltimaZi18AniZi),
  @ZileSuspendareHand = (select COALESCE(SUM(datediff(d,CASE WHEN F11105 <  @PrimaZiAn THEN @PrimaZiAn else F11105 END,CASE WHEN F11107 > @UltimaZiHand THEN @UltimaZiHand else F11107 END) + 1) ,0)  from (select * from F100 where f10003 = @F10003) a  join f111_2 Z on a.f10003 = z.f11103
  and F11105 <= F11107 AND F11107 >= @PrimaZiAn AND F11105 <= @UltimaZiHand) ,  @ZileSuspendareHandZi = (select COALESCE(SUM(datediff(d,CASE WHEN F11105 < @PrimaZiAn THEN @PrimaZiAn else F11105 END,CASE WHEN F11107 > @UltimaZiHandZi THEN @UltimaZiHandZi else F11107 END)+1) ,0)
  from (select * from F100 where f10003 = @F10003) a  join f111_2 Z on a.f10003 = z.f11103
  and F11105 <= F11107 AND F11107 >= @PrimaZiAn AND F11105 <= @UltimaZiHandZi) ;



  select @ZileCuvenite = case when @mod= 1 then 
			round(convert(float,(@ZileCuveniteAn -  @ZileCuveniteAnSuplim18Ani - @ZileCuveniteAnSuplimHand) * (@ZileAngajare - isnull(@ZileSuspendare,0))) /CONVERT(float,@ZileAn),0) +
    convert(int, round( case when @CalculCOPropHand = 0  then 1 else (datediff(day, @PrimaZiAn,  @UltimaZiHand)+1 - @ZileSuspendareHand) / convert(float, @ZileAn) end * @ZileCuveniteAnSuplimHand,0)) +
	convert(int, round( case when @CalculCOProp18Ani = 0  then 1 else (datediff(day, @PrimaZiAn,  @UltimaZi18Ani)+1 - @ZileSuspendare18Ani) / convert(float, @ZileAn) end * @ZileCuveniteAnSuplim18Ani,0)) 
            else (select Cuvenite from Ptj_tblZileCO where f10003 = @f10003 and an = year(@zi)) end;

  select @ZileCuveniteZi =  round(convert(float, (@ZileCuveniteAn -  @ZileCuveniteAnSuplim18Ani - @ZileCuveniteAnSuplimHand)  * (@ZileAngajareZi - isnull(@ZileSuspendareZi,0))) /CONVERT(float,@ZileAn),0)+
    convert(int, round( case when @CalculCOPropHand = 0  then 1 else (datediff(day, @PrimaZiAn,  @UltimaZiHandZi)+1 - @ZileSuspendareHandZi) / convert(float, @ZileAn) end * @ZileCuveniteAnSuplimHand,0)) +
	convert(int, round( case when @CalculCOProp18Ani = 0  then 1 else (datediff(day, @PrimaZiAn,  @UltimaZi18aniZi)+1 - @ZileSuspendare18AniZi) / convert(float, @ZileAn) end * @ZileCuveniteAnSuplim18Ani,0)) 
 
INSERT INTO @CalculCO
 SELECT @ZileCuveniteAn, isnull(@ZileCuvenite,0), @ZileCuveniteZi, isnull((select SoldAnterior from Ptj_tblZileCO where f10003 = @f10003 and an=year(@zi)),0);

  RETURN;
 END
