ALTER FUNCTION [dbo].[CalculCO] (
       @f10003 INT,
  @zi datetime,
  @mod int,
  @grila int
)
  RETURNS @CalculCO TABLE (
      ZileCuveniteAn int,
      ZileCuvenite int,
      ZileCuveniteZi int,
      ZileAnPrecedent int
  )
AS

BEGIN

declare @ZileCuveniteAn int,  @ZileCuveniteAnSuplim18Ani int, @ZileCuveniteAnSuplimHand int, @ZileCuvenite int, @ZileCuveniteZi int, @ZileAnPrecedent int, @ZileAngajare int, @ZileAngajareZi int,@ZileSuspendare int, @ZileSuspendareZi int, @ZileSuspendare18Ani int, @ZileSuspendare18AniZi int, @ZileSuspendareHand int, @ZileSuspendareHandZi int, @PrimaZiAn date, @UltimaZiAn date, @UltimaZi18Ani date, @UltimaZiHand date, @UltimaZi18aniZi date, @UltimaZiHandZi date, @TipCalcul int, @ZileSuplimentare int, @LuniVechime int, @DataPrimeiAngajari date, @CalculCOProp18Ani int, @CalculCOPropHand int, @ZileAn int, @SuspendariExcluse nvarchar(100), @f10023 datetime


-- @TipCalcul
--  1 -- se calculeaza vechimea in munca in ultima zi din an
-- 2. se calculeaza vechimea in munca in prima zi din an
--  3 se calculeaza vechimea in munca la data angajarii
--   11 -- se calculeaza vechimea in companie in ultima zi din an
-- 12 se calculeaza vechimea in companie in prima zi din an
--  13 se calculeaza vechimea in companie la data angajarii
--   21 -- se calculeaza vechimea de la data angajarii in ultima zi din an
-- 22 se calculeaza vechimea de la data angajarii in prima zi din an
--  23 se calculeaza vechimea de la data angajarii la data angajarii
--   31 -- se calculeaza vechimea de la data primei angajarii in ultima zi din an
-- 32 - se calculeaza vechimea de la data primei angajarii in prima zi din an
--  33  -se calculeaza vechimea de la data primei angajarii la data angajarii 

-- 99 - particular

select @ZileAn = 365
if  year(@zi) % 4 = 0
  select @ZileAn = 366;

if isnull(@grila,0)= 0
  select @grila = f10072 from f100 where f10003 = @f10003;


select @f10023 = DataPlecare from DamiDataPlecare(@f10003, @zi);

Select @ZileSuplimentare = Convert(int,isnull((select "Valoare" from "tblParametrii" where "Nume"='NrZilePersoanaDizabilitatiSauMaiMica18Ani'),3));
Select @TipCalcul = Convert(int,isnull((select "Valoare" from "tblParametrii" where "Nume"='ModCalculZileCOCuvenite'),1));
Select @CalculCOProp18Ani = Convert(int,isnull((select "Valoare" from "tblParametrii" where "Nume"='ModCalculZileCO_Proportional_18Ani'),0));
Select @CalculCOPropHand = Convert(int,isnull((select "Valoare" from "tblParametrii" where "Nume"='ModCalculZileCO_Proportional_Handicap'),0));
Select @SuspendariExcluse = Convert(nvarchar(100),isnull((select "Valoare" from "tblParametrii" where "Nume"='ModCalculZileCO_SuspendariExcluse'),' '));


Select @PrimaZiAn = CASE WHEN cast(F10022 as date) < convert(varchar, year(@zi))  +  '-01-01'  THEN convert(varchar, year(@zi))  + '-01-01'  ELSE cast(F10022 as date) END, @UltimaZiAn = CASE WHEN cast(@f10023 as date) < convert(varchar, year(@zi))  +  '-12-31'  THEN cast(@f10023 as date) ELSE convert(varchar, year(@zi))  +  '-12-31'  END from (select * from F100 where f10003 = @F10003) a ;

Select @ZileAngajare = datediff(day, @PrimaZiAn, @UltimaZiAn)+1 , @ZileAngajareZi = datediff(day, @PrimaZiAn,  (CASE WHEN cast(@f10023 as date) < @zi THEN cast(@f10023 as date) ELSE @zi END))+1 from (select * from F100 where f10003 = @F10003) a  ;

Select @DataPrimeiAngajari = case when year(isnull(F1001049,'2100-01-01')) not in (1900,2100) then F1001049 else F10022 end from (select f100.f10003, f100.f10022, f1001.F1001049 from F100 join f1001 on f100.f10003 = f1001.f10003 where f100.f10003 = @F10003) a  ;


If @TipCalcul in (0,1)
   Select @LuniVechime = ISNULL(convert(int,substring(F100644,1,2)),0) * 12 + ISNULL(convert(int,substring(F100644,3,2)),0) + DATEDIFF (MONTH,   (select convert(nvarchar(4),F01011) + '-' +
          convert(nvarchar(4),F01012) + '-01' from F010),convert(varchar, year(@zi))  +  '-12-31') from f100 where f10003 = @f10003 Else if @TipCalcul = 2
   Select @LuniVechime = ISNULL(convert(int,substring(F100644,1,2)),0) * 12 + ISNULL(convert(int,substring(F100644,3,2)),0) + DATEDIFF (MONTH,   (select convert(nvarchar(4),F01011) + '-' +
          convert(nvarchar(4),F01012) + '-01' from F010),convert(varchar, year(@zi))  +  '-01-01') from f100 where f10003 = @f10003 Else if @TipCalcul = 3
   Select @LuniVechime = ISNULL(convert(int,substring(F100644,1,2)),0) * 12 + ISNULL(convert(int,substring(F100644,3,2)),0) + DATEDIFF (MONTH,   (select convert(nvarchar(4),F01011) + '-' +
          convert(nvarchar(4),F01012) + '-01' from F010), @zi ) from f100 where f10003 = @f10003 Else If @TipCalcul = 11
   Select @LuniVechime = ISNULL(convert(int,substring(F100643,1,2)),0) * 12 + ISNULL(convert(int,substring(F100643,3,2)),0) + DATEDIFF (MONTH,   (select convert(nvarchar(4),F01011) + '-' +
          convert(nvarchar(4),F01012) + '-01' from F010),convert(varchar, year(@zi))  +  '-12-31') from f100 where f10003 = @f10003 Else if @TipCalcul = 12
   Select @LuniVechime = ISNULL(convert(int,substring(F100643,1,2)),0) * 12 + ISNULL(convert(int,substring(F100643,3,2)),0) + DATEDIFF (MONTH,   (select convert(nvarchar(4),F01011) + '-' +
          convert(nvarchar(4),F01012) + '-01' from F010),convert(varchar, year(@zi))  +  '-01-01') from f100 where f10003 = @f10003 Else if @TipCalcul = 13
   Select @LuniVechime = ISNULL(convert(int,substring(F100643,1,2)),0) * 12 + ISNULL(convert(int,substring(F100643,3,2)),0) + DATEDIFF (MONTH,   (select convert(nvarchar(4),F01011) + '-' +
          convert(nvarchar(4),F01012) + '-01' from F010), @zi ) from f100 where f10003 = @f10003 Else If @TipCalcul = 21
   Select @LuniVechime =  DATEDIFF (MONTH, F10022,convert(varchar, year(@zi))  +  '-12-31')
   - case when day(f10022) > day(convert(varchar, year(@zi))  +  '-12-31') then 1 else 0 end from f100 where f10003 = @f10003 Else if @TipCalcul = 22
   Select @LuniVechime =  DATEDIFF (MONTH, F10022,convert(varchar, year(@zi))  +  '-01-01')
   - case when day(f10022) > day(convert(varchar, year(@zi))  +  '-01-01') then 1 else 0 end from f100 where f10003 = @f10003 Else if @TipCalcul = 23
  Select @LuniVechime = DATEDIFF (MONTH, F10022, @zi )
   - case when day(f10022) > day(@zi)  then 1 else 0 end from f100 where f10003 = @f10003 Else If @TipCalcul = 31 
	Select @LuniVechime =  DATEDIFF (MONTH, @DataPrimeiAngajari,convert(varchar, year(@zi))  +  '-12-31')
	- case when day(@DataPrimeiAngajari) > day(convert(varchar, year(@zi))  +  '-12-31') then 1 else 0 end from f100 where f10003 = @f10003 Else if @TipCalcul = 32
	Select @LuniVechime =  DATEDIFF (MONTH, @DataPrimeiAngajari,convert(varchar, year(@zi))  +  '-01-01') 
	- case when day(@DataPrimeiAngajari) > day(convert(varchar, year(@zi))  +  '-01-01') then 1 else 0 end from f100 where f10003 = @f10003 Else if @TipCalcul = 33 
	Select @LuniVechime = DATEDIFF (MONTH, @DataPrimeiAngajari, @zi )  
	- case when day(@DataPrimeiAngajari) > day(@zi)  then 1 else 0 end from f100 where f10003 = @f10003 Else if @TipCalcul = 99
   select @LuniVechime =  DATEDIFF (MONTH,  case when f10022 <= '2018-02-14' then '2018-02-14' else f10022 end , @zi )
   - case when ( case when f10022 <= '2018-02-14' then 14 else day(f10022) end) > day(@zi)  then 1 else 0 end
  from f100 where f10003 = @f10003;

if isnull(@LuniVechime,0) < =0 
	 select @LuniVechime = 0;

select @ZileCuveniteAnSuplimHand  = CASE WHEN ISNULL(a.F10027,0)>=2 and (f100271 = '2100-01-01' or f100271 = '1900-01-01' or @PrimaZiAn <= f100271) THEN convert(int, @ZileSuplimentare) else 0 end,
@ZileCuveniteAnSuplim18Ani =   case when dateadd(year,18,f10021) >= @PrimaZiAn  then convert(int, @ZileSuplimentare,0)  else 0 end
 from (select * from F100 where f10003 = @F10003) a ;  

If @mod <> 1
   select @ZileCuveniteAn = CuveniteAn from ptj_tblzileco where an=year(@zi) and f10003 = @f10003 else
  select @ZileCuveniteAn =     c.F02615 + @ZileCuveniteAnSuplim18Ani + @ZileCuveniteAnSuplimHand
      from (select * from F100 where f10003 = @F10003) a    left join F026 c on convert(int,@grila) = c.F02604 and
      (convert(int,c.F02610/100) * 12) <= @LuniVechime and @LuniVechime < (convert(int,c.F02611/100) * 12)  where (year(@zi)  between year(F10022) and year(F10023) ) and a.F10003= @f10003 ;


 select @UltimaZi18Ani = case when  dateadd(year, 18, f10021) <= @UltimaZiAn  then dateadd(year, 18, f10021)  else @UltimaZiAn end,  @UltimaZiHand = case when f100271 = '2100-01-01' or f100271 = '1900-01-01' or f100271 > @UltimaZiAn then @UltimaZiAn else f100271 end  from (select * from F100 where f10003 = @F10003) a;

 select @UltimaZi18AniZi = case when @UltimaZi18Ani <= CONVERT(date,@zi) then @UltimaZi18Ani else CONVERT(date,@zi) end,
  @UltimaZiHandZi = case when @UltimaZiHand <= CONVERT(date,@zi) then @UltimaZiHand else CONVERT(date,@zi) end;

  with xx as  ( select f111.f11103 Marca, f111.f11105 de_la_data, case when f111.f11107='2100-01-01' then f111.f11106 else dateadd(d,-1,f111.f11107) end la_data from f111
	 inner join
(select a.f11103, a.f11105, case when a.f11107='2100-01-01' then a.f11106 else dateadd(d,-1,a.f11107) end f11107, a.time, max(b.time) timp from F111 a inner join f111 b  on
a.F11103 = b.F11103 and  (a.f11105 <= case when b.f11107='2100-01-01' then b.f11106 else dateadd(d,-1,b.f11107) end   and b.f11105 <= case when a.f11107='2100-01-01'
then a.f11106 else dateadd(d,-1,a.f11107) end)  group by a.f11103, a.f11105, case when a.f11107='2100-01-01' then a.f11106 else dateadd(d,-1,a.f11107) end, a.time) t  on f111.f11103 = t.f11103 and
f111.f11105 = t.f11105 and   case when f111.f11107='2100-01-01' then f111.f11106 else dateadd(d,-1,f111.f11107) end = t.f11107 and f111.time = t.timp 
where CHARINDEX(concat(',',ltrim(rtrim(convert(nvarchar(100),f111.f11104))),','), concat(',',ltrim(rtrim(@SuspendariExcluse)),','))  = 0  union all select f10003 Marca, datainceput de_la_data, datasfarsit la_data  from ptj_cereri inner join Ptj_tblAbsente on Ptj_Cereri.IdAbsenta = Ptj_tblAbsente.id  where
ptj_cereri.IdStare=3 and isnull(Ptj_tblAbsente.AbsenteCFPInCalculCO,0) = 1  ),  yy as  (select distinct a.marca, min(b.de_la_data) de_la_data, max(b.la_data) la_data from xx a  inner join xx b on a.marca = b.marca and  (a.de_la_data <= b.la_data and b.de_la_data <= a.la_data)  group by a.marca, a.de_la_data, a.la_data),
 f111_2 as   (select distinct a.marca f11103, min(b.de_la_data) f11105, max(b.la_data)  f11107 from yy a  inner join yy b on a.marca = b.marca and (a.de_la_data <=
  b.la_data and b.de_la_data <= a.la_data)  group by a.marca, a.de_la_data, a.la_data)

 select  @ZileSuspendare= (select COALESCE(SUM(datediff(d,CASE WHEN F11105 <  @PrimaZiAn THEN @PrimaZiAn else F11105 END,CASE WHEN F11107 > @UltimaZiAn THEN @UltimaZiAn else F11107 END) + 1) ,0) from (select * from F100 where f10003 = @F10003) a  join f111_2 Z on a.f10003 = z.f11103  and F11105 <= F11107 AND F11107 >= @PrimaZiAn AND F11105 <= @UltimaZiAn) , @ZileSuspendareZi = (select COALESCE(SUM(datediff(d,CASE WHEN F11105 < @PrimaZiAn THEN @PrimaZiAn else F11105 END,CASE WHEN F11107 > CONVERT(date,@zi) THEN CONVERT(date,@zi) else F11107 END)+1) ,0)  from (select * from F100 where f10003 = @F10003) a  join f111_2 Z on a.f10003 = z.f11103  and F11105 <= F11107 AND F11107 >= @PrimaZiAn AND F11105 <= CONVERT(date,@zi)),  @ZileSuspendare18Ani= (select COALESCE(SUM(datediff(d,CASE WHEN F11105 <  @PrimaZiAn THEN @PrimaZiAn else F11105 END,CASE WHEN F11107 > @UltimaZi18Ani THEN @UltimaZi18Ani else F11107 END) + 1) ,0) from (select * from F100 where f10003 = @F10003) a  join f111_2 Z on a.f10003 = z.f11103  and F11105 <= F11107 AND F11107 >= @PrimaZiAn AND F11105 <= @UltimaZi18Ani) , @ZileSuspendare18AniZi = (select COALESCE(SUM(datediff(d,CASE WHEN F11105 < @PrimaZiAn THEN @PrimaZiAn else F11105 END,CASE WHEN F11107 > @UltimaZi18AniZi THEN @UltimaZi18AniZi else F11107 END)+1) ,0)  from (select * from F100 where f10003 = @F10003) a  join f111_2 Z on a.f10003 = z.f11103  and F11105 <= F11107 AND F11107 >= @PrimaZiAn AND F11105 <= @UltimaZi18AniZi),  @ZileSuspendareHand = (select COALESCE(SUM(datediff(d,CASE WHEN F11105 <  @PrimaZiAn THEN @PrimaZiAn else F11105 END,CASE WHEN F11107 > @UltimaZiHand THEN @UltimaZiHand else F11107 END) + 1) ,0) from (select * from F100 where f10003 = @F10003) a  join f111_2 Z on a.f10003 = z.f11103  and F11105 <= F11107 AND F11107 >= @PrimaZiAn AND F11105 <= @UltimaZiHand) , @ZileSuspendareHandZi = (select COALESCE(SUM(datediff(d,CASE WHEN F11105 < @PrimaZiAn THEN @PrimaZiAn else F11105 END,CASE WHEN F11107 > @UltimaZiHandZi THEN @UltimaZiHandZi else F11107 END)+1) ,0)  from (select * from F100 where f10003 = @F10003) a  join f111_2 Z on a.f10003 = z.f11103  and F11105 <= F11107 AND F11107 >= @PrimaZiAn AND F11105 <= @UltimaZiHandZi) ;



 select @ZileCuvenite = case when @mod= 1 then 
			round(convert(float,(@ZileCuveniteAn -  @ZileCuveniteAnSuplim18Ani - @ZileCuveniteAnSuplimHand) * (@ZileAngajare - isnull(@ZileSuspendare,0))) /CONVERT(float,@ZileAn),0) +
   convert(int, round( case when @CalculCOPropHand = 0  then 1 else (datediff(day, @PrimaZiAn,  @UltimaZiHand)+1 - @ZileSuspendareHand) / convert(float, @ZileAn) end * @ZileCuveniteAnSuplimHand,0)) +
	convert(int, round( case when @CalculCOProp18Ani = 0  then 1 else (datediff(day, @PrimaZiAn,  @UltimaZi18Ani)+1 - @ZileSuspendare18Ani) / convert(float, @ZileAn) end * @ZileCuveniteAnSuplim18Ani,0)) 
           else (select Cuvenite from Ptj_tblZileCO where f10003 = @f10003 and an = year(@zi)) end;

 select @ZileCuveniteZi =  round(convert(float, (@ZileCuveniteAn -  @ZileCuveniteAnSuplim18Ani - @ZileCuveniteAnSuplimHand)  * (@ZileAngajareZi - isnull(@ZileSuspendareZi,0))) /CONVERT(float,@ZileAn),0)+
   convert(int, round( case when @CalculCOPropHand = 0  then 1 else (datediff(day, @PrimaZiAn,  @UltimaZiHandZi)+1 - @ZileSuspendareHandZi) / convert(float, @ZileAn) end * @ZileCuveniteAnSuplimHand,0)) +
	convert(int, round( case when @CalculCOProp18Ani = 0  then 1 else (datediff(day, @PrimaZiAn,  @UltimaZi18aniZi)+1 - @ZileSuspendare18AniZi) / convert(float, @ZileAn) end * @ZileCuveniteAnSuplim18Ani,0)) 

INSERT INTO @CalculCO
SELECT @ZileCuveniteAn, isnull(@ZileCuvenite,0), @ZileCuveniteZi, isnull((select SoldAnterior from Ptj_tblZileCO where f10003 = @f10003 and an=year(@zi)),0);

 RETURN;
END
GO

--https://github.com/wizromRD/WizOne/issues/560
--#560 - De adaugat 1, 2 campuri in template destinate pentru formula Sql intre 2, 3 alte campuri din template. Pe formular sa faca calcul la nivel de linie. #560

--  Competente

DECLARE @i INT
SET @i = 1
WHILE (@i <= 500)
BEGIN
	IF ((SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Eval_ConfigCompTemplateDetail WHERE TemplateId=@i AND ColumnName='Total1')=0 AND (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Eval_ConfigObTemplate WHERE TemplateId=@i) > 0)
	INSERT INTO Eval_ConfigCompTemplateDetail(Id, TemplateId, ColumnName, Width, Obligatoriu, Citire, Editare, Vizibil, IdNomenclator) VALUES(6, @i, 'Total1', 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, -99);
	IF ((SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Eval_ConfigCompTemplateDetail WHERE TemplateId=@i AND ColumnName='Total2')=0 AND (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Eval_ConfigObTemplate WHERE TemplateId=@i) > 0)
	INSERT INTO Eval_ConfigCompTemplateDetail(Id, TemplateId, ColumnName, Width, Obligatoriu, Citire, Editare, Vizibil, IdNomenclator) VALUES(7, @i, 'Total2', 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, -99);

    SET @i = @i + 1
END
GO

--  Obiective

DECLARE @i INT
SET @i = 1
WHILE (@i <= 500)
BEGIN
    IF ((SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Eval_ConfigObTemplateDetail WHERE TemplateId=@i AND ColumnName='Total1')=0 AND (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Eval_ConfigObTemplate WHERE TemplateId=@i) > 0)
	INSERT INTO Eval_ConfigObTemplateDetail(Id, TemplateId, ColumnName, Width, Obligatoriu, Citire, Editare, Vizibil, TipValoare, IdNomenclator) VALUES(14, @i, 'Total1', 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, -99, -99);
	IF ((SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Eval_ConfigObTemplateDetail WHERE TemplateId=@i AND ColumnName='Total2')=0 AND (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM Eval_ConfigObTemplate WHERE TemplateId=@i) > 0)
	INSERT INTO Eval_ConfigObTemplateDetail(Id, TemplateId, ColumnName, Width, Obligatoriu, Citire, Editare, Vizibil, TipValoare, IdNomenclator) VALUES(15, @i, 'Total2', 100, 0, 0, 0, 0, -99, -99);

    SET @i = @i + 1
END
GO

 CREATE TABLE Org_DateGenerale
   (	"Id" int, 
	"DataVigoare" DATETIME, 
	"PostId" int, 
	"PostDenumire" nVARCHAR(250), 
	"FunctieId" int, 
	"FunctieDenumire" nVARCHAR(250),

	"ContractDurataData" DATETIME, 
	"TipContract" int, 
	"NrOre" int, 
	"Locatie" nVARCHAR(max), 
	"Salariul" int, 
	"BugetExistent" int, 
	"CentruCost" int, 
	"MotiveId" int, 
	"MotiveDescriere" nVARCHAR(max), 
	"DataInceput" DATETIME, 
	"DataSfarsit" DATETIME,

	"NumeComplet" nVARCHAR(250), 
	"Companie" int, 
	"Subcompanie" int, 
	"Filiala" int, 
	"Sectie" int, 
	"Dept" int,

	"Rol2Observatii" nVARCHAR(max),

	"Rol4Observatii" nVARCHAR(max), 
	"Rol5Observatii" nVARCHAR(max),

MERGE INTO F704 USING
(SELECT "F10003", MAX("DataModif") AS DM, MAX("IdAtribut") AS IDA
FROM  "Avs_Cereri" WHERE "IdAtribut" = 25 AND "DurataContract" = 1 AND convert(date, "DataModif") >= convert(date, '01/10/2020', 103) GROUP BY "F10003") t
ON (F70403 = t."F10003" AND F70404 = t.IDA AND F70406 = convert(date, '01/01/2100', 103))
WHEN MATCHED THEN UPDATE SET F70406 = DM;

Update F095 set F09511='Nedeterminat' where F09505=CONVERT(DATETIME, '01/01/2100',103) and (F09511 is null or F09511='0');
Update F095 set F09511='Determinat' where F09505<>CONVERT(DATETIME, '01/01/2100',103) and (F09511 is null or F09511='0');


INSERT INTO tblMeniuri(Id, Nume, Descriere, Pagina, Stare, Icoana) VALUES(123, 'Circuit formulare', 'Circuit formulare', 'Pagini\SablonNomen[Org_Circuit]', 1, 'm1.png')
GO

drop SEQUENCE Ptj_Cereri_Id_SEQ
GO

declare @maxId as int 
select @maxId = max(Id) + 1 from Ptj_Cereri
declare @s nvarchar(4000);
set @s = N'
CREATE SEQUENCE Ptj_Cereri_Id_SEQ  AS INTEGER  
START WITH ' + cast(@maxId as nvarchar) + '
INCREMENT BY 1  
NO CYCLE;'

EXEC (@s);

GO



alter FUNCTION [dbo].[DamiDept] (@f10003 int, @dt DATE)
RETURNs table AS
return
 
       SELECT top 1 Dept =   Dept, Subdept =   Subdept,  Birou =   Birou, Data_dept = data_dept  from
(
SELECT top 1 1 as rank, F70403 marca,  F70417 dept,  F70418 Subdept, F704180 Birou, f70406 data_dept,  F70406 Data from f704   WHERE F70404=5 AND F70406 <= @dt and F70403 = @f10003 ORDER BY F70406 DESC
union
select 2 as rank, f100.f10003 marca, f10007 dept,  F100958 Subdept,  F100959 Birou, case when coalesce(year(F100910),2100) in (1900,2100) then F10022 else f100910 end data_dept, case when coalesce(100*year(F100910)+month(F100910), 100*2100+1) = 100 * f01011 + f01012 then F100910 else  DATEFROMPARTS(f01011, f01012, 1) end data from f100 join f1001 on f100.F10003=f1001.F10003  join f010 on 1=1 where f100.f10003 =@f10003 and case when coalesce(100*year(F100910)+month(F100910), 100*2100+1) = 100 * f01011 + f01012 then F100910 else  DATEFROMPARTS(f01011, f01012, 1) end<=@dt
union
select top 1 3 as rank, f910.f91003 marca, F91007 dept, F910958 subdept, F910959 Birou, case when coalesce(year(F910910),2100) in (1900,2100) then F91022 else f910910 end data_dept, case when coalesce(100*year(F910910)+month(F910910), 100*2100+1) = 100 * f910.YEAR + f910.month then F910910 else  DATEFROMPARTS(f910.year, f910.MONTH, 1) end data from f910 join f9101 on f910.F91003=f9101.F91003 and f910.year = f9101.year and f910.month = f9101.MONTH where case when coalesce(100*year(F910910)+month(F910910), 100*2100+1) = 100 * f910.YEAR + f910.month then F910910 else  DATEFROMPARTS(f910.year, f910.MONTH, 1) end <= @dt and f910.f91003 = @f10003 order by f910.year desc, f910.month desc
union
select 4 as rank, f100.f10003 marca, F10007 dept,  F100958 Subdept, F100959 Birou, case when coalesce(year(F100910),2100) in (1900,2100) then F10022 else f100910 end data_dept, DATEFROMPARTS(1900,1,1) data from f100 join f1001 on f100.F10003=f1001.F10003 where f100.f10003 =@f10003
) x
order by data desc, rank
GO



alter FUNCTION [dbo].[DamiSubdept] (@f10003 int, @dt DATE)
RETURNs table AS
return
 
SELECT top 1 Subdept =   Subdept, Data_Subdept = data_Subdept  from
(
SELECT top 1 1 as rank, F70403 marca,  F70418 Subdept,  f70406 data_Subdept,  F70406 Data from f704   WHERE F70404=5 AND F70406 <= @dt and F70403 = @f10003 ORDER BY F70406 DESC
union
select 2 as rank, f100.f10003 marca, F100958 Subdept, case when coalesce(year(F100910),2100) in (1900,2100) then F10022 else f100910 end data_Subdept,
case when coalesce(100*year(F100910)+month(F100910), 100*2100+1) = 100 * f01011 + f01012 then F100910 else  DATEFROMPARTS(f01011, f01012, 1) end data
from f100
inner join f1001 on f100.F10003=f1001.F10003
join f010 on 1=1 where f100.f10003 =@f10003 and case when coalesce(100*year(F100910)+month(F100910), 100*2100+1) = 100 * f01011 + f01012 then F100910 else 
DATEFROMPARTS(f01011, f01012, 1) end<=@dt
union
select top 1 3 as rank, f910.f91003 marca, F910958 subdept, case when coalesce(year(F910910),2100) in (1900,2100) then F91022 else f910910 end data_subdept,
case when coalesce(100*year(F910910)+month(F910910), 100*2100+1) = 100 * f910.YEAR + f910.month then F910910 else  DATEFROMPARTS(f910.year, f910.MONTH, 1) end data
from f910 join F9101 on f910.f91003 = f9101.f91003 and f910.YEAR = f9101.year and f910.MONTH = f9101.MONTH
where  case when coalesce(100*year(F910910)+month(F910910), 100*2100+1) = 100 * f910.YEAR + f910.month then F910910 else  DATEFROMPARTS(f910.year, f910.MONTH, 1) end <= @dt
and f910.f91003 = @f10003 order by f910.year desc, f910.month desc
union
select 4 as rank, f100.f10003 marca, F100958 Subdept, case when coalesce(year(F100910),2100) in (1900,2100) then F10022 else f100910 end data_Subdept, DATEFROMPARTS(1900,1,1) data from f100
join f1001 on f100.F10003=f1001.F10003
where f100.f10003 =@f10003
) x
order by data desc, rank
GO

alter FUNCTION [dbo].[DamiBirou] (@f10003 int, @dt DATE)
RETURNs table AS
return
 
SELECT top 1 Birou =   Birou, Data_Birou = data_Birou  from
(
SELECT top 1 1 as rank, F70403 marca,  F704180 Birou,  f70406 data_Birou,  F70406 Data from f704   WHERE F70404=5 AND F70406 <= @dt and F70403 = @f10003 ORDER BY F70406 DESC
union
select 2 as rank, f100.f10003 marca, F100959 Birou, case when coalesce(year(F100910),2100) in (1900,2100) then F10022 else f100910 end data_Birou,
case when coalesce(100*year(F100910)+month(F100910), 100*2100+1) = 100 * f01011 + f01012 then F100910 else  DATEFROMPARTS(f01011, f01012, 1) end data
from f100
inner join f1001 on f100.F10003=f1001.F10003
join f010 on 1=1 where f100.f10003 =@f10003 and case when coalesce(100*year(F100910)+month(F100910), 100*2100+1) = 100 * f01011 + f01012 then F100910 else 
DATEFROMPARTS(f01011, f01012, 1) end<=@dt
union
select top 1 3 as rank, f910.f91003 marca, F910959 Birou, case when coalesce(year(F910910),2100) in (1900,2100) then F91022 else f910910 end data_birou,
case when coalesce(100*year(F910910)+month(F910910), 100*2100+1) = 100 * f910.YEAR + f910.month then F910910 else  DATEFROMPARTS(f910.year, f910.MONTH, 1) end data
from f910 join F9101 on f910.f91003 = f9101.f91003 and f910.YEAR = f9101.year and f910.MONTH = f9101.MONTH
where case when coalesce(100*year(F910910)+month(F910910), 100*2100+1) = 100 * f910.YEAR + f910.month then F910910 else  DATEFROMPARTS(f910.year, f910.MONTH, 1) end <= @dt
and f910.f91003 = @f10003 order by f910.year desc, f910.month desc
union
select 4 as rank, f100.f10003 marca, F100959 Birou, case when coalesce(year(F100910),2100) in (1900,2100) then F10022 else f100910 end data_Birou, DATEFROMPARTS(1900,1,1) data from f100
join f1001 on f100.F10003=f1001.F10003
where f100.f10003 =@f10003
) x
order by data desc, rank
GO

UPDATE A
SET A."OraInceputDeLa" = Z.OraInceputDeLa, A.OraInceputLa = Z."OraInceputLa", A.OraSfarsitDeLa = Z."OraSfarsitDeLa", A.OraSfarsitLa = Z.OraSfarsitLa
FROM "Ptj_ContracteSchimburi" A
INNER JOIN (
SELECT "ContractId", "ZiSapt", "ProgramDen", "ProgramId", "OraInceput", "OraInceputDeLa", "OraInceputLa", "OraSfarsit", "OraSfarsitDeLa", "OraSfarsitLa", "ModVerificare"
FROM (
SELECT DISTINCT A."Id" AS "ContractId", A."Denumire" AS "ContractDen", 1 AS "ZiSapt", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb1", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN COALESCE(A."Program1", A."Program0") ELSE COALESCE(B."IdProgram", D."IdProgram") END AS "ProgramId",
C."Denumire" AS "ProgramDen", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb1", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN C."OraIntrare" ELSE COALESCE(B."OraInceput", D."OraInceput") END AS "OraInceput", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb1", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."OraInceputDeLa", D."OraInceputDeLa") END AS "OraInceputDeLa", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb1", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."OraInceputLa", D."OraInceputLa") END AS "OraInceputLa", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb1", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN C."OraIesire" ELSE COALESCE(B."OraSfarsit", D."OraSfarsit") END AS "OraSfarsit", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb1", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."OraSfarsitDeLa", D."OraSfarsitDeLa") END AS "OraSfarsitDeLa", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb1", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."OraSfarsitLa", D."OraSfarsitLa") END AS "OraSfarsitLa", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb1", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."ModVerificare", D."ModVerificare") END AS "ModVerificare"
FROM "Ptj_Contracte" A
LEFT JOIN "Ptj_ContracteSchimburi" B ON A."Id"=B."IdContract" AND B."TipSchimb"=1 
LEFT JOIN "Ptj_ContracteSchimburi" D ON A."Id"=D."IdContract" AND D."TipSchimb"=0 
LEFT JOIN "Ptj_Programe" C ON C."Id" = (CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb1", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN COALESCE(A."Program1", A."Program0") ELSE COALESCE(B."IdProgram", D."IdProgram") END)
UNION
SELECT DISTINCT A."Id" AS "ContractId", A."Denumire" AS "ContractDen", 2 AS "ZiSapt", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb2", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN COALESCE(A."Program2", A."Program0") ELSE COALESCE(B."IdProgram", D."IdProgram") END AS "ProgramId",
C."Denumire" AS "ProgramDen", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb2", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN C."OraIntrare" ELSE COALESCE(B."OraInceput", D."OraInceput") END AS "OraInceput", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb2", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."OraInceputDeLa", D."OraInceputDeLa") END AS "OraInceputDeLa", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb2", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."OraInceputLa", D."OraInceputLa") END AS "OraInceputLa", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb2", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN C."OraIesire" ELSE COALESCE(B."OraSfarsit", D."OraSfarsit") END AS "OraSfarsit", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb2", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."OraSfarsitDeLa", D."OraSfarsitDeLa") END AS "OraSfarsitDeLa", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb2", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."OraSfarsitLa", D."OraSfarsitLa") END AS "OraSfarsitLa", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb2", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."ModVerificare", D."ModVerificare") END AS "ModVerificare"
FROM "Ptj_Contracte" A
LEFT JOIN "Ptj_ContracteSchimburi" B ON A."Id"=B."IdContract" AND B."TipSchimb"=2
LEFT JOIN "Ptj_ContracteSchimburi" D ON A."Id"=D."IdContract" AND D."TipSchimb"=0 
LEFT JOIN "Ptj_Programe" C ON C."Id" = (CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb2", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN COALESCE(A."Program2", A."Program0") ELSE COALESCE(B."IdProgram", D."IdProgram") END)
UNION
SELECT DISTINCT A."Id" AS "ContractId", A."Denumire" AS "ContractDen", 3 AS "ZiSapt", 
CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb3", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN COALESCE(A."Program3", A."Program0") ELSE COALESCE(B."IdProgram", D."IdProgram") END AS "ProgramId",

CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb8", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN NULL ELSE COALESCE(B."ModVerificare", D."ModVerificare") END AS "ModVerificare"
FROM "Ptj_Contracte" A

LEFT JOIN "Ptj_ContracteSchimburi" D ON A."Id"=D."IdContract" AND D."TipSchimb"=0 
LEFT JOIN "Ptj_Programe" C ON C."Id" = (CASE WHEN COALESCE(A."TipSchimb8", A."TipSchimb0") = 1 THEN COALESCE(A."Program8", A."Program0") ELSE COALESCE(B."IdProgram", D."IdProgram") END)
) X
) Z ON A.IdContract=Z.ContractId AND A.IdProgram=Z.ProgramId AND A.TipSchimb=Z.ZiSapt

CREATE TABLE [dbo].[Curs_Anterior](
	[F10003] [int] NULL,
	[CursId] [int] NULL,
	[CursNume] [nvarchar](4000) NULL,
	[SesiuneId] [int] NULL,
	[SesiuneNume] [nvarchar](4000) NULL,

	[Organizator] [nvarchar](4000) NULL,
	[Trainer] [nvarchar](4000) NULL,
	[Certificat] [nvarchar](4000) NULL,
	[Observatii] [nvarchar](4000) NULL,
	[IdStare] [int] NULL,
	[IdAuto] [int] IDENTITY(1,1) NOT NULL,
	[USER_NO] [int] NULL,
	[TIME] [datetime] NULL,
	[DenCurs] [nvarchar](500) NULL,
	[CuloareStare] [nvarchar](50) NULL,
	[areFisier] [int] NULL,
	[DataInceput] [datetime] NULL,
	[DataSfarsit] [datetime] NULL,
 CONSTRAINT [Curs_Anterior_PK] PRIMARY KEY CLUSTERED 
(
	[IdAuto] ASC
)WITH (PAD_INDEX = OFF, STATISTICS_NORECOMPUTE = OFF, IGNORE_DUP_KEY = OFF, ALLOW_ROW_LOCKS = ON, ALLOW_PAGE_LOCKS = ON) ON [PRIMARY]
) ON [PRIMARY]

GO

(
	[IdAuto] ASC

) ON [PRIMARY]

) ON [PRIMARY]

CREATE FUNCTION [dbo].[DamiPozitii] (@IdPost int, @dt DATE) 
RETURNs table AS 
return 

	WITH 

	HCEfectiv (IdPost, Activi, Suspendati, Candidati)  as
	(
		SELECT IdPost, 
		SUM(CASE WHEN Y.F10022 <= @dt AND @dt <= Z.DataPlecare THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS Activi,
		SUM(CASE WHEN 
			(Y.F100922 <= @dt AND @dt <= (CASE WHEN COALESCE(Y.F100924, '2100-01-01') = '2100-01-01' THEN Y.F100923 ELSE Y.F100924 END)) 
			AND 
			(Y.F10022 <= @dt AND @dt <= Z.DataPlecare) 
		THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS Suspendati,  
		SUM(CASE WHEN Y.F10025 IN (900) THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS Candidati
		FROM Org_relPostAngajat X 
		INNER JOIN F100 Y ON X.F10003=Y.F10003
		OUTER APPLY DamiDataPlecare(X.F10003, @dt) Z
		WHERE X.DataInceput <= @dt AND @dt <= X.DataSfarsit GROUP BY IdPost
	),

	tree (Id, IdSuperior, Stare, DataInceput, DataSfarsit, Pozitii, PozitiiAprobate, Activi, Suspendati, Candidati) as 
	(
		SELECT A.Id, A.IdSuperior, A.Stare, A.DataInceput, A.DataSfarsit, COALESCE(B.Pozitii,0) AS Pozitii, COALESCE(B.PozitiiAprobate,0) AS PozitiiAprobate,
		COALESCE(C.Activi,0) AS Activi, COALESCE(C.Suspendati,0) AS Suspendati, COALESCE(C.Candidati,0) AS Candidati
		FROM Org_Posturi A
		LEFT JOIN Org_PosturiPozitii B ON A.Id = B.IdPost AND B.DataInceput <= @dt AND @dt <= B.DataSfarsit 
		LEFT JOIN HCEfectiv C ON A.Id = C.IdPost
		WHERE A.Id = @IdPost AND A.DataInceput <= @dt AND @dt <= A.DataSfarsit AND COALESCE(A.Stare,0)=1
		UNION ALL
		SELECT A.Id, A.IdSuperior, A.Stare, A.DataInceput, A.DataSfarsit, 
		(SELECT COALESCE(X.Pozitii,0) AS Pozitii FROM Org_PosturiPozitii X WHERE X.IdPost=A.Id AND X.DataInceput <= @dt AND @dt <= X.DataSfarsit) AS Pozitii,
		(SELECT COALESCE(X.PozitiiAprobate,0) AS PozitiiAprobate FROM Org_PosturiPozitii X WHERE X.IdPost=A.Id AND X.DataInceput <= @dt AND @dt <= X.DataSfarsit) AS PozitiiAprobate,
		(SELECT COALESCE(Y.Activi,0) AS Activi FROM HCEfectiv Y WHERE Y.IdPost = A.Id) AS Activi,
		(SELECT COALESCE(Y.Suspendati,0) AS Suspendati FROM HCEfectiv Y WHERE Y.IdPost = A.Id) AS Suspendati,
		(SELECT COALESCE(Y.Candidati,0) AS Candidati FROM HCEfectiv Y WHERE Y.IdPost = A.Id) AS Candidati
		FROM Org_Posturi A 
		INNER JOIN tree D on A.IdSuperior = D.Id AND D.DataInceput <= @dt AND @dt <= D.DataSfarsit
		WHERE 
		A.DataInceput <= @dt AND @dt <= A.DataSfarsit AND COALESCE(A.Stare,0)=1
	)

	SELECT 
	SUM(COALESCE(Pozitii,0)) AS Pozitii,  
	SUM(COALESCE(PozitiiAprobate,0)) AS PozitiiAprobate, 
	SUM(COALESCE(Activi,0)) AS Activi, 
	SUM(COALESCE(Suspendati,0)) AS Suspendati, 
	SUM(COALESCE(Candidati,0)) AS Candidati
	FROM tree;

GO

ALTER FUNCTION [dbo].[DamiDataPlecare] (@f10003 int, @dt DATE) 
RETURNs table AS 
return 

	 
       SELECT top 1 DataPlecare =   DataPlecare from
(
SELECT top 1 1 as rank, F70403 marca,  F70406 - 1 dataplecare,  F70406 Data from f704 join f100 on f70403 = f10003 WHERE F70404=4 AND F70406 <= @dt and F70406 - 1 >= f10022 and F70403 = @f10003 ORDER BY F70406 DESC
union
select 2 as rank, f10003 marca, f10023 Dataplecare,   DATEFROMPARTS(f01011, f01012, 1) data from f100 join f010 on 1=1 where f10003 =@f10003 and DATEFROMPARTS(f01011, f01012, 1)<=@dt
union
select top 1 3 as rank, f91003 marca, f91023 dataplecare,  DATEFROMPARTS(year, MONTH, 1) data from f910 where DATEFROMPARTS(year, MONTH, 1)<= @dt and f91003 = @f10003 order by year desc, month desc
union
select 4 as rank, f10003 marca, F10023 dataplecare, DATEFROMPARTS(1900,1,1) data from f100 where f10003 =@f10003
) x
order by data desc, rank

drop SEQUENCE Ptj_Cereri_Id_SEQ
GO

declare @maxId as int 
select @maxId = max(Id) + 1 from Ptj_Cereri
declare @s nvarchar(4000);
set @s = N'
CREATE SEQUENCE Ptj_Cereri_Id_SEQ  AS INTEGER  
START WITH ' + cast(@maxId as nvarchar) + '
INCREMENT BY 1  
NO CYCLE;'

EXEC (@s);

alter FUNCTION [dbo].[DamiDept] (@f10003 int, @dt DATE)
RETURNs table AS
return
 
       SELECT top 1 Dept =   Dept, Subdept =   Subdept,  Birou =   Birou, Data_dept = data_dept  from
(
SELECT top 1 1 as rank, F70403 marca,  F70417 dept,  F70418 Subdept, F704180 Birou, f70406 data_dept,  F70406 Data from f704   WHERE F70404=5 AND F70406 <= @dt and F70403 = @f10003 ORDER BY F70406 DESC
union
select 2 as rank, f100.f10003 marca, f10007 dept,  F100958 Subdept,  F100959 Birou, case when coalesce(year(F100910),2100) in (1900,2100) then F10022 else f100910 end data_dept, case when coalesce(100*year(F100910)+month(F100910), 100*2100+1) = 100 * f01011 + f01012 then F100910 else  DATEFROMPARTS(f01011, f01012, 1) end data from f100 join f1001 on f100.F10003=f1001.F10003  join f010 on 1=1 where f100.f10003 =@f10003 and case when coalesce(100*year(F100910)+month(F100910), 100*2100+1) = 100 * f01011 + f01012 then F100910 else  DATEFROMPARTS(f01011, f01012, 1) end<=@dt
union
select top 1 3 as rank, f910.f91003 marca, F91007 dept, F910958 subdept, F910959 Birou, case when coalesce(year(F910910),2100) in (1900,2100) then F91022 else f910910 end data_dept, case when coalesce(100*year(F910910)+month(F910910), 100*2100+1) = 100 * f910.YEAR + f910.month then F910910 else  DATEFROMPARTS(f910.year, f910.MONTH, 1) end data from f910 join f9101 on f910.F91003=f9101.F91003 and f910.year = f9101.year and f910.month = f9101.MONTH where case when coalesce(100*year(F910910)+month(F910910), 100*2100+1) = 100 * f910.YEAR + f910.month then F910910 else  DATEFROMPARTS(f910.year, f910.MONTH, 1) end <= @dt and f910.f91003 = @f10003 order by f910.year desc, f910.month desc
union
select 4 as rank, f100.f10003 marca, F10007 dept,  F100958 Subdept, F100959 Birou, case when coalesce(year(F100910),2100) in (1900,2100) then F10022 else f100910 end data_dept, DATEFROMPARTS(1900,1,1) data from f100 join f1001 on f100.F10003=f1001.F10003 where f100.f10003 =@f10003
) x
order by data desc, rank
GO



alter FUNCTION [dbo].[DamiSubdept] (@f10003 int, @dt DATE)
RETURNs table AS
return
 
SELECT top 1 Subdept =   Subdept, Data_Subdept = data_Subdept  from
(
SELECT top 1 1 as rank, F70403 marca,  F70418 Subdept,  f70406 data_Subdept,  F70406 Data from f704   WHERE F70404=5 AND F70406 <= @dt and F70403 = @f10003 ORDER BY F70406 DESC
union
select 2 as rank, f100.f10003 marca, F100958 Subdept, case when coalesce(year(F100910),2100) in (1900,2100) then F10022 else f100910 end data_Subdept,
case when coalesce(100*year(F100910)+month(F100910), 100*2100+1) = 100 * f01011 + f01012 then F100910 else  DATEFROMPARTS(f01011, f01012, 1) end data
from f100
inner join f1001 on f100.F10003=f1001.F10003
join f010 on 1=1 where f100.f10003 =@f10003 and case when coalesce(100*year(F100910)+month(F100910), 100*2100+1) = 100 * f01011 + f01012 then F100910 else 
DATEFROMPARTS(f01011, f01012, 1) end<=@dt
union
select top 1 3 as rank, f910.f91003 marca, F910958 subdept, case when coalesce(year(F910910),2100) in (1900,2100) then F91022 else f910910 end data_subdept,
case when coalesce(100*year(F910910)+month(F910910), 100*2100+1) = 100 * f910.YEAR + f910.month then F910910 else  DATEFROMPARTS(f910.year, f910.MONTH, 1) end data
from f910 join F9101 on f910.f91003 = f9101.f91003 and f910.YEAR = f9101.year and f910.MONTH = f9101.MONTH
where  case when coalesce(100*year(F910910)+month(F910910), 100*2100+1) = 100 * f910.YEAR + f910.month then F910910 else  DATEFROMPARTS(f910.year, f910.MONTH, 1) end <= @dt
and f910.f91003 = @f10003 order by f910.year desc, f910.month desc
union
select 4 as rank, f100.f10003 marca, F100958 Subdept, case when coalesce(year(F100910),2100) in (1900,2100) then F10022 else f100910 end data_Subdept, DATEFROMPARTS(1900,1,1) data from f100
join f1001 on f100.F10003=f1001.F10003
where f100.f10003 =@f10003
) x
order by data desc, rank
GO

alter FUNCTION [dbo].[DamiBirou] (@f10003 int, @dt DATE)
RETURNs table AS
return
 
SELECT top 1 Birou =   Birou, Data_Birou = data_Birou  from
(
SELECT top 1 1 as rank, F70403 marca,  F704180 Birou,  f70406 data_Birou,  F70406 Data from f704   WHERE F70404=5 AND F70406 <= @dt and F70403 = @f10003 ORDER BY F70406 DESC
union
select 2 as rank, f100.f10003 marca, F100959 Birou, case when coalesce(year(F100910),2100) in (1900,2100) then F10022 else f100910 end data_Birou,
case when coalesce(100*year(F100910)+month(F100910), 100*2100+1) = 100 * f01011 + f01012 then F100910 else  DATEFROMPARTS(f01011, f01012, 1) end data
from f100
inner join f1001 on f100.F10003=f1001.F10003
join f010 on 1=1 where f100.f10003 =@f10003 and case when coalesce(100*year(F100910)+month(F100910), 100*2100+1) = 100 * f01011 + f01012 then F100910 else 
DATEFROMPARTS(f01011, f01012, 1) end<=@dt
union
select top 1 3 as rank, f910.f91003 marca, F910959 Birou, case when coalesce(year(F910910),2100) in (1900,2100) then F91022 else f910910 end data_birou,
case when coalesce(100*year(F910910)+month(F910910), 100*2100+1) = 100 * f910.YEAR + f910.month then F910910 else  DATEFROMPARTS(f910.year, f910.MONTH, 1) end data
from f910 join F9101 on f910.f91003 = f9101.f91003 and f910.YEAR = f9101.year and f910.MONTH = f9101.MONTH
where case when coalesce(100*year(F910910)+month(F910910), 100*2100+1) = 100 * f910.YEAR + f910.month then F910910 else  DATEFROMPARTS(f910.year, f910.MONTH, 1) end <= @dt
and f910.f91003 = @f10003 order by f910.year desc, f910.month desc
union
select 4 as rank, f100.f10003 marca, F100959 Birou, case when coalesce(year(F100910),2100) in (1900,2100) then F10022 else f100910 end data_Birou, DATEFROMPARTS(1900,1,1) data from f100
join f1001 on f100.F10003=f1001.F10003
where f100.f10003 =@f10003
) x
order by data desc, rank
GO

ALTER FUNCTION [dbo].[DamiPozitii] (@IdPost int, @dt DATE) 
RETURNs table AS 
return 

	WITH 

	HCEfectiv (IdPost, Activi, Suspendati, Candidati)  as
	(
		SELECT IdPost, 
		SUM(CASE WHEN Y.F10025=900 THEN 0 ELSE CASE WHEN Y.F10022 <= @dt AND @dt <= Z.DataPlecare THEN 1 ELSE 0 END END) AS Activi,
		SUM(CASE WHEN 
			(Y.F100922 <= @dt AND @dt <= (CASE WHEN COALESCE(Y.F100924, '2100-01-01') = '2100-01-01' THEN Y.F100923 ELSE Y.F100924 END)) 
			AND 
			(Y.F10022 <= @dt AND @dt <= Z.DataPlecare) 
		THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS Suspendati,  
		SUM(CASE WHEN Y.F10025 IN (900) THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS Candidati
		FROM Org_relPostAngajat X 
		INNER JOIN F100 Y ON X.F10003=Y.F10003
		OUTER APPLY DamiDataPlecare(X.F10003, @dt) Z
		WHERE X.DataInceput <= @dt AND @dt <= X.DataSfarsit GROUP BY IdPost
	),

	tree (Id, IdSuperior, Stare, DataInceput, DataSfarsit, Pozitii, PozitiiAprobate, Activi, Suspendati, Candidati) as 
	(
		SELECT A.Id, A.IdSuperior, A.Stare, A.DataInceput, A.DataSfarsit, COALESCE(B.Pozitii,0) AS Pozitii, COALESCE(B.PozitiiAprobate,0) AS PozitiiAprobate,
		COALESCE(C.Activi,0) AS Activi, COALESCE(C.Suspendati,0) AS Suspendati, COALESCE(C.Candidati,0) AS Candidati
		FROM Org_Posturi A
		LEFT JOIN Org_PosturiPozitii B ON A.Id = B.IdPost AND B.DataInceput <= @dt AND @dt <= B.DataSfarsit 
		LEFT JOIN HCEfectiv C ON A.Id = C.IdPost
		WHERE A.Id = @IdPost AND A.DataInceput <= @dt AND @dt <= A.DataSfarsit AND COALESCE(A.Stare,0)=1
		UNION ALL
		SELECT A.Id, A.IdSuperior, A.Stare, A.DataInceput, A.DataSfarsit, 
		(SELECT COALESCE(X.Pozitii,0) AS Pozitii FROM Org_PosturiPozitii X WHERE X.IdPost=A.Id AND X.DataInceput <= @dt AND @dt <= X.DataSfarsit) AS Pozitii,
		(SELECT COALESCE(X.PozitiiAprobate,0) AS PozitiiAprobate FROM Org_PosturiPozitii X WHERE X.IdPost=A.Id AND X.DataInceput <= @dt AND @dt <= X.DataSfarsit) AS PozitiiAprobate,
		(SELECT COALESCE(Y.Activi,0) AS Activi FROM HCEfectiv Y WHERE Y.IdPost = A.Id) AS Activi,
		(SELECT COALESCE(Y.Suspendati,0) AS Suspendati FROM HCEfectiv Y WHERE Y.IdPost = A.Id) AS Suspendati,
		(SELECT COALESCE(Y.Candidati,0) AS Candidati FROM HCEfectiv Y WHERE Y.IdPost = A.Id) AS Candidati
		FROM Org_Posturi A 
		INNER JOIN tree D on A.IdSuperior = D.Id AND D.DataInceput <= @dt AND @dt <= D.DataSfarsit
		WHERE 
		A.DataInceput <= @dt AND @dt <= A.DataSfarsit AND COALESCE(A.Stare,0)=1
	)

	SELECT 
	SUM(COALESCE(Pozitii,0)) AS Pozitii,  
	SUM(COALESCE(PozitiiAprobate,0)) AS PozitiiAprobate, 
	SUM(COALESCE(Activi,0)) AS Activi, 
	SUM(COALESCE(Suspendati,0)) AS Suspendati, 
	SUM(COALESCE(Candidati,0)) AS Candidati
	FROM tree;

ALTER FUNCTION [dbo].[CalculCO] (
       @f10003 INT,
  @zi datetime,
  @mod int,
  @grila int
)
  RETURNS @CalculCO TABLE (
      ZileCuveniteAn int,
      ZileCuvenite int,
      ZileCuveniteZi int,
      ZileAnPrecedent int
  )
AS

BEGIN

declare @ZileCuveniteAn int,  @ZileCuveniteAnSuplim18Ani int, @ZileCuveniteAnSuplimHand int, @ZileCuvenite int, @ZileCuveniteZi int, @ZileAnPrecedent int, @ZileAngajare int, @ZileAngajareZi int,@ZileSuspendare int, @ZileSuspendareZi int, @ZileSuspendare18Ani int, @ZileSuspendare18AniZi int, @ZileSuspendareHand int, @ZileSuspendareHandZi int, @PrimaZiAn date, @UltimaZiAn date, @UltimaZi18Ani date, @UltimaZiHand date, @UltimaZi18aniZi date, @UltimaZiHandZi date, @TipCalcul int, @ZileSuplimentare int, @LuniVechime int, @DataPrimeiAngajari date, @CalculCOProp18Ani int, @CalculCOPropHand int, @ZileAn int, @SuspendariExcluse nvarchar(100), @f10023 datetime, @DataAnCalculVechime datetime


-- @TipCalcul
--  1 -- se calculeaza vechimea in munca in ultima zi din an
-- 2. se calculeaza vechimea in munca in prima zi din an
--  3 se calculeaza vechimea in munca in ziua angajarii
--  4 -- se calculeaza vechimea in munca in ultima zi din an, iar pentru cei plecati in timpul anului la data plecarii

--   11 -- se calculeaza vechimea in companie in ultima zi din an
-- 12 se calculeaza vechimea in companie in prima zi din an
--  13 se calculeaza vechimea in companie in ziua angajarii
--14 - se calculeaza vechimea in companie in ultima zi din an, iar pentru cei plecati in timpul anului la data plecarii

--   21 -- se calculeaza vechimea de la data angajarii in ultima zi din an
-- 22 se calculeaza vechimea de la data angajarii in prima zi din an
--  23 se calculeaza vechimea de la data angajarii in ziua angajarii
--   24 -- se calculeaza vechimea de la data angajarii in ultima zi din an, iar pentru cei plecati in timpul anului la data plecarii

--   31 -- se calculeaza vechimea de la data primei angajarii in ultima zi din an
-- 32 - se calculeaza vechimea de la data primei angajarii in prima zi din an
--  33  -se calculeaza vechimea de la data primei angajarii in ziua angajarii 
--   34 -- se calculeaza vechimea de la data primei angajarii in ultima zi din an, iar pentru cei plecati in timpul anului la data plecarii

-- 99 - particular

select @ZileAn = 365
if  year(@zi) % 4 = 0
  select @ZileAn = 366;

if isnull(@grila,0)= 0
  select @grila = f10072 from f100 where f10003 = @f10003;


select @f10023 = DataPlecare from DamiDataPlecare(@f10003, @zi);

Select @ZileSuplimentare = Convert(int,isnull((select "Valoare" from "tblParametrii" where "Nume"='NrZilePersoanaDizabilitatiSauMaiMica18Ani'),3));
Select @TipCalcul = Convert(int,isnull((select "Valoare" from "tblParametrii" where "Nume"='ModCalculZileCOCuvenite'),1));
Select @CalculCOProp18Ani = Convert(int,isnull((select "Valoare" from "tblParametrii" where "Nume"='ModCalculZileCO_Proportional_18Ani'),0));
Select @CalculCOPropHand = Convert(int,isnull((select "Valoare" from "tblParametrii" where "Nume"='ModCalculZileCO_Proportional_Handicap'),0));
Select @SuspendariExcluse = Convert(nvarchar(100),isnull((select "Valoare" from "tblParametrii" where "Nume"='ModCalculZileCO_SuspendariExcluse'),' '));


Select @PrimaZiAn = CASE WHEN cast(F10022 as date) < convert(varchar, year(@zi))  +  '-01-01'  THEN convert(varchar, year(@zi))  + '-01-01'  ELSE cast(F10022 as date) END, @UltimaZiAn = CASE WHEN cast(@f10023 as date) < convert(varchar, year(@zi))  +  '-12-31'  THEN cast(@f10023 as date) ELSE convert(varchar, year(@zi))  +  '-12-31'  END from (select * from F100 where f10003 = @F10003) a ;

Select @ZileAngajare = datediff(day, @PrimaZiAn, @UltimaZiAn)+1 , @ZileAngajareZi = datediff(day, @PrimaZiAn,  (CASE WHEN cast(@f10023 as date) < @zi THEN cast(@f10023 as date) ELSE @zi END))+1 from (select * from F100 where f10003 = @F10003) a  ;

Select @DataPrimeiAngajari = case when year(isnull(F1001049,'2100-01-01')) not in (1900,2100) then F1001049 else F10022 end from (select f100.f10003, f100.f10022, f1001.F1001049 from F100 join f1001 on f100.f10003 = f1001.f10003 where f100.f10003 = @F10003) a  ;


Select @DataAnCalculVechime = case when @TipCalcul in (0,1,11,21,31) then convert(varchar, year(@zi)) + '-12-31'
								when @TipCalcul in (2,12,22,32) then convert(varchar, year(@zi))  +  '-01-01'
								when @TipCalcul in (3,13,23,33) then @zi
								when  @TipCalcul in (4,14,24,34) then case when year(@f10023) > year(@zi) then convert(varchar, year(@zi)) + '-12-31' else @f10023 end
								end ;

Select @LuniVechime = case 

when @TipCalcul in (0,1,2,3,4) then
	ISNULL(convert(int,substring(F100644,1,2)),0) * 12 + ISNULL(convert(int,substring(F100644,3,2)),0) + DATEDIFF (MONTH,   (select convert(nvarchar(4),F01011) + '-' +
    convert(nvarchar(4),F01012) + '-01' from F010), @DataAnCalculVechime)

when @TipCalcul in (11,12,13,14) then
	ISNULL(convert(int,substring(F100643,1,2)),0) * 12 + ISNULL(convert(int,substring(F100643,3,2)),0) + DATEDIFF (MONTH,   (select convert(nvarchar(4),F01011) + '-' +
    convert(nvarchar(4),F01012) + '-01' from F010), @DataAnCalculVechime) 

when @TipCalcul in (21,22,23,24) then
     DATEDIFF (MONTH, F10022, @DataAnCalculVechime)
   - case when day(f10022) > day(@DataAnCalculVechime) then 1 else 0 end  
 
when @TipCalcul in (31,32,33,34) then
	  DATEDIFF (MONTH, @DataPrimeiAngajari, @DataAnCalculVechime)
	- case when day(@DataPrimeiAngajari) > day(@DataAnCalculVechime) then 1 else 0 end  

when @TipCalcul = 99 then
     DATEDIFF (MONTH,  case when f10022 <= '2018-02-14' then '2018-02-14' else f10022 end , @zi )
   - case when ( case when f10022 <= '2018-02-14' then 14 else day(f10022) end) > day(@zi)  then 1 else 0 end

 end     from f100 where f10003 = @f10003;

if isnull(@LuniVechime,0) < =0 
	 select @LuniVechime = 0;

select @ZileCuveniteAnSuplimHand  = CASE WHEN ISNULL(a.F10027,0)>=2 and (f100271 = '2100-01-01' or f100271 = '1900-01-01' or @PrimaZiAn <= f100271) THEN convert(int, @ZileSuplimentare) else 0 end,
@ZileCuveniteAnSuplim18Ani =   case when dateadd(year,18,f10021) >= @PrimaZiAn  then convert(int, @ZileSuplimentare,0)  else 0 end
 from (select * from F100 where f10003 = @F10003) a ;  

If @mod <> 1
   select @ZileCuveniteAn = CuveniteAn from ptj_tblzileco where an=year(@zi) and f10003 = @f10003 else
  select @ZileCuveniteAn =     c.F02615 + @ZileCuveniteAnSuplim18Ani + @ZileCuveniteAnSuplimHand
      from (select * from F100 where f10003 = @F10003) a    left join F026 c on convert(int,@grila) = c.F02604 and
      (convert(int,c.F02610/100) * 12) <= @LuniVechime and @LuniVechime < (convert(int,c.F02611/100) * 12)  where (year(@zi)  between year(F10022) and year(F10023) ) and a.F10003= @f10003 ;


 select @UltimaZi18Ani = case when  dateadd(year, 18, f10021) <= @UltimaZiAn  then dateadd(year, 18, f10021)  else @UltimaZiAn end,  @UltimaZiHand = case when f100271 = '2100-01-01' or f100271 = '1900-01-01' or f100271 > @UltimaZiAn then @UltimaZiAn else f100271 end  from (select * from F100 where f10003 = @F10003) a;

 select @UltimaZi18AniZi = case when @UltimaZi18Ani <= CONVERT(date,@zi) then @UltimaZi18Ani else CONVERT(date,@zi) end,
  @UltimaZiHandZi = case when @UltimaZiHand <= CONVERT(date,@zi) then @UltimaZiHand else CONVERT(date,@zi) end;

  with xx as  ( select f111.f11103 Marca, f111.f11105 de_la_data, case when f111.f11107='2100-01-01' then f111.f11106 else dateadd(d,-1,f111.f11107) end la_data from f111
	 inner join
(select a.f11103, a.f11105, case when a.f11107='2100-01-01' then a.f11106 else dateadd(d,-1,a.f11107) end f11107, a.time, max(b.time) timp from F111 a inner join f111 b  on
a.F11103 = b.F11103 and  (a.f11105 <= case when b.f11107='2100-01-01' then b.f11106 else dateadd(d,-1,b.f11107) end   and b.f11105 <= case when a.f11107='2100-01-01'
then a.f11106 else dateadd(d,-1,a.f11107) end)  group by a.f11103, a.f11105, case when a.f11107='2100-01-01' then a.f11106 else dateadd(d,-1,a.f11107) end, a.time) t  on f111.f11103 = t.f11103 and
f111.f11105 = t.f11105 and   case when f111.f11107='2100-01-01' then f111.f11106 else dateadd(d,-1,f111.f11107) end = t.f11107 and f111.time = t.timp 
where CHARINDEX(concat(',',ltrim(rtrim(convert(nvarchar(100),f111.f11104))),','), concat(',',ltrim(rtrim(@SuspendariExcluse)),','))  = 0  union all select f10003 Marca, datainceput de_la_data, datasfarsit la_data  from ptj_cereri inner join Ptj_tblAbsente on Ptj_Cereri.IdAbsenta = Ptj_tblAbsente.id  where
ptj_cereri.IdStare=3 and isnull(Ptj_tblAbsente.AbsenteCFPInCalculCO,0) = 1  ),  yy as  (select distinct a.marca, min(b.de_la_data) de_la_data, max(b.la_data) la_data from xx a  inner join xx b on a.marca = b.marca and  (a.de_la_data <= b.la_data and b.de_la_data <= a.la_data)  group by a.marca, a.de_la_data, a.la_data),
 f111_2 as   (select distinct a.marca f11103, min(b.de_la_data) f11105, max(b.la_data)  f11107 from yy a  inner join yy b on a.marca = b.marca and (a.de_la_data <=
  b.la_data and b.de_la_data <= a.la_data)  group by a.marca, a.de_la_data, a.la_data)

 select  @ZileSuspendare= (select COALESCE(SUM(datediff(d,CASE WHEN F11105 <  @PrimaZiAn THEN @PrimaZiAn else F11105 END,CASE WHEN F11107 > @UltimaZiAn THEN @UltimaZiAn else F11107 END) + 1) ,0) from (select * from F100 where f10003 = @F10003) a  join f111_2 Z on a.f10003 = z.f11103  and F11105 <= F11107 AND F11107 >= @PrimaZiAn AND F11105 <= @UltimaZiAn) , @ZileSuspendareZi = (select COALESCE(SUM(datediff(d,CASE WHEN F11105 < @PrimaZiAn THEN @PrimaZiAn else F11105 END,CASE WHEN F11107 > CONVERT(date,@zi) THEN CONVERT(date,@zi) else F11107 END)+1) ,0)  from (select * from F100 where f10003 = @F10003) a  join f111_2 Z on a.f10003 = z.f11103  and F11105 <= F11107 AND F11107 >= @PrimaZiAn AND F11105 <= CONVERT(date,@zi)),  @ZileSuspendare18Ani= (select COALESCE(SUM(datediff(d,CASE WHEN F11105 <  @PrimaZiAn THEN @PrimaZiAn else F11105 END,CASE WHEN F11107 > @UltimaZi18Ani THEN @UltimaZi18Ani else F11107 END) + 1) ,0) from (select * from F100 where f10003 = @F10003) a  join f111_2 Z on a.f10003 = z.f11103  and F11105 <= F11107 AND F11107 >= @PrimaZiAn AND F11105 <= @UltimaZi18Ani) , @ZileSuspendare18AniZi = (select COALESCE(SUM(datediff(d,CASE WHEN F11105 < @PrimaZiAn THEN @PrimaZiAn else F11105 END,CASE WHEN F11107 > @UltimaZi18AniZi THEN @UltimaZi18AniZi else F11107 END)+1) ,0)  from (select * from F100 where f10003 = @F10003) a  join f111_2 Z on a.f10003 = z.f11103  and F11105 <= F11107 AND F11107 >= @PrimaZiAn AND F11105 <= @UltimaZi18AniZi),  @ZileSuspendareHand = (select COALESCE(SUM(datediff(d,CASE WHEN F11105 <  @PrimaZiAn THEN @PrimaZiAn else F11105 END,CASE WHEN F11107 > @UltimaZiHand THEN @UltimaZiHand else F11107 END) + 1) ,0) from (select * from F100 where f10003 = @F10003) a  join f111_2 Z on a.f10003 = z.f11103  and F11105 <= F11107 AND F11107 >= @PrimaZiAn AND F11105 <= @UltimaZiHand) , @ZileSuspendareHandZi = (select COALESCE(SUM(datediff(d,CASE WHEN F11105 < @PrimaZiAn THEN @PrimaZiAn else F11105 END,CASE WHEN F11107 > @UltimaZiHandZi THEN @UltimaZiHandZi else F11107 END)+1) ,0)  from (select * from F100 where f10003 = @F10003) a  join f111_2 Z on a.f10003 = z.f11103  and F11105 <= F11107 AND F11107 >= @PrimaZiAn AND F11105 <= @UltimaZiHandZi) ;



 select @ZileCuvenite = case when @mod= 1 then 
			round(convert(float,(@ZileCuveniteAn -  @ZileCuveniteAnSuplim18Ani - @ZileCuveniteAnSuplimHand) * (@ZileAngajare - isnull(@ZileSuspendare,0))) /CONVERT(float,@ZileAn),0) +
   convert(int, round( case when @CalculCOPropHand = 0  then 1 else (datediff(day, @PrimaZiAn,  @UltimaZiHand)+1 - @ZileSuspendareHand) / convert(float, @ZileAn) end * @ZileCuveniteAnSuplimHand,0)) +
	convert(int, round( case when @CalculCOProp18Ani = 0  then 1 else (datediff(day, @PrimaZiAn,  @UltimaZi18Ani)+1 - @ZileSuspendare18Ani) / convert(float, @ZileAn) end * @ZileCuveniteAnSuplim18Ani,0)) 
           else (select Cuvenite from Ptj_tblZileCO where f10003 = @f10003 and an = year(@zi)) end;

 select @ZileCuveniteZi =  round(convert(float, (@ZileCuveniteAn -  @ZileCuveniteAnSuplim18Ani - @ZileCuveniteAnSuplimHand)  * (@ZileAngajareZi - isnull(@ZileSuspendareZi,0))) /CONVERT(float,@ZileAn),0)+
   convert(int, round( case when @CalculCOPropHand = 0  then 1 else (datediff(day, @PrimaZiAn,  @UltimaZiHandZi)+1 - @ZileSuspendareHandZi) / convert(float, @ZileAn) end * @ZileCuveniteAnSuplimHand,0)) +
	convert(int, round( case when @CalculCOProp18Ani = 0  then 1 else (datediff(day, @PrimaZiAn,  @UltimaZi18aniZi)+1 - @ZileSuspendare18AniZi) / convert(float, @ZileAn) end * @ZileCuveniteAnSuplim18Ani,0)) 

INSERT INTO @CalculCO
SELECT @ZileCuveniteAn, isnull(@ZileCuvenite,0), @ZileCuveniteZi, isnull((select SoldAnterior from Ptj_tblZileCO where f10003 = @f10003 and an=year(@zi)),0);

 RETURN;
END

ALTER VIEW [dbo].[Admin_Cursuri_VIEW] as
 select Marca,NumeComplet,IdTipCurs,IdDescriereCurs,NumeFurnizor,TemaCurs,Info,NrOre,DataCurs,Buget,PerioadaAmortizare,AutorizareExpirare,USER_NO,[TIME],IdAuto,DataInceput, DataSfarsit, NrZile,IdMoneda, Operator
from
Admin_Cursuri
UNION ALL
SELECT Marca,NumeComplet,IdTipCurs,IdDescriereCurs,NumeFurnizor,TemaCurs,Info,NrOre,DataCurs,Buget,PerioadaAmortizare,AutorizareExpirare,USER_NO,[TIME],IdAuto,DataInceput, DataSfarsit, NrZile,IdMoneda, null as Operator
from
Cursuri_VIEW
UNION ALL
SELECT Id_Angajat as marca, Curs_tblCursSesiune.denumire as numecomplet, tipsesiune as idtipcurs, null as IdDescriereCurs, null as NumeFurnizor, null as TemaCurs, Curs_tblCursSesiune.observatii as info, TotalOre as nrore,
null as datacurs,Curs_tblCursSesiune.Buget, null as PerioadaAmortizare, null as AutorizareExpirare,Curs_tblCursSesiune.USER_NO,Curs_tblCursSesiune.[TIME],Curs_tblCursSesiune.IdAuto, DataInceput, DataSfarsit, null as NrZile,  IdMoneda, curs_tblcurs.OrganizatorId as Operator

from Curs_tblCursSesiune 
join curs_tblcurs on curs_tblcurs.id = Curs_tblCursSesiune.IdCurs
join Curs_relCursAngajati on Curs_relCursAngajati.Id_Curs = curs_tblcurs.id

CREATE VIEW [dbo].[Schedule]
AS
SELECT 'CR' + CAST(ce.IdAuto AS VARCHAR) AS Id, 1 AS Type, ce.Id AS InternalId, ce.F10003 AS EmployeeId, 
		ab.Denumire AS Name, ce.Observatii AS Remarks, ce.IdAbsenta AS LabelId, ce.IdStare AS StatusId,
		ce.DataInceput AS StartDate, DATEADD(DD, 1, ce.DataSfarsit) AS EndDate 
FROM Ptj_Cereri AS ce
INNER JOIN Ptj_tblAbsente AS ab ON ce.IdAbsenta = ab.Id
INNER JOIN Ptj_tblStari AS st ON ce.IdStare = st.Id
UNION
SELECT 'CC' + CAST(cc.IdAuto AS VARCHAR) AS Id, 2 AS Type, cc.IdAuto AS InternalId, cc.F10003 AS EmployeeId, 
		fcc.F06205 AS Name, cc.Observatii AS Remarks, 0 AS LabelId, cc.IdStare AS StatusId,		
		ISNULL(cc.De, DATEADD(HH, 9, CAST(cc.Ziua AS DATETIME))) AS StartDate, 
		ISNULL(cc.La, DATEADD(MI, (9 * 60) + ISNULL(cc.NrOre1, 0) + ISNULL(cc.NrOre2, 0) + ISNULL(cc.NrOre3, 0), CAST(cc.Ziua AS DATETIME))) AS EndDate
FROM Ptj_CC AS cc
INNER JOIN F062 AS fcc ON cc.F06204 = fcc.F06204
INNER JOIN Ptj_tblStari AS st ON cc.IdStare = st.Id;
GO

	[CodIndemnizatie] [int] NULL,

	[NumarCM] [nvarchar](20) NULL,

CREATE TABLE [dbo].[CM_tblStari](
	[Id] [int] NULL,
	[Denumire] [nvarchar](50) NULL,
	[Culoare] [nvarchar](50) NULL,
	[USER_NO] [int] NULL,
	[TIME] [datetime] NULL,
	[IdAuto] [int] IDENTITY(1,1) NOT NULL,
 CONSTRAINT [CM_tblStari_PK] PRIMARY KEY CLUSTERED 
(
	[IdAuto] ASC
)WITH (PAD_INDEX = OFF, STATISTICS_NORECOMPUTE = OFF, IGNORE_DUP_KEY = OFF, ALLOW_ROW_LOCKS = ON, ALLOW_PAGE_LOCKS = ON) ON [PRIMARY]
) ON [PRIMARY]

GO
SET IDENTITY_INSERT [dbo].[CM_tblStari] ON 
GO

CREATE PROCEDURE [dbo].[CalculCOProc2]
     @marci nvarchar(4000),
	@zi datetime,
	@mod int = 1,
	@grila int = 0
AS

BEGIN

DECLARE @f10003 INT;
DECLARE @ZileCuveniteAn INT;
DECLARE @ZileCuvenite INT;
DECLARE @ZileCuveniteZi INT;
DECLARE @ZileAnPrecedent INT;
DECLARE @cnt INT;
DECLARE @cursor_db CURSOR


IF @marci = 'P1' -- Toti
	BEGIN 
		SET @cursor_db = CURSOR FOR 
		SELECT f10003 
		FROM f100
	END

IF @marci = 'P2' -- Activi
	BEGIN 
		SET @cursor_db = CURSOR FOR 
		SELECT f10003 
		FROM f100 outer apply DamiDataPlecare(f100.f10003, convert(date, getdate())) ddp
		WHERE convert(date, getdate()) between convert(date, F10022) and ddp.DataPlecare    
	END

IF @marci = 'P3' -- Plecati
	BEGIN 
		SET @cursor_db = CURSOR FOR 
		SELECT f10003 
		FROM f100 outer apply DamiDataPlecare(f100.f10003, convert(date, getdate())) ddp
		WHERE convert(date, getdate()) > ddp.DataPlecare   
	END

IF @marci = 'P4' -- In avans
	BEGIN 
		DECLARE @sql_xml XML = Cast('<root><U>'+ Replace(@marci, ',', '</U><U>')+ '</U></root>' AS XML)

		SET @cursor_db = CURSOR FOR 
		SELECT f.x.value('.', 'BIGINT') AS user_id
		FROM @sql_xml.nodes('/root/U') f(x) 
	END

IF @marci not like 'P%' 
	BEGIN
		SET @cursor_db = CURSOR FOR 
		SELECT f10003 
		FROM f100 
		WHERE convert(date, getdate()) < f10022 
	END

OPEN @cursor_db  
FETCH NEXT FROM @cursor_db INTO @f10003  

WHILE @@FETCH_STATUS = 0  
BEGIN  

	SELECT @ZileCuveniteAn=ZileCuveniteAn, @ZileCuvenite=ZileCuvenite,@ZileCuveniteZi=ZileCuveniteZi,@ZileAnPrecedent=ZileAnPrecedent  FROM CalculCO(@f10003, @zi, @mod, @grila)

	SELECT @cnt = COUNT(*) FROM Ptj_tblZileCO WHERE F10003 = @f10003 and An = year(@zi)

		if (year(@zi) = (SELECT F01011 FROM F010))
		UPDATE F100 set F100642 =  @ZileCuveniteAn, F100995 =  @ZileCuvenite, F100996 = @ZileAnPrecedent WHERE
		F10003 = @f10003;

	  if (year(@zi) >= (SELECT F01011 FROM F010))
	   if(@cnt > 0)
			UPDATE Ptj_tblZileCO set CuveniteAn = @ZileCuveniteAn, Cuvenite = @ZileCuvenite WHERE
			F10003 = @f10003 and An = year(@zi);
		else
			INSERT INTO Ptj_tblZileCO (F10003, An, Cuvenite, SoldAnterior, Efectuate, CuveniteAn)
			VALUES (@f10003, year(@zi), @ZileCuvenite, 0, 0, @ZileCuveniteAn)


		  FETCH NEXT FROM @cursor_db INTO @f10003 
END 

CLOSE @cursor_db  
DEALLOCATE @cursor_db 

END

CREATE TABLE [dbo].[Ptj_tblZileCOSuplimentare](
[F10003] [int] NULL,
[AnInceput] [int] NULL,
[AnSfarsit] [int] NULL,
[ZileCOSuplimentare] [int] NULL,
[USER_NO] [int] NULL,
[TIME] [datetime] NULL,
[IdAuto] [int] IDENTITY(1,1) NOT NULL,
CONSTRAINT [Ptj_tblZileCOSuplimentare_PK] PRIMARY KEY CLUSTERED
(
[IdAuto] ASC
)WITH (PAD_INDEX = OFF, STATISTICS_NORECOMPUTE = OFF, IGNORE_DUP_KEY = OFF, ALLOW_ROW_LOCKS = ON, ALLOW_PAGE_LOCKS = ON) ON [PRIMARY]
) ON [PRIMARY]

GO


ALTER FUNCTION [dbo].[CalculCO] (
       @f10003 INT,
  @zi datetime,
  @mod int,
  @grila int
)
  RETURNS @CalculCO TABLE (
      ZileCuveniteAn int,
      ZileCuvenite int,
      ZileCuveniteZi int,
      ZileAnPrecedent int
  )
AS

BEGIN

declare @ZileCuveniteAn int,  @ZileCuveniteAnSuplim18Ani int, @ZileCuveniteAnSuplimHand int, @ZileCuvenite int, @ZileCuveniteZi int, @ZileAnPrecedent int, @ZileAngajare int, @ZileAngajareZi int,@ZileSuspendare int, @ZileSuspendareZi int, @ZileSuspendare18Ani int, @ZileSuspendare18AniZi int, @ZileSuspendareHand int, @ZileSuspendareHandZi int, @PrimaZiAn date, @UltimaZiAn date, @UltimaZi18Ani date, @UltimaZiHand date, @UltimaZi18aniZi date, @UltimaZiHandZi date, @TipCalcul int, @ZileSuplimentare int, @ZileSuplimentareAng int, @LuniVechime int, @DataPrimeiAngajari date, @CalculCOProp18Ani int, @CalculCOPropHand int, @ZileAn int, @SuspendariExcluse nvarchar(100), @f10023 datetime, @DataAnCalculVechime datetime


-- @TipCalcul
--  1 -- se calculeaza vechimea in munca in ultima zi din an
-- 2. se calculeaza vechimea in munca in prima zi din an
--  3 se calculeaza vechimea in munca in ziua angajarii
--  4 -- se calculeaza vechimea in munca in ultima zi din an, iar pentru cei plecati in timpul anului la data plecarii

--   11 -- se calculeaza vechimea in companie in ultima zi din an
-- 12 se calculeaza vechimea in companie in prima zi din an
--  13 se calculeaza vechimea in companie in ziua angajarii
--14 - se calculeaza vechimea in companie in ultima zi din an, iar pentru cei plecati in timpul anului la data plecarii

--   21 -- se calculeaza vechimea de la data angajarii in ultima zi din an
-- 22 se calculeaza vechimea de la data angajarii in prima zi din an
--  23 se calculeaza vechimea de la data angajarii in ziua angajarii
--   24 -- se calculeaza vechimea de la data angajarii in ultima zi din an, iar pentru cei plecati in timpul anului la data plecarii

--   31 -- se calculeaza vechimea de la data primei angajarii in ultima zi din an
-- 32 - se calculeaza vechimea de la data primei angajarii in prima zi din an
--  33  -se calculeaza vechimea de la data primei angajarii in ziua angajarii 
--   34 -- se calculeaza vechimea de la data primei angajarii in ultima zi din an, iar pentru cei plecati in timpul anului la data plecarii

-- 99 - particular

select @ZileAn = 365
if  year(@zi) % 4 = 0
  select @ZileAn = 366;

if isnull(@grila,0)= 0
  select @grila = f10072 from f100 where f10003 = @f10003;


select @f10023 = DataPlecare from DamiDataPlecare(@f10003, @zi);

Select @ZileSuplimentare = Convert(int,isnull((select "Valoare" from "tblParametrii" where "Nume"='NrZilePersoanaDizabilitatiSauMaiMica18Ani'),3));
select @ZileSuplimentareAng = convert(int, isnull((select isnull(ZileCOSuplimentare,0) from Ptj_tblZileCOSuplimentare where f10003 = @f10003 and (year(@zi) between AnInceput and AnSfarsit)),0));
Select @TipCalcul = Convert(int,isnull((select "Valoare" from "tblParametrii" where "Nume"='ModCalculZileCOCuvenite'),1));
Select @CalculCOProp18Ani = Convert(int,isnull((select "Valoare" from "tblParametrii" where "Nume"='ModCalculZileCO_Proportional_18Ani'),0));
Select @CalculCOPropHand = Convert(int,isnull((select "Valoare" from "tblParametrii" where "Nume"='ModCalculZileCO_Proportional_Handicap'),0));
Select @SuspendariExcluse = Convert(nvarchar(100),isnull((select "Valoare" from "tblParametrii" where "Nume"='ModCalculZileCO_SuspendariExcluse'),' '));


Select @PrimaZiAn = CASE WHEN cast(F10022 as date) < convert(varchar, year(@zi))  +  '-01-01'  THEN convert(varchar, year(@zi))  + '-01-01'  ELSE cast(F10022 as date) END, @UltimaZiAn = CASE WHEN cast(@f10023 as date) < convert(varchar, year(@zi))  +  '-12-31'  THEN cast(@f10023 as date) ELSE convert(varchar, year(@zi))  +  '-12-31'  END from (select * from F100 where f10003 = @F10003) a ;

Select @ZileAngajare = datediff(day, @PrimaZiAn, @UltimaZiAn)+1 , @ZileAngajareZi = datediff(day, @PrimaZiAn,  (CASE WHEN cast(@f10023 as date) < @zi THEN cast(@f10023 as date) ELSE @zi END))+1 from (select * from F100 where f10003 = @F10003) a  ;

Select @DataPrimeiAngajari = case when year(isnull(F1001049,'2100-01-01')) not in (1900,2100) then F1001049 else F10022 end from (select f100.f10003, f100.f10022, f1001.F1001049 from F100 join f1001 on f100.f10003 = f1001.f10003 where f100.f10003 = @F10003) a  ;


Select @DataAnCalculVechime = case when @TipCalcul in (0,1,11,21,31) then convert(varchar, year(@zi)) + '-12-31'
                                                                                                                        when @TipCalcul in (2,12,22,32) then convert(varchar, year(@zi))  +  '-01-01'
                                                                                                                        when @TipCalcul in (3,13,23,33) then @zi
                                                                                                                        when  @TipCalcul in (4,14,24,34) then case when year(@f10023) > year(@zi) then convert(varchar, year(@zi)) + '-12-31' else @f10023 end
                                                                                                                        end ;

Select @LuniVechime = case 

when @TipCalcul in (0,1,2,3,4) then
               ISNULL(convert(int,substring(F100644,1,2)),0) * 12 + ISNULL(convert(int,substring(F100644,3,2)),0) + DATEDIFF (MONTH,   (select convert(nvarchar(4),F01011) + '-' +
    convert(nvarchar(4),F01012) + '-01' from F010), @DataAnCalculVechime)

when @TipCalcul in (11,12,13,14) then
               ISNULL(convert(int,substring(F100643,1,2)),0) * 12 + ISNULL(convert(int,substring(F100643,3,2)),0) + DATEDIFF (MONTH,   (select convert(nvarchar(4),F01011) + '-' +
    convert(nvarchar(4),F01012) + '-01' from F010), @DataAnCalculVechime) 

when @TipCalcul in (21,22,23,24) then
     DATEDIFF (MONTH, F10022, @DataAnCalculVechime)
   - case when day(f10022) > day(@DataAnCalculVechime) then 1 else 0 end  
 
when @TipCalcul in (31,32,33,34) then
                 DATEDIFF (MONTH, @DataPrimeiAngajari, @DataAnCalculVechime)
               - case when day(@DataPrimeiAngajari) > day(@DataAnCalculVechime) then 1 else 0 end  

when @TipCalcul = 99 then
     DATEDIFF (MONTH,  case when f10022 <= '2018-02-14' then '2018-02-14' else f10022 end , @zi )
   - case when ( case when f10022 <= '2018-02-14' then 14 else day(f10022) end) > day(@zi)  then 1 else 0 end

end     from f100 where f10003 = @f10003;

if isnull(@LuniVechime,0) < =0 
                select @LuniVechime = 0;

select @ZileCuveniteAnSuplimHand  = CASE WHEN ISNULL(a.F10027,0)>=2 and (f100271 = '2100-01-01' or f100271 = '1900-01-01' or @PrimaZiAn <= f100271) THEN convert(int, @ZileSuplimentare) else 0 end,
@ZileCuveniteAnSuplim18Ani =   case when dateadd(year,18,f10021) >= @PrimaZiAn  then convert(int, @ZileSuplimentare,0)  else 0 end
from (select * from F100 where f10003 = @F10003) a ;  

If @mod <> 1
   select @ZileCuveniteAn = CuveniteAn from ptj_tblzileco where an=year(@zi) and f10003 = @f10003 else
  select @ZileCuveniteAn =     c.F02615 + @ZileSuplimentareAng + @ZileCuveniteAnSuplim18Ani + @ZileCuveniteAnSuplimHand
      from (select * from F100 where f10003 = @F10003) a    left join F026 c on convert(int,@grila) = c.F02604 and
      (convert(int,c.F02610/100) * 12) <= @LuniVechime and @LuniVechime < (convert(int,c.F02611/100) * 12)  where (year(@zi)  between year(F10022) and year(F10023) ) and a.F10003= @f10003 ;


select @UltimaZi18Ani = case when  dateadd(year, 18, f10021) <= @UltimaZiAn  then dateadd(year, 18, f10021)  else @UltimaZiAn end,  @UltimaZiHand = case when f100271 = '2100-01-01' or f100271 = '1900-01-01' or f100271 > @UltimaZiAn then @UltimaZiAn else f100271 end  from (select * from F100 where f10003 = @F10003) a;

select @UltimaZi18AniZi = case when @UltimaZi18Ani <= CONVERT(date,@zi) then @UltimaZi18Ani else CONVERT(date,@zi) end,
  @UltimaZiHandZi = case when @UltimaZiHand <= CONVERT(date,@zi) then @UltimaZiHand else CONVERT(date,@zi) end;

  with xx as  ( select f111.f11103 Marca, f111.f11105 de_la_data, case when f111.f11107='2100-01-01' then f111.f11106 else dateadd(d,-1,f111.f11107) end la_data from f111
               inner join
(select a.f11103, a.f11105, case when a.f11107='2100-01-01' then a.f11106 else dateadd(d,-1,a.f11107) end f11107, a.time, max(b.time) timp from F111 a inner join f111 b  on
a.F11103 = b.F11103 and  (a.f11105 <= case when b.f11107='2100-01-01' then b.f11106 else dateadd(d,-1,b.f11107) end   and b.f11105 <= case when a.f11107='2100-01-01'
then a.f11106 else dateadd(d,-1,a.f11107) end)  group by a.f11103, a.f11105, case when a.f11107='2100-01-01' then a.f11106 else dateadd(d,-1,a.f11107) end, a.time) t  on f111.f11103 = t.f11103 and
f111.f11105 = t.f11105 and   case when f111.f11107='2100-01-01' then f111.f11106 else dateadd(d,-1,f111.f11107) end = t.f11107 and f111.time = t.timp 
where CHARINDEX(concat(',',ltrim(rtrim(convert(nvarchar(100),f111.f11104))),','), concat(',',ltrim(rtrim(@SuspendariExcluse)),','))  = 0  union all select f10003 Marca, datainceput de_la_data, datasfarsit la_data  from ptj_cereri inner join Ptj_tblAbsente on Ptj_Cereri.IdAbsenta = Ptj_tblAbsente.id  where
ptj_cereri.IdStare=3 and isnull(Ptj_tblAbsente.AbsenteCFPInCalculCO,0) = 1  ),  yy as  (select distinct a.marca, min(b.de_la_data) de_la_data, max(b.la_data) la_data from xx a  inner join xx b on a.marca = b.marca and  (a.de_la_data <= b.la_data and b.de_la_data <= a.la_data)  group by a.marca, a.de_la_data, a.la_data),
f111_2 as   (select distinct a.marca f11103, min(b.de_la_data) f11105, max(b.la_data)  f11107 from yy a  inner join yy b on a.marca = b.marca and (a.de_la_data <=
  b.la_data and b.de_la_data <= a.la_data)  group by a.marca, a.de_la_data, a.la_data)

select  @ZileSuspendare= (select COALESCE(SUM(datediff(d,CASE WHEN F11105 <  @PrimaZiAn THEN @PrimaZiAn else F11105 END,CASE WHEN F11107 > @UltimaZiAn THEN @UltimaZiAn else F11107 END) + 1) ,0) from (select * from F100 where f10003 = @F10003) a  join f111_2 Z on a.f10003 = z.f11103  and F11105 <= F11107 AND F11107 >= @PrimaZiAn AND F11105 <= @UltimaZiAn) , @ZileSuspendareZi = (select COALESCE(SUM(datediff(d,CASE WHEN F11105 < @PrimaZiAn THEN @PrimaZiAn else F11105 END,CASE WHEN F11107 > CONVERT(date,@zi) THEN CONVERT(date,@zi) else F11107 END)+1) ,0)  from (select * from F100 where f10003 = @F10003) a  join f111_2 Z on a.f10003 = z.f11103  and F11105 <= F11107 AND F11107 >= @PrimaZiAn AND F11105 <= CONVERT(date,@zi)),  @ZileSuspendare18Ani= (select COALESCE(SUM(datediff(d,CASE WHEN F11105 <  @PrimaZiAn THEN @PrimaZiAn else F11105 END,CASE WHEN F11107 > @UltimaZi18Ani THEN @UltimaZi18Ani else F11107 END) + 1) ,0) from (select * from F100 where f10003 = @F10003) a  join f111_2 Z on a.f10003 = z.f11103  and F11105 <= F11107 AND F11107 >= @PrimaZiAn AND F11105 <= @UltimaZi18Ani) , @ZileSuspendare18AniZi = (select COALESCE(SUM(datediff(d,CASE WHEN F11105 < @PrimaZiAn THEN @PrimaZiAn else F11105 END,CASE WHEN F11107 > @UltimaZi18AniZi THEN @UltimaZi18AniZi else F11107 END)+1) ,0)  from (select * from F100 where f10003 = @F10003) a  join f111_2 Z on a.f10003 = z.f11103  and F11105 <= F11107 AND F11107 >= @PrimaZiAn AND F11105 <= @UltimaZi18AniZi),  @ZileSuspendareHand = (select COALESCE(SUM(datediff(d,CASE WHEN F11105 <  @PrimaZiAn THEN @PrimaZiAn else F11105 END,CASE WHEN F11107 > @UltimaZiHand THEN @UltimaZiHand else F11107 END) + 1) ,0) from (select * from F100 where f10003 = @F10003) a  join f111_2 Z on a.f10003 = z.f11103  and F11105 <= F11107 AND F11107 >= @PrimaZiAn AND F11105 <= @UltimaZiHand) , @ZileSuspendareHandZi = (select COALESCE(SUM(datediff(d,CASE WHEN F11105 < @PrimaZiAn THEN @PrimaZiAn else F11105 END,CASE WHEN F11107 > @UltimaZiHandZi THEN @UltimaZiHandZi else F11107 END)+1) ,0)  from (select * from F100 where f10003 = @F10003) a  join f111_2 Z on a.f10003 = z.f11103  and F11105 <= F11107 AND F11107 >= @PrimaZiAn AND F11105 <= @UltimaZiHandZi) ;



select @ZileCuvenite = case when @mod= 1 then 
                                             round(convert(float,(@ZileCuveniteAn -  @ZileCuveniteAnSuplim18Ani - @ZileCuveniteAnSuplimHand) * (@ZileAngajare - isnull(@ZileSuspendare,0))) /CONVERT(float,@ZileAn),0) +
   convert(int, round( case when @CalculCOPropHand = 0  then 1 else (datediff(day, @PrimaZiAn,  @UltimaZiHand)+1 - @ZileSuspendareHand) / convert(float, @ZileAn) end * @ZileCuveniteAnSuplimHand,0)) +
               convert(int, round( case when @CalculCOProp18Ani = 0  then 1 else (datediff(day, @PrimaZiAn,  @UltimaZi18Ani)+1 - @ZileSuspendare18Ani) / convert(float, @ZileAn) end * @ZileCuveniteAnSuplim18Ani,0)) 
           else (select Cuvenite from Ptj_tblZileCO where f10003 = @f10003 and an = year(@zi)) end;

select @ZileCuveniteZi =  round(convert(float, (@ZileCuveniteAn -  @ZileCuveniteAnSuplim18Ani - @ZileCuveniteAnSuplimHand)  * (@ZileAngajareZi - isnull(@ZileSuspendareZi,0))) /CONVERT(float,@ZileAn),0)+
   convert(int, round( case when @CalculCOPropHand = 0  then 1 else (datediff(day, @PrimaZiAn,  @UltimaZiHandZi)+1 - @ZileSuspendareHandZi) / convert(float, @ZileAn) end * @ZileCuveniteAnSuplimHand,0)) +
               convert(int, round( case when @CalculCOProp18Ani = 0  then 1 else (datediff(day, @PrimaZiAn,  @UltimaZi18aniZi)+1 - @ZileSuspendare18AniZi) / convert(float, @ZileAn) end * @ZileCuveniteAnSuplim18Ani,0)) 

INSERT INTO @CalculCO
SELECT @ZileCuveniteAn, isnull(@ZileCuvenite,0), @ZileCuveniteZi, isnull((select SoldAnterior from Ptj_tblZileCO where f10003 = @f10003 and an=year(@zi)),0);

RETURN;
END
